column3: Izesu' aza lelikumu' ve lo minevo' alevo've hulo lute ngemali'mi monovo lelebizavo ningo gele none. Nemu' laza a'mine'mine ogo evenekumu' nene minevo' alevote hulolonido' o neive.

Zuda ve O'moso'mo avo'ningine ise'ine izingumu' gili holise' minaa' ani' gamene nene alitelesa gamene hamo' ha neivo Izesu' aza me misubo hulosa melehida viline' gamene nene mo ogave lo gala giline' ve. Eze evenele me misubou' minani' lulo ngimine' nene atoli'mine ogo ngemo heleline' nesi nene ivile' ivosa minine' ve.

Ido' kilisimasi foti (40) ne'mi lulou' ma nene O'moso'mo zamotinemu' mulunou' goloso gehepeve giline' neve. A'mine hamo' aleve ingine kilisimasi foti (40) ne'mi lulou' lihime di ebe' hadivela hili gese' ani' aleve engi' nemu' nene mulunou' goloso gehepeve giline' ma neive.

Lingine O'moso'mi izipahala mini ei' gamazi've gili dalizado' o neine' nenaze. Nemu' nene lingine gomu' ezemu' gilami haza minani' gamenela vomine lanite' gilaa' ani' inite' malo' nene gohi mini milamilo.
Ee, O'moso'mo evene' ato ato' muki' nene ise'ine izelido' lisihe' i minilizangumu' ve lo evene' muki' nene ezelo' gelekele' amaa' monovo'mi gesi mingu' nene hulo-ngidine' ve.

Ido' a'mine ve'inesi ha minaa' nani' inite' seta've seta've engi' vovo'ninguti' nene nolo ma ti' lo soto' ine' ma giluve: Ga'na gamene ogavo noso' nite' meni've dizo vavo noso' nite' viti meni hizilizani' nene moni naba fo kina (K4) ne'mine hulisa noso' nite' viti nene geni've ngomo vani kilo (1Kg) a'ne'minevo' nene dalisave. Ido' noso' nite' goloso gidini bali nene meni hizilisa fo kina hulilizado' nene tili kilo (3Kg) ne'minevo' nene dalisave. Ne neiha noso' nite' gize vata' iga' ani' uveli'mi za've oliva za nesi ido' vaini nala' nesi nene ha minilisasize. Do goloso amozo lo lo-dine' ve.
Ne'mine igi Guvelesi ve'mi velelo' langisetine lutine di'mi limilo. Ne'mine ikevo Guvelesi ve aza do'mo dize-lengedeleseive.

Nemu' nene aza numudo' namado' ve monovote do soto' molo do lisihe' ogo lihime lemeline' gamene molo neive. Ido' a'mine gameneu' goni' gelelive nene do kegeso hulo-dine'. Ido' a'mine do kegese-dive ma nene neive li numudo' namado' ve gililizave lo hilinguti' do ote-davo neive.

Ne'mine igi amilite uhoni nala' nene di gangi guve'inesi ve nabalite gihaa' ani' inite' ne'mine apa nite' igi lili' igi godololo' gihi-di gulehe' lavolavo guve'inesi vete ngilaa' ani' ne'mine nene di ngili-dani' ve.
Nemu' nene monoteli'mi biluva' ve nete ngemenga likelizave lo naza vene' gosoho' gevono' minani' nene velo' gohi vi izipe gidi mili numu'ine ebe'nido' nene gizebo igi minilizave losa noluve.

Me'neho nene nenikisi minaa' neivo naza nene me'nehosi minaa' nouve lo lo-lengemaa' nouvoni' nene gili ele'vole' ilizado' o neive. Ido' haza gili ele'vole' amilizado' noline' nene neni' me'nehi gono do ogo molo nouvoni' initetoti' nene gili ele'vole' ilizani' o neive.

Ne'mine ogosa a'mine helaa' monovo nesi ido' hilavete minaa' ani' numuno ebe' nesi nene salfa gehenilo' olo' lo mino noso ohuno ne'mino molo miningu' nene do hulo-ngidine' ve. A'mine salfa gehenilo' olo' lo mino noso ohuno ne'mino molo minine' neve nene helaa' naba tuu ma ne neive.

Ido' dizine' nene Zuda veti eveneto' medelo mino O'moso inite' lehize-daa' ive naba aza ei' vanise've do dizamo ize ato atoliti vanise'ine nene O'moso'mi kekeize atoli'mine lo minine' numuno lulo'veu' nene kilisimasilo' kilisimasilo' do dizo O'moso lehize-deka' lehize-deka' oga' ine' ne'mine nene ei' Kilisito' ilido' o minidiniko O'moso'mo misubo do soto' idoti' api' ogo gamene muki' oko'no hulo'mo ogo mulumo geleka' geleka' ogovo' minidine'za a'mine Zuda veti eveneto' medelo mino O'moso inite' lehize-daa' ive naba'mo oga' ine' ne'mine ilido' minamine' nenako nemu' aza gamene muki' eze oko'no hulo vanise've lepo O'moso lehize-deka' lehize-deka' ogo minelesa dizine' nevoba asi O'moso'mo molani' gamene nene osu' lolosa neivo Kilisito' aza gamene hamokovo' ei' oko'no nene hulo vanise've lepo O'moso lehize-do lihimete nene mudise hulo-ledelesa soto' ine' ve.
ingine goloso nite' i'mi vangumu' gosele' belamivo gizebo o-ngede'mo vo neivo kilisimasi foti (40) ogo vine'.
Nemu' nene neze zuho mate, noso' nitekisi lebeni initekisi nalisa igi di nubo niigi ma nene lingine zuho amani' nene ikevo maka' nalone li gizebo mini ikevosavo' nene nalo.

Ido' ne'mine lo-ngemavo naza ninge nouvo sipisipi angale ne'mo nene buku'mi nala've naba sigisi ma nene huko apasavo mimi' naba goloso ine' ve. Ido' ho' nene gonobu' elo lihizine' nene vene' gevonolite gonobu' initekovo' ngilaa' naani' gele vine' ne'mine ine' ve. Ido' ike'ni'mi velelo' nene vanise ne'mino gulehe' elo osu' line' ve.

Ido' vene' linge ma nene izipaha'ine hilikenguti' nene O'moso'mo do ote-ngedavo gohi ize'ningida igi gi'mizaa' ani' ve. Ido' linge ma ingine O'mosomu' gili ele'vole' igi minani' ne'mo ve malite gavoso ngibili goboni mili-ngidi ti' li li-ngidaa' ani' ve: Isetine izo gavoso lengebelamoloniko lingine O'moso mehedine imi mono' nene hulilizave li ne'mine li-ngidaa' ani'za alingeta hele noloninguti' gohi oto minevo' minevo' lemeni dameni lamine' doso' ma nenave li gili huli nizavo ngibilikevo hilaa' ani' ve.

Lavo Paulo' aza pilisi ve ti' lo lo-ngimine': Laza nene Loma ve lengi' muliseuti' nosine'za Loma ve i-ngidisa'mani' inite' ma i-lidi goni' i-lidilisa gilani' nene leze monovo vise' igi lihimete di soto' mili lami haza evene' mukiliti ve'nido' gavoso libili nala' numungu' huli-lidani' ma nemu' nene suno' limiselilisa nilahe. Ne'mino nomive. Angise'ine igi lele'mize heta ikevo volosine' o neive.

Ee, O'moso'mo lo huko line' gamazi ado' vene' vemoho' lili' ikeni' nete vene' vemoho' masi gopo ingamilo, ido' evene' ma ngibili hilamilo, ido' gumine amilo, ido' evene' maliti inite'nido' mumuzo' amilo line' gamazisi ido' O'moso'mo lo huko line' gamazi ato ato' muki' nesi nene ado' gamazi ti' lo ma neine' ne'mo nene asabu' izo osu' lo neive. Ado' lingine lengi' okodinemu' gilaa' nani' ne'mini lengi' nizada minilizavemu' nene gili lutine ngimilo.

Ido' ogavo eze ningo emeni dameni ne'mine gidinisi minelone li ezemu' gili ele'vole' igi minaa' nave muki' ingine nene ei' lulo lamine' minine' ne'mino leze lute nesi lamine' minelive li engi' lu'ine di lamine' igi minaa' nave.
Ee, neni' lu'neu' gehepeve vomine O'moso'mi lou' gamazimu' nene lanite' gelaa' nouha
Ido' lingine gamene gamene Guvelesi vemu' longolize izivo' minilo. Ido' gohi ti' lo noluve: Longolize izivo' minilo.
Ne'mine lavo naza a'mine ne'mine nolo molo gamazi lo-nimive nene ningelesa mine velepe' izuvoni' ve. Ne'mine ogo ninguvoni' nene ngolidunu' lili' ani' lamu seveni nene ningo

Ido' O'moso aza evene' mine gelaa' ebe' ngemelesa nouvongu' nene ingine mini gilamilisave lo evene' zamotinemu' lo huko line' ma neve. A'mine hamo' aleve ingine O'moso'mi gamazi gili huli mehe'ine imave engikumu' nene mine gelaa' ebe' ngemelesa nouvongu' nene igi mini gilamilisave lo lo hukine' ve.
Olihe amuvo gomu' ave muki' nene gizengize ve guminelo' ve ne'minevo' minani'za sipisipi ize nete ingine ma gili ngimamani' ve.

Gonolo' gipe alu lingine lengehelele gehepeve izivo mini metinge gizebo vetine nene gelekele' i-ngidivo' minilo. Ado' gizebo vetine ve lamine' hongu ve ne'mine minilizanikovo' gelekele' i-ngidi minilizavoba asi metinge gasava ve minilizani' nesi nene ha gelekele' i-ngidivo' minilo.
Ele'mizi vikevo sakupo gamazi laa' ave soza li ti' li lani': Me ve nene mono' ebe' memukisi O'moso'mo lavo Mose' lo huko-lidine' gamazi mamukisi dovo ledevo' ogo lo minaa' neive.

Ido' a'mine noluvoni' inite' muki' nene O'mosolatikovo' soto' ine' monovo ne neive. O'moso aza nene Kilisito' gono dadi'mo nene eze biluva' o-do minuninguti' nene laza ezela ogo do hamo' ogo bizelone' akate vele-ledosa evene' linge nene ezesi di hamo' igi bizilizangumu' ve losa a'mine akalo' ngele'mize molalone' gono nene mo leli' limine' ma neive.

Ido' O'moso'mi velemu' igi eze gamazi li soto' iga' ave polohete ingine evenelite goboni nimili-ngidavo nemu' nene gosele' asele' ami ele'vole' igi minani' nene gili nizave. Ingine mulumo initeku' mini gosele' asele' amo ele'vole' ogo minali'mi monovo nene lelebizikenaze. Ingine adi'mine ilo.
Ido' Guvelesi ve'mi gulive di minilizave nene O'moso'mo do ngu' ize-lengedeleseive lo gize neive.

ti' li lani' ve: Mo lamine' likeve. Nemu' nene leli' O'mosote aza amuzo ve mino ido' ele'vole' ogo mino ido' gala gele nge lo minaa' ive dizo neivo guvele monaa' neingumu' nene isaa' neve lo do naba o-do opo'ni nolune' nene mo huko vamo minevo' minevo' ogo minelive. Mo ne'mino miniliho.

Ido' gonolisetine nene okodine losuvolo' mineline' inite' ado' madudine zopovo nalava izi di ma'mine ma'mine iga' nehe, ngolidunu' lili' ani' inite' nehe, okodido' inite' lamine' tamine' nehe, nevo'mine inite' neve nene minelivoba

Nemu' nene gaza govozo helamo mino Guvetesi vemu' gamazi've nene lo soto sotokovo' ozo. Ido' a'mine Guvetesi vemu' nalato' ve lolo' ogo nouve nenikumukisi nene govozo helamozo. Asi Kilisito' gamazi laminekumu' lelitokisi soto' o-ledaa' neine' mulumo geni inite' ne'mine soto' o gemeline' nene gazasi O'moso'mo amuzo geme neine' ne'mi votigilelo' do molo ha gehe'mo vo minezo.
Ido' gamazi gihile lamine' ne'mo gono'inemu' do lisihe' o-ngedavo mini kegesi minilizado' o neize. Nemu' nene naza engikumu' ve lo oko'ne hulolodo' na'nise'ne nene mine kegese nouve.

Upuho' igi otilo. Lengita monotine linge nene ha neiha mo helelido' o neine' nene hize ele' igi di ngi lilo. Nanitekumu' ve. Lingine igi mili iga' nani' monovotine nene neni' O'moso'ne'mo ningine' nene ei' gele neine' makilo' olihe vo damine' nemu' nene mo ninge nouve.
Ido' neloti' angelo' naba tili ne'mo vo ei' lapese'veu' minine' inite' goloso ma nene lepe hulo noso naba' nabaukisi hinipini' noso ngomo ngamaukisi ogavo vanise gehepeve lolo' ine' ve.

Ee, idise mela O'moso'mo nasahili' noo-lidivo none' aka nene a'mine Guvetesi ve ne'mo vele-ledavosa a'mingu' none. Ido' a'mingu' mino O'moso'mi emeni dameni lamine' nene mudise do leli' olosune lo a'minemu' nene gilingili ogo gizebo ogo lolize izo minaa' noune.

Ee, vene' vemoho' gipe alu gopo'napa ingi'mi monaa' nave nehe ido do goloso o-ngedeline' monovo goloso igi mili iga' nave nehe ido' inite' gohi gohi dalone li gilaa' nave nene a'mine inite' ne'mo engi' O'moso'ine gelavo soza o'moso opo'ni li minaa' ave ne'mine ve nene O'mososi Kilisitokisi gizebo i minasingu' nene vi hilami salani mili-lidasine' inite' nesi nene ma damilisave lo laminetokovo' nolo-lingimuze. Gili minilo. Ido' a'mine ne'mine monovo daa' nave nene O'mososi Kilisitokisi gizebo i minasingu' nene vi hilamilisanako nemu' nene lingine a'mine ne'mine monovo nene damilo lo nolo-lingimuve.

Ido' Abalahamu' aza O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo minine' nenako nemu' nene O'moso'mo naza gelebizeloni' misubola ga' lo vozo lo lo-davo aza a'mido' gele do vine' ve. Ee, aza vo heteleline' misubo nemukisi nene ningo gelamo gopo eze misubo've hulo O'moso'mo a'vopilemo' zuholiti misubo minelive lo alinge' imine' misubola nene ga' lo vo minine'.

Ido' lutine nene do gopo o-lengedavo vi tolovo ikelizaze. Negi noso nene ni sipaki igi minamilo. Asi O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo nene lutine vaito' gizebo o neivo mini ei' lilidokovo' nene e'meti minilo.
Ido' ingine ne'mine mana'mine monovo goloso gopo iga' ilizani' monovo'nido' nene evene' muki' nge'metilisave. Nemu' nene evenelite mono' aka gihile nene divi' ledivi' ilisave.

Ne'mine noluvoni' nene KIlisito' aza lihimetemu' helo heta ato' vesi ido' Zuda vesi sitato' O'moso metehida alone' akate vele-ledavo O'moso'mi Sikalahu' hamo' ne'mo lele'mizo a'mine akalo' ogavo laza sitato' a'mido' ha oga' noune' nenako nemu' noluve.

Ido' heta ato' ve Izesu'nimu' gili ele'vole' igi nizavemu' nene gozopo' luhuvo nite' gizo hulune' nene lo hukune' gamazi nene ti' lo gizune' ma neive: Avazaha o'moso niteliti noso' nitekuti' nami ize guloliti vanise'ine nami ido' nala' i-ngidikevo hilani' ize guloti' nami vene' vemoho' ido' alungo umungive gopo ingamilo lo lo huko-ngidune' ma neive.
nGemavo Petolo' ti' lo lo-imine': Ananiazo. Gaza Satani'mo lemo lukau' gono davo nanimu' O'moso'mi Sikalahu' soza gani lo-emo misubo'mi meni lingela do halekekane.

Ido' O'moso'mo ne'mine ogo monoli'mi amuzo ato ato' lehize-ledo ne'mine gonolo' lele'mize molaa' neine' nene eze aleve lelikumu' nene monoku' izipe ngomo ne'mine minikevo tilikilo' ve ingine lengele'mize gopo ilisa gotine izi soza mono' ato ato' li-lingimikevo ne'mo gamene gamene hepeli'mo pipiza' nite' do volelo' melo' oga' neine' ne'mine igi mini me monoku' volobe ido' ma monoku' me volobe li minikelizave lo O'moso'mo eze evenele nene ge hize ele' o-nede ne hize ele' o-gede li gono di'mi vi mini lengi' mulise Kilisito' oko'no ne'mine neine' nene hize ele' ikevo amuzo molo minavo lingine muki' nene O'moso neni' gipe'nemu' gili ele'vole' igi ei' monovo've nene gili vevesi minikevo ne'mo lutine do hamo' ogavo monoku' lodive igi Kilisito' emeni dameni vai' nene lengita mine osu' lilido' o minivo minilizangumu' ve lo a'mine gono nene leli' daloningumu' ve lo do va'va' o-ledo gono ato atoku' lele'mize molaa' neive.

Ido' evene' malite monokumu' do gese' oga' monovo hulaa' nani' ne'mine igi lingine hulami monokumu' di gese' i'mi vi mini monoku' ge hize ele' o-nede ne hize ele' o-gede li minilo. Gamene naba mo avito' navo lingine mo ningi gili nizani' nenaze. Nemu' nene lingine mo ge hize ele' o-nede ne hize ele' o-gede livi' livi' igivo' minilo.

Nemu' nene lingine me misubou' monovo danava goloso lutingu' neine' ado' vene' vemoho' gipe alu gopo ingaa' monovosi ido' lute do goloso iline' monovo ato ato' nesi ido' inite' goloso mamu' lutine otavo ninge lamine' oga' nesi ido' inite' gohi masi masi dunivoo lii mumuzo' oga' monovo nene soza o'mosolo' gelekele' oga' monovo ne'mine nenaze a'mine nesi nene mo ngibili hilani' gelavo mudise hulisa minilo.

Labana' gamene'mi evenele nounako sipaki amo lute gate do veveso minelone. Ne'mine ogo Izesu'nimu' gele ele'vole' o none' ido' lute ngemaa' noune' ne'mo lepesete lolo' ogavo O'moso'mo do lu' izavo lamine' minelone lo lute gilingili ogo minaa' neine' ne'mo leze lovo angili' ne'mine lolo' ogavo minelone.

Ido' naza O'moso'mo gonou' amuzo gimine' nene amuzo molo do otezo noluvoni' nene a'mine O'moso'mo leme neine' lemeni dameni neve nene laza evenekumu' lovozo helo golise gelaa' lemeni dameni leme neivoba asi evene' ve'nido' ele'vole' ogo ogo molo oga' amuzo do minaa' lemeni damenisi ido' evene' lute ngemaa' lemenisi ido' lute okodelo' gizebo ele'vole' oga' amuzosi nene lehize-lede neize.
Ido' evene' lingelite eze ningo gele none li gamazi've gili disa'mani' nene ingine sozalo' ve minikevo gamazi gihile engita nomive.

naza nene nolize gehepeve izeloni' aka nene ma di soto' i-nidisa ne'mine igi minilo: A'mine nene ado' lingine lutine gatine di hamo' igivo' mini lutine ngemaa' monovo hamoto' e'meti ge luka neme ne lu'ne geme li mini lutine vo hamo' ogavo hamo' gatinevo' gili minilo.
Ne'mine lingumu' nene goni' o-deloningumu' analo' dalone li ne'mine ilisa ani'za ne'mine i-dilizave lo O'moso'mo molo-dine' gamene nene olihe amine' nenako ne'mo nene ne'mine i-damani' ve.

gono lamine' di nizavo heneni'ine nene a'mine gono lamine' ne'mo nene lolo' ogavosa a'mine nene vauve ili dii mini engita minine' inite' nene inele panala igi evene' masi nasahili' i-ngidi minilo lo lo-ngedezo.
Ne'mine lavo ingine ti' li li-imani' ve: Aza nene monovo goloso daa' ive minamidiniko laza nene gei' nanida ma ele'mizo amunidine.

Evene' ma ingine gamene mamu' nene gamene naba ve li gilaa' nani' nene Guvelesi vemu' gili ne'mine iga' nave. Ido' evene' ma noso' nite' ato ato' muki' naa' nani' nene a'mine noso' nitekumu' nene O'moso tangezo' ve li opo'ni li-daa' nani' nenako neve nene mo Guvelesi vemu' gili minisa naa' nave. Ido' evene' ma ingine noso' nite' ma malise iga' nave ingine Guvelesi vemu' gili malise igi inginesi O'moso tangezo' ve li opo'ni li-daa' nave.

Lingine Kilisito' do lamine' o-ledelesa neive li gili mu'musi' igi gizebo nizani' nenako nemu' a'mingu' nene longolizesi izisa minilo. Ido' geni inite' lengita soto' ilingumu' nene monotine hulami a'mine geni nene hongu li mini gihi minilo. Ido' O'mosola li minilizani' nene hulami laakovo' igi minilo.
Ne'mine lo lo-emo amiliti gizebo ve ti' lo lo-imine': Lingine Paulo'ni gizebo i-di ne'mine mana'mine i-dami zogo ve zuholite igi na'na' i-dilisa nilavo ma ha gili ngimilo.

Ido' evene' lute ngemaa' noogo ma nadi' nadi' i-lidilizahe nemu' lamo ha geho mino engikumu' nene evene' lamine' nizave lo gele ele'vole' o-ngede mino engita inite' lamine' muki' nene mo soto' o ngemeleseive lo gelo minelone. Ido' lute ngemaa' noune' nemu' nene ingine nanite' nanite' di gopo i-lidilizahe nene ha ninge'mo voovo' minelesune.

Ido' ve mali'mo gamazi ma line' mono' godolou' minine' ne'mo nene lelitokisi vo do neive. A'mine gamazi nene ti' lo lo neive: Naza gele ele'vole' ogo nouvoni' nenako nemu' nene naza lo soto' nouve. Lazasi nene a'mine'mine ogo Izesu'nimu' gele ele'vole' o minosa nene lo soto' oga' noune.

Ido' neze zuho mate, gatine do ti' lo nolo-lingidune: Izesu' evenele malite oko'ine losuvo'mi gono dami gopo minaa' nani' nene di hehe li-ngidilo. Ido' golise gelekele' igi nizave nene di amuzo mili-ngidilo. Ido' Izesu' evenele maliti lu'ine nene ele'vole' amivo ma nene hize ele' i-ngidilo. Ne'mine igi evene' mukikumu' elese' igi hongu li minilo.

Ido' neloti' nene angelo' naba faef ne'mo vo ei' lapese'veu' minine' inite' goloso nene lepe hulo loposo niteli'mo gizebo o-ngedo minaa' ine' mo'mosi'velo' nene ogavo a'mine gizebo o-ngedo minaa' ine' alevetida nene liti'muso naba izine' ve. Ne'mine ogavo evene' ingine mulumo giladi'mo ve'ine nahuno nene ingihi mata' mata' izi minii

Ido' nemu' nene a'mine noluvoni' gamazilo' nene e'meti igi mili minilizave nene lengita O'mosolati' hongu nesi ido' mangi gatulo nesi nene mino Isilaele' zuho gihile O'moso'mi evenele mukitasi nene mine do vo miniliho lo noluve.

Guvelesi ve'mi akamu' vetete' igi li-imikevo giline'. Ido' aza Izesu'nimu' gamazi nene do veveso laminosa ngilingili ogo amuzo molo vetete' ogo lo-ngeme' ngeme' ogo minine'za Izesu' zuho mono' noso hili-ngidaa' ani' monovo nene gelamo Zohane' mono' noso holo-ngedaa' ine' monovovo' nene gelo nemukovo' lo-ngemaa' ine'.
Ti' li lilizaha noso' nite' ma nene ha nalizahe ido' malise ilizahe ne'mine ilizangukisi ido' inite' ato ato' ilizangukisi nene O'moso'mi gulive do naba iline' initekovo' igi mili minilo.

lingine neve Kilisito' lehize-lingidine' Sikalahu've nene ha di mini'mi vi nizave. Di mini'mi vi nizanako evene' laza inite' matakumu' apize lengemelonido' nomive. A'mine Sikalahu've lehize-lingidine' ne'mo inite' matakumu' apize lengemaa' neive. Ido' gamazi lo-lengemaa' neine' nene sozasi nomive. Laminetokovo' lo-lengemaa' neine' nenako lido' nene gili di Kilisitoda gi'mizi minilo.

Ve ma sikalahu've nomivo oko'no losuvovo' mineline' nene mo hele neive lolosune. A'mine'mine ogo ve ma aza haza gele ele'vole' ogo mineline'za monovo lamine' ogo molo minamivo ma eze gele ele'vole' oga' neine've nene ezela mo helave lo lolosune.
Ne'mine lavo mukilite ningi nizavo noso' nite' ma do O'moso opo'ni lo do gito api' ogo nani'.

nGemamolone'za avazaha o'moso niteliti noso' nitekuti' nene namii vene' vemoho' gopo ingamii ize gulo nala' i-ngidanguti' namii ize guloliti vanise'ine namii malise igi kekeize li minilizave lo luhuvo nite' gizelone lo nogiluve.

Lo lavo Paulo' ti' lo lo-imine': Gaza lukau' guho' novine' gei' nene O'moso'mo gebeleleseive. Gaza nene Mose' lo huko line' akalo' nele'mizo molalove lo nolane'za a'mine lo huko line' gamazi nene avuto' ogo nibililizave lo go'ine noizabe.
Nemu' nene Izesu' Kilisitoda gi'mize minuniveti okodela nene lihime gohi ma nomivo O'moso'mo lihime lemelido' minamune.

Ne'mi monovo ne'mino neive: O'moso'mo izebolo' molani' nene apase-ledo lihime lemelove lo lele'mize molani' nomive. Asi Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' do lu' izavo minelone lo lele'mize molani' ma neive.

leme heta ogo vo misubou' misubou' evene' zuho ato ato' ado' nGogu ve Mangongu ve lani' aleve nene go'ine izo ngele'mize gopo oloseive. Ido' ngele'mize gopo ogo lovo di soto' igi hizilizangumu' nene do nubo o-ngedeleseive. A'mine di nubo ilizaa eveneliti naba'ine nene guvo noso gahevela gepe minine' ne'mini gatamolonido' mini vai' goloso minilisave.

Ido' gomuta nene lengikuti' evene' linge ma nete ne'mini goloso inite' daa' ave ma minani'za lingine igi Guvelesi ve Izesu' Kilisitoda gi'mizi eze gulive nene di lengita adi'mo O'moso'mi Sikalahu' nene lengita ogo gono do a'mine monovo golosotine nene gilite-lengedo O'moso'mi evenele lamine' lolo' o-lengedavo O'moso'mo lihimetinesi nomine' ve lo-lingidine' ve.

Ne'mine o-nidine' ne'mo naza idise mela mulumo alumo nite' mene gehe'mo nouvoni'za naza gele mu'musi' o-daa' nouve Kilisito' monovo've nene naza ningo gele minuvodi'mo aza gono nimine' nene do nouvo aza a'mido' gizebo lamine' iline' amuzo'vesi mino gizebo lamine' ogo neivo gamene naba aloseive lo gele ele'vole' o nouvoni' nenako nemu' novozo helamo mino a'mine gono nene daa' nouve.

Ne'mine igi mini lingine nene O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mi amuzololo' nene gamene gamene O'mosola li mini inite' nanitekumu' vise' ilizahe nemu' nene O'mosola livo' minilo. Ne'mine ilizangumu' nene gosele' lengebelamivo lutine okise ongamivo mini O'moso'mi zuho muki' engikumu' nene O'mosola livi' livi' igi minaa' ilo.

Paulo' nazasi ido' Siluvanokisi Timoteokisi laza Meteho O'moso ido' Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' eze evenele zuho lingine Tesalonika ebeku' mulise milaa' nani' nene luhuvo nite' gize-lengedelone losa luhuvo nite' mene nogize-lingiduze. Ningilo. Nogize-lengedo O'moso'mo nasahili o-lengedavo hongu lamineku' minilizave lo ezela noluve.
Hongu livo' minaa' nani' monovotine nene ningilizaze. Evene' mukita di soto' igi ngelebizilo. Guvelesi ve nene mo avito' oganaze.

Ne'mine line' nenako lingine lebeni inite' vaini nososi beleti nesi naliza gamenelo' gamenelo' nene Guvelesi ve hiline' gamazi nene li soto soto' i'mi vi minilisave. Ido' ne'mine i'mi vi nizavo Guvelesi ve tine' molo aline' gamene aliteleseive.

O'mosomu' gili ele'vole' i mini O'mosola lilizani' nene Guvelesi ve'mo do lamine' o-davo inite' gize dave aza lamine' geleleseive. Lamine' gelavo lihime've ma mineline' nene O'moso'mo a'mine lihime've hulo-deleseive.

Gamene gamene holuka' neiha holise' neiha O'mosola laa' nouvongu' geikumu' ga'ne molosa'mivo mino O'moso isaa' neve laa' nouve. A'mine O'moso nene avo'nemote gelekele' i-di opo'ni laa' adi'mine ogo lu'neu' monovo lisihekovo' neivo minosa nene gelekele' o-do opo'ni laa' nouve.

Ne'mine igisa golomukisi geheni gavulomukisi ti' li li-ngidani' ve: Laza nene mo'mosi'velo' minive O'moso'mi velelo' soto' ogo minamoloningumukisi ido' sipisipi angale'mo izebolo' molavo lihime lemelinguti' olovo' ogo mineloningumukisi nene lingine limi mili hiti-lidi di haleki-lidilo.

Gatine ngolo' live nii ma nene O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo eze evenele mulise minika' minika' angu' nolo-ngimine' gamazi meve nene gililo. Ve ma ingine monoli'mi lovou' Satani ivile' ilizave nene naza Okulumokuti' noso' nite' haleko minaa' neine' mana nene ma ngemekuvo nalisave. Ido' ma nene geheni mokono' ngemelesuve. A'mine gehenilo' nene gulive gosoho' mineka' mineka' ine' ngemekuvo dalizave netevo' nene a'mine gulivemu' nene suno' gili minilisave.

A'mine soza mono' apizi lingimilizave nene inite' gohi gohi dalone lii soza gamazi li-lingimilizadoti' nene lengitati' moni gelelehe' ilisave. O'moso'mo gozopo' aka'mila a'mine ve lihime ngemelesa line' nene hazamu' ma lamive. A'mine gamazi lokivo neine' nene okise ongamo ha neivo mo do goloso gehepeve o-ngedeleseive.
Ee, ingine gamazi gihile laminekumu' ngumo helamivo minani' nenako O'moso'mo asi've lavo ga'ine gili gopo ilisave. Gili gopo ilizani' ne'mo soza gamazilo' nene mudise gili ele'vole' ilisave.
Ne'mine noluvoni' nene mono' godolou' gamazi ma ti' li gizi nizani' nene lengito' vo davosa noluve: Zuda ve lengi' monovotine nene heta ato' ve ingine ningisa O'moso nene divi ledivi' iga' nave.

Ido' Halao' luso ve've seta' Zaneki Zabeleki ingine Mose' gamazi've di'mi limilisa asidi'mine igi noluve ingine mene gamazi gihile di'mi limilisa iga' nave. Ingine nene lu'ine ga'ine unuvo ogo goloso o vine' neivo mini ingine O'moso'mo gilivo lisihe' amine' monokumukovo' gili ele'vole' iga' nave.
Naza lu'ne ngeme nouvoni' aleve muki' nene ve'ine zopovo si'ze-ngedo ngelemo lihime ngemaa' nouze. Nemu' nene lingine monokumu' nene gilingili igi minisa lutine di velepe' izilo.

Nemu' nene ezemu' gele ele'vole' unidoti' nene O'moso'mo ve lisihe' ve lo-ledavo mino O'moso'mo lelikumu' izebolo' molani' nene mateline' aka Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' velavo ne'mo nene O'mososi lezesi vovoteu' nene gamazisi nomivo lamine' none.

Gei' monovokalokisi ido' evene' apize ngeme ngeme' iline' gamazilokisi nene ninge lamine' gehepeve o minezo. Gaza a'mine gamazilo' nene mo gi'mize gili' lo mineline' ne'mo nene gasika lukuvo nalinido' gele'mize molosa gei' gamazika gililizavesi nene lukuvo nalizado' ngele'mize molalosainaze. A'mine gamazilo' nene gi'mize gili' lo minezo.

nGebelekuvo Guvelesi ve Izesu'ni divi ledivi' ilizave lo Zuda veti mono' numuno'ine mukiku' gamene muki' ngebelaa' uvoni' ma neive. Ne'mine ogo engikumu' nizebolo' goloso do mino heta ato' veti numuno ebe'ningu' minangukisi goboni molo-ngedo minaa' uvoni' ma neive.

Ido' gomu' lemeni dameni goloso ne'mi monovo nene ha soto' ogo neine' nenako ne'mino neine' ma nene lingine mo gili ningani' ma neive: Vene' vemoho' alu gipe gopo' napa ongo'mo monaa' monovo ido' ne'mine monovo lute do goloso iline' monovo ato ato' ido' lovozo helamo a'mine monovo ato ato' nene evene' ve'nido' do soto' oga'
Ve ma monoku' mine zuho' oga' ive nesi ido' mine gizebo ve ne'mine nesi nene haza inite' ve. O'moso ei' hamo' gihile do soto' oga' neine' neevo' nene inite' naba goloso neive.

Ido' O'moso'mo ne'mino nasahili' o-lingidine' nenako nemu' nene Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' ogo soto' neivo ningelone' gamenemu' gizebo igi minangumu' nene monovo danava lamine' ato ato' O'moso'mo eze evenele lehize-ledaa' neinguti' nene lingine monovo danava hamokisi ma vise' isa'mave.

Ido' neloti' nene Okulumokuti' nolo naba ma soto' ine' nene giluve. A'mine nolo nene noso naba'mi gugu ne'minosa mino ido' go' ngilili naba'mi gugu ne'minosa minine' ve. Ee, a'mine nolo giluvoni' nene evene' mukilite ngita bili minaa' naani' ne'minosa minine' ve.

Ido' O'moso'mi gamazi've li soto' iga' ave mukilite eze gamazi've ne'mine li gizi milani' ma neive: Ezemu' gili amuzo milaliza aleve muki' O'moso'mo Izesungumu' ve lo lihime'ine apase-ngedeleseive lo Petolo' line'.

Ve ma ingine nene O'moso'mi monovo danava lamine' goloso neine' nene dalizangumukisi ido' ninge lamine' do-ngedo do naba o-ngedeline' nemukisi ido' helamaa' ngemeni dameni dalizangumukisi nene aka vise' ogo do soto' olone li geni initeli'mi lulou' minilizahe mulumo alumo initeli'mi lulou' minilizahe nemu' nene gilami gili huli geli geli igi monovo laminekovo' igi mili minilizani' nene O'moso'mo minevo' minevo' ngemeni dameni lehize-ngedeleseive.

Ne'mine likevo Paulo' ti' lo lo-ngimine': Zohane' aza nene evene' ingine lu'ine di velepe' izangumu' noso holo-ngedo ti' lo lo-ngimine': Mehe'nela ve ma nave. Ezemu' nene gili ele'vole' ilizani' o neive. Ido' ti' lo line' nemu' naza lo-lengemelove. A'mine gili ele'vole' ilizave nene Izesu' ve.

Ido' O'mosomu' ne'mine lo gele none' nenako nemu' nene laza ti' lo gelelesune: Guvelesi ve aza evene' lisihe' ngemengu' soto' o ngemelinguti' do ngu' izaa' monovomu' nene gele mino evene' goloso nene lihime'ine abeleni ogo ngeme'mo vo mino mukito' goni' o-ledeline' gamenemu' gizebo ogo lihime'ine do minaa' monovo nesi nene mo gele neive.

Vikedine'za ingine minani' misubo ivile' ogo minine' ebe' Okulumoku' neine' nela lu'ine nene vavo a'mine misubou' nene ha gopo minani' ve. Ido' ingine ne'mine igi minaa' ani' nemu' O'moso aza engi' O'moso'ine minine' nemu' nene O'moso'ine nouve loo lo soto' olosa ovozo helaa' ine' nevoba olize izo lo soto' oga' ine' ve. Ido' aza nene engi' alinge' miniliza numuno ebe'ine do soto' ogo molo-ngidine' nenako ne'mo nene engi' O'moso'ine minine' nemu' ovozo helamaa' ine' nene mo gele none.

Monoku' vo damine' gamazi heluno ne'mine gihile've nomine' getipe gamazi laa' nani' nene mehenga emaa' ozo. Ne'mine oga' noogosa monoto' monovo do hehe lovo' ogo molo iliningumu' nene ele'vole' ogo a'mine'mi gono've do ninge' ninge' ogo doka' doka' o'mo vo minezo.

Ingine a'mine misubo'mi gelengu' nene mine hutile' igi mini O'moso'mo lulo eme minine' numuno ebe' ado' eze evenele ingi monaa' ani' numuno ebe'ine Zelusalemi nene di vodo vodo i-di minani' ve. Ne'mine ani'za olo' ne'mo Okulumokuti' lemo do mikile' o-ngidine' ve.
Ne'mine lo Izesu' Kilisito' gulivelo' noso hilalo lavo mono' noso hili-ngidikevo ingine gamene ngomosi' Petolo' engita minelive li likevo ngomosi' ma minine' ve.
Ido' Izesu' aza inite' ma lehize-ledelove lo lo huko line' nene minevo' minevo' ogo minaa' lemeni dameni nene lehize-ledelove lo molo-lede neive.

O'mosolati' gele vevesaa' monovo di minave engi' monovo'ine nene ne'mino neive: Inite' naba nene lu'ningu' goloso initekisi nomivo lu'ine laminekovo' minaa' neive. Ido' a'midoti' nene ve hongu vevo' mini gelekele' igi evene' muhele'ine ningi di lamine' tamine' i-ngidi ido' evenekumu' gili mamu' ngumo hilivo mamu' gosele' ngibilivo ami di kegesi-ngidami mini ve'ine avileloti' soza lamilisave.
Meleho ne'mo nene gipele lulo eme osu' lo mino inite' mata' nene ei' anau' molo osu' lo neive.

Evene' malite Guvelesi ve alosa lo huko line' gamazi do gihile izelingumu' nene zou zou gohi lave li gilaa' nani' nene ladani igi gilikeve. Aza nene zou zou lamive. Asi evene' hamokisi vi tolovo ilizave lo gelamo mukito' nene lu'ine di velepe' izilizahoo lo lengikumu' nene goseleka lamo ha gizebo o neive.

Naza giluvoni' evene' muki' nene neni' uvodi'mine igi vene' dami hazavo' minilisave lo gele nouvoni'za O'moso ne'mo mino ogo molo olone' amuzote nene ato ato' lehize-lidine' nenako ne'mo ma nete nene na minuvodi'mine igi ngeli minamilisave.

Nemu' nene lingine evene' lutine ngimaa' monovolo' nene amuzo mili e'metilo. Ido' neloti' nene monoli'mi amuzo lingela nene ma dalone lisa amuzo milalo. Ne'mine niigi O'moso'mi veleti' gamazi li soto' igakumu' nene gilavo dizelive.

Ne'mine noluvoni' nene nemu' noluve. O'moso gozopo' aka'mila liti'muso izo miningu' labana' soto' ilive live ne'mo nene O'moso neni' nemeni dameni nene Izesu' Kilisito' veleloti' soto' neivosa a'midoti' nene ningi gililizangumu' ve losa luteu' nene hize labana' ele-lidine' ma neive.
Ido' Zuda ve ma minine' gulive Apolo' aza Alekisadilia ebeku' gidaveli'mo Eheso ebeta ogo heteline'. Aza nene gamazi gehe izo noso'vesivo' laa' ive mino mono' godolouti' gamazi nene gele osu' line'.

Ido' a'mine ize ne'mi vanise've nene O'moso imi sikizapovola nene di vi numuno ebe' heta gizi'votaa' ani' nenako ne'mo Izesu' aza ei' vanise'vedunu' eveneliti lihimete apase-ledo O'moso'mi evenele lolo' ogo minelonido' do lisihe' o-ledelesa Zelusalemi numuno ebeli'mi gesi gatedoti' lemo heta ogo mulumo gelo hiline'.
Haza ve nabe li gilikelizaze. Ne'mine gamazi lo-ngemo ga'ine do ngele'mize veveso amuzo molo lo-ngemezo.
O'moso'mo gipele hamo' leli' do lu' izo minevo' minevo' lemeni dameni do soto' o-ledelive me misubouko imiselavo lemo ani'. Nemu' nene O'moso'mo lulo limine' nene soto' ogavo ningekune.

Ahonoo, misubo mene olihe do soto' amosa luka nemosa nemu' amuzo atoli'mine ogo minine' nemaine' nene ningilizangumu' nene a'mine gei' do nemaine' evene' nene neni' mineloda nenikisi maka' minelone losa gele nouve.
Ido' zaa' zaa' akalo' vilizahe a'mida nene inite' mata' di goloso gehepeve iga' ido' evene' geni ngimaa' ne'mine iga' nave.

Ido' eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' ave nabalitevo' mono' numuno nabau' lavolavo izi hukikani' nene di veseme' ili O'moso'mi mo'mosi'vevo' ve langu' dizaa' ani' ne'mine ogo O'moso'mi gipele Izesu' aza eveneto' medelo mino O'moso inite' lehize-daa' ive nabate dizo minive lolo' ogo okulumo' ivile' ogosa hozila O'moso'mi mo'mosi've gehepeve neida Okulumokuko dizo minine' nenako nemu' monote gele ele'vole' une' nene do amuzo molo do ngi lo do minelone.

Ado' labana've naba' nabasi minivelati' gamazi ti' lo ezela limine' gamenela nene laza a'mida mino ningo gele minune' ve: Neni' vo'nelo' gipe'ne hamo me ve nene neive. Eikumu' nene naza lanite' lamine' nogiluve lo meleho O'moso'mo do naba o-do opo'ni line' ve.

A'mine ne'mine amuzo ato ato' muki' nene a'mine Sikalahu' hamo' ne'movo' nene do soto' ogo ei' lulolokovo' a'mine lemelesa gala giline' amuzo nene nani'mine amuzo lemelesa gilihe nene leli' evene' hamo hamo' nene ize' molo lemaa' neive.

Ido' neloti' nene angelo' naba fo ne'mo nene pikuli hubu lo do nolo molavo ho' nene laka'ni mili seto hamo minanguti' linge hamota nene belavo liti'muso izine' ve. Ido' a'mine'mine votigilelo' ike'ni mininguti' lingela nene belavo liti'muso izine' ve. Ido' a'mine'mine votigilelo' sonohi' linge setata nene ha nizasivo hamota nene belavo liti'muso izine' ve. Holise' hamoku' gamene seto hamo mininguti' linge hamota nene labana've nomine' minine' ve. Ido' a'mine'mine ogo liti'muso hamoku' ize gito seto hamo mininguti' linge hamota nene labana' ngomosi minamivo liti'muso gehepeve ize minine' ve.
Ne'mine ogavo evene' muki' mono' numudo' gizebo ve ma gulive Sositene'ni nene ele'mizi di vi goni' numuno velela bilivi' bilivi' igi minani'za Galio' aza ningo ninge huline' ve.
Ne'mine lavo ingine analo' do goni' o-delone li gohi ne'mine ilisa ani'za Izesu' aza engi' vovo'ninguti' nene hulo-ngedo vavo ingine di a'ningu' milamani' ve.
Ne'mine o neine' nenako nemu' nene laza gono daakumu' gosele' osa'mune. Ee, okode losuvola amuzote neve nene labuluvo olosa api' o'mo novivosi gamene gamene lute nene gosoho' oka' oka' o'mo novive.

Ne'mini nizavo Malia' nene oko'nido' hilaa' ani' uveli meni've dize minine' uveli nalida guvisedunu' gehepeve lili' ani' uveli nene botolo' naba gidini ma do ogo Izesu' gizenelo' leko holo-dosa godolo zopovodunu' nene gilite-dine' ve. Ne'mine neivo a'mine uveli'mi unuvo lamine' nene numungu' bizo minine' ve.

Ido' O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' oga' ive minine' ne'mo a'mine vozo lo-dine' misubolo' nene vo hetelo a'mida nene gopo venenga ve ne'mine gelo mino O'moso'mo a'mine misubo salani molo-lengedekuve lo lo huko-ngidive sita' ei' gipele Isakaki ido' Isaka' gipele Zakoboki nesi nene a'mida seli numungukovo' ingi monani' ve.
Neze zuhokizo, naza ogo molo oga' nouvodo' nene api'napi' igi mini leli' lengelebizuune' monovo ne'mido' e'meti igi mili minaa' avelo' nene ngamamaka mili ningi minisa nene a'mine'mine ilo.
Ido' geni initeli'mi lulou' minii ma nene ge hize ele' o-nede ne hize ele' o-gede li minilo. Ne'mine igi minilizani' nene Kilisito' lo huko line' lou' gamazi malo' nene mo e'meti osu' lilisave.

Nemu' nene O'moso'mo ningivo lihimete nomivo ve lisihe' minaa' noune' ne'mi monovo mo ningi osu' li nilisave. Ne'mi monovo ne'mino neive: Evene' haza gili ele'vole' iga' nanikovo' nene O'moso'mo ningivo lisihe' osa'mive. Ido' evene' ezemu' gili ele'vole' igi monovo lamine' nesi igi mili iga' nani' nene ningivo evene' lisihe' lihime'ine nomine' minaa' nave.
Ido' O'moso'mo nene ne'mine oga' neine' nenako nemu' nene nadive lolone. O'moso'mo oga' neine' nene mo lisihe' amive lolobe. O'ove. Mo keke' ne'mine ma lamolosune.

Ido' monoku' gilizevo igi minave ma lengita ikevo ma nene ha ngele'mizi milalo. Ido' ngele'mizi milalizani' nene ingine lingine gatine gilado' vo lisihe' amiline' ga'ine gili nilizangumu' nene lesisi igi gamazidunu' ge hulo ne hulo lilisamu' nene ngele'mizi milamilo.

Ne'mine ogavo angelo' naba Maikoli' ve ido' eze angelo'vesi nene sata' gele vine' loposo nite' naba nene lovo i imikevo a'mine loposo nite' sata' gele vine' nesi ido' eze angelo've zuhosi nene lovo hizi nizavo Okulumoto' nene lovo naba soto' ine' ve.

Ido' lengi' di goloso nii-lingidavo ma a'mido' golo hizi di goloso i-ngidamilo. Ido' a'mine'mine igi lengi' nene gamazidunu' gizi'voti gamazi ma nili-lingidavo ma nene a'mido' golo hizi lingine gizi'voti li-ngidamilo. Asi O'moso'mo lengi' vise lo do eita ine' nene eitati' nene no'noho' dalizave losa ne'mine ine' nenako nemu' nene ne'mine nii-lingidavo ma a'mido' nene O'moso'mo no'noho' ize-lingidivo lisavo' nene li-ngimilo.
A'mine nimiselive nene nenikisi maka' neive. Ee, naza ei' mulunou' lamine' geleline' initekovo' oga' nouvoni' nenako nemu' nene aza ninge mate nimikivo ma minesa'muve.

Ido' ne'mine igi lingine lovo hizi ngivile' ilizangumu' ve li ele'vole' igi oti mini gamazi laminetokovo' laa' monovo ne'mo nene gopotido' leti ne'mine lolo' ogo minavo ido' monovo lisihe' ogo molo minaa' ne'mo nene losodido' lepese ne'mine lolo' ogo minavo

Suno' minine' inite' ado' a'ne zamela nene sonohi' seveni do nouvo ningaine' ne'mi monovo nesi ido' ngolidunu' lili' ani' lamu seveni minine' ne'mi monovo nesi nene ne'mino neive: A'mine sonohi' seveni nene evene'ne mulise seveni neti angelo'nido' nene medeli avazaha ne'mine nene nizave. Ido' a'mine lamu seveni nene a'mine evene'ne mulise sevenilo' nene medeli avazaha ne'mine nene nizave.

Ido' ningo gelaa' noune' nene O'moso aza angelototi' gamene li'nibevo' lemeti' ogo minelive lo angelototi' do lemeti' ogo hulo-dive Izesu'nimu' nene ningo gelaa' noune. Ee, O'moso'mo nasahili' o-ledo evene' mukikumu' helelive lo imiseline' ve. Ido' a'mine ve Izesu' nene mulumo gelo hilingumu' ve lo O'moso'mo do hozi lo-doo Guvelesi ve lolo' o-dine' nemu' nene mo ningo gelaa' noune.

Ne'mine noluvoni' nene nanitekumu' ve. O'moso'mo gilivo lamine' iline' inite' olone li gilisa lingine a'mine inite' ilizado' nene do upuho' noo-lengedo asi've O'moso neve nene lengiku' omo mino gono nodave.
Gamazi mene nolo-lingimuvoni' nene lu'ne gulumo avile lisivo minaa' nouvoni' monovo nene lengitasi minivo a'mine ne'mo vai' lo lingibilivo minilizave losa noluve.

Do lu' izaa' ive O'mososi ido' lele'mize lamine' ilive ne neive lo gele medele minaa' unive Izesu' Kilisitokisi engi' nene Izesu' Kilisito' aposolo lolo' iline li lasido' lolo' uve neni' Paulo' luhuvo nite' meve nene

Ido' a'mine'mine ogo venelite e'metilizani' monovomu' lo-gemelove: Vene' neve nene evenelite ma ningilizahe ningamilizahe li madu'ine zopovo nalava izi di ma'mine ma'mine igi oko'nido' nite' meni've dizo minine' inite' ngilisa gonolise inite' ato ato' meni've dizo minine' ngalulu' nehe ngolidunu' lili' ani' inite' nehe nevo'mine inite' ngilami ha evene' do upuho' o-ngedamiline' inite' laminekovo' ngilaa' ilizani' nene lamine' ve.

Ningosa Izesu' aza naladunu' ngebeleline' gavoso ma lolo' ogo mono' numuno naba'mi gesi minguti' nene sipisipi ize'inesi bulumaka'inesi mukito' nene ngeleto do hulo heta ogo moni senisimi igi minaveti holomo nene do velepe' izo moni'ine nene do tululu lo hulo misubolo' o-ngidine' ve.

Ido' ne'mine noluvoni' nene O'moso'mo asi've gono dosa leli' do soto' o-ledavo none' nenako nemu' noluve. Aza nene leli' olihe do soto' o-ledamosa leli' nene monovo laminetokovo' e'meti minilizave losa gomukuti' gele minine' nenako laza Izesu' Kilisitoda gi'mizekunivo nemu' nene aza a'mine monovo lamine' nene igi mili minilizangumu' ve lo lemeni dameni gosoho' do soto' o-lidine' ve.

Lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' alevekizo, lutine do ningelesa lengemengu' molo ololi'mo longolaa' neine' ne'mino mulumo geni gihi-lingidilisa naavo lengi' soto' o-lengedelesa neingumu' nene lingine leli' soto' o-ledamilido' o neine' inite' atoli'mine ma soto' o-ledelesa neihe li upuho' amilo.

Sipisipi angale ne'mo eze zuho do eita iline' gamene mo ogavo a'mine eze zuho mulise neve nene eita volone li elenaho ne'mini gonolise igi di nene igi nizani' nenako nemu' nene laza muhele' ahele' amo lolize naba goloso izo mino O'moso do naba o-duke'zo.

Ne'mine igi O'moso'mo do lu' izaa' neine' ne'mo nene lovo angilitine ainidunu' lili' ani' ne'mine lolo' ogavo di gihi mini O'moso'mi gamazi ei' Sikalahu'veli'mo lengemaa' neine' ne'mo nene bainati mite' ne'mine lolo' ogavo di minilo.
Vo ninge neivo Aigita ve mali'mo Isilaele' ve ma do goloso o-do neivo ningo eze zuho alete molo-do Aigita ve'mo monovo do goloso o-dido' nene golo hizo a'mine Aigita ve nene bele hiline'.
Leze zuho mate, lingine gosele' lengebelamivo mini gono lamine' veveso lisihe' o mineline' gono ha di minilo.
Inite' mali'mo lutine nene do goloso ogalize. Ehe' igi mini mono' nemu' gatine sita sata' gilami amuzo mili gili ele'vole' igivo' minilo. Ido' ele'vole' igi vemoho' lili' igi oti pehe li minilo.

Lingine mono' numuno ado' seli numuno gele vine' di monani' nene avazaha o'mosotine Moloko'nisi ido' gohi ma sonohi' avazaha'vesi minine' Lehana'nisi ngopo'ni lilisa di monani' ma ve. Lolize izo a'mine inite' ngopo'ni lo minelone li avazaha inite' lili' igi di minani' nemu' nene na'nise lokuvo Kanaha misubo huli vi Babelonia misubo nesi huli misubo mauko vi mini mulumo gili minilisave line' ve.
Nemu' nene leze zuhokizo, veteti' gamazi lo-lingimune' nehe luhuvo nitekuti' lo-lingimune' nehe mono' gamazi apize lingimune' muki' nene amuzo mili di gili' li di minilo.

Ido' asi've O'moso'mo nene minevo' minevo' lemeni dameni ne'mo hele vaa' okode'mi ebe' nene dalingumu' ve losa leli' nene do va'va' o-ledosa a'mine salani molo-lidine' inite' muki' nene damolonivoba mo dalosune li ningi gililizangumu' ve lo a'minguti' gana' dalonido' o neine' inite' ei' Sikalahu've nene mo lehize-lede neive.
Vene' neve nene gelekele' gehepeve igi mini elese' iki mini gamazi nene di madu'ningu' milika' milika' igivo' minaa' ilizave.

Ido' evene' mali'mo mono' gizebo ve mamu' monovo goloso dave lo goni' o-delesa ma nolivo ma nene a'mine monovo goloso do noline' nemu' nene evene' sitape setohamo he ne'minete mo ne'mine ogave li hamo' gamazivo' gehepeve lamavo ma nene alamo goni' o-damolosane.

Lingine nene O'moso'mi evenelelite ilizado' o minine' monovolo' nene igi adingu' di ge nabuti' ize ne gabuti' ize li minaa' ilo. Ido' Kilisito' eveneleliti mulise mevola mini'mi monadite nene muki' longopo'ni nilave.

Ne'mine lii u'musupo gisi godo'nido' hiliisa geke' geke' li gisi ngisi mili ive nama igi ti' li lani' ve: Agae, agae, numuno ebe' naba ma laee. Guvo nosolo' sipi di monave muki' nene ei' a'mine numuno ebe' Babelonia nelati' heneni nganeni di moni' moni' igi moni heneni ve lili' iga' ani' maho. Idise nene mo gamene hamo' maukovo' inite' muki' nene tava li di hulikevo mo golosolo' molavo mulumo gele-dekune li lani' ve.

Vekizo, Meteho lulo atoli'mine ogo leme neine' nene gili nizahe. Ee, lulo atoli'mine ogo limidoti' nene izipaha'ne zuho ve lo lo-ledaa' neive. Ido' lamine' izipahala zuho none. None'za me misubou' ve O'moso gelekele' i-damani' ingine nene O'moso ningi gilamani' nenako lezesi a'mine'mine igi ningi gilamaa' nave.

Ido' mono' gizebo ve gono'ine neivo ha iga' naani' ne'mine igi goso'velite ilizani' o neine' inite' nesi nene mo ne'mino neive: Lingine nene gizebo vetinelite lilizani' gamazilo' nene ha gili ngimisa minilo. Ido' mono' godolou' O'moso'mi monovo ma ti' li gizi nizani' ma neive: Evene' ma oko'ine di dizi minaa' nave nene O'moso'mo biluva' o-ngedaa' neiha evene' ma engi' oko'ine di'mi limi minaa' nave engi' nene ninge lamine' o-ngedo nasahili' o-ngedaa' neive. Aza ne'mine oga' neine' nenako nemu' nene evene' muki' lingine okodine di'mi limi mini ge gelekele' o-nede ne gelekele' o-gede li minilo.

O'ove. E'metamilivoba asi a'mine gamazi'velo' nene ha mo e'meteleseive. Evene' vai' nene sozalo' vevo' minilisaha O'moso neve nene gamazi gihile laminekovo' laa' ive mineleseive. Ne'mine neingumu' nene mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizani' ma neive: Ne'mino neine' nene nanitekumu' ve. O'mosoo, gaza gamazi lisihekovo' liline' o neine' nene mo soto' neivo goniku' nesi nene gasika ngivile' olosane lo neive.
Ido' eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' ave naba nete gei' guliveka di nizave nene na'nava ngemo ngele'mizo vilive li li-di luhuvo nite' gizi imikevo ogo mela neive.

Ne neiha gomu' nene O'moso'mi eveneleliti vovo'ningu' nene soza polohetesi soto' igi minaa' ani' ve. Ne'mine iga' ani' ne'mine igi lengi' vovotingukisi nene soza mono' apizi lingimilizave soto' igi minilisave. Engi' nene monovo'ine di haleki mini lengele'mize goloso ilido' o mineline' soza mono' nene li soto' igisa engi' meni hize-ngidive Guvelesi ve nesi nene mehe'ine imilisave. Ido' ne'mine ilizadoti' nene O'moso'mo upuho' nite' ngiso do goloso o-ngedeleseive.

Ne'mine lavo Zuda veti ve naba'ine nete Izesu'ni bililiza akamu' nene gohi amuzo goloso milisa vise' igi minani'. Ido' ne'mine ani' nene nanitekumu' ve. Ingine holisekumu' lou' milani' nene Izesu' avuto' ogave li neemukovo' nene bililiza akamu' vise' igi minani' nevoba asi've Izesu' ne'mo O'moso nene neni' me'neho gehepeve ve line' ne'mo nene ei' Izesu' nene O'mososi do lisihe' ogosa lave liisa nemukisi nene bililisa gohi nabisa amuzo milave.
Lingine nene naza apize lengemo lo-lingimuvoni' initekumu' nene e'meti gili minaa' nani' nemu' longopo'ni lo do naba noo-lingiduve.

Davidi' ezemu' ti' lo gizine' ve: Guvelesi ve nezesi gamene gamene minaa' neive lo a'mine nene ga'neu' soto' o neivo naza gele minaa' uvoni' ve. Aza inite' mali'mo do goloso o-nedalive lo neni' a'ne zamela minaa' neive.

Lingine nene lengemeni dameni gosoho' ogavo gohi soto' ani' ve. Ido' gohi soto' ani' nene helosa osu' lilive'mo zuho molavosa nevoba asi helosa osu' lamaa' neive'mo zuho molavosa gohi soto' ani' ma neive. Ee, minevo' minevo' ogo mino minevo' minevo' ogali'mi monovo do soto' o-ledaa' neine' inite' O'moso'mi gamazi ne'mo lengi' lutingu' gono dadoti' nene lengemeni dameni do gosoho' ogavo gohi soto' ani' ma neive.

O'moso'mo do lamine' o-lengedelingumu' ve li lihime di mini' mini' ani' nene ingine li soto' avo lingine li soto' avo di bizi O'mosola li ge numuna lo-nede ne numuna lo-gede laa' ilo. Ve lisihe' vevesi minavete O'mosola lilizani' nene amuzo malehe inite' neive. Ne'mo O'moso'mo gelavo inite' gihilevo' soto' oloseive.
Naza mo lamineto' gehepeve nolo-lingimuve. Gili ele'vole' ilizave muki' nene minevo' minevo' minaa' ngemeni dameni nene mo di nizave.
Naza hulo-lengedo voloni' nene lingine mudise muhele' izipe ne'mine minilizave losa hulo-lengedamolosuve. Naza nene lengita gohi alosuve.
Ne'mine ilisaha inite' lamine' vai' goloso vauve elosa lelita neive. Inite' naba gana' nene O'moso'mo lo huko lo-lidine' gamazi've nene Zuda ve leli' nene di minilizave losa lehize-lidine' ve.

Ido' gonou' ve lingine nene Kilisito' gamazi lido' gili di minani' gilivosa me misubouko gizebo i-lingidaa' navetine nene evene' nabate nizave li engikumu' lengehelele izivo mini lutine mili hamo' gehepeve i mini lilizado' gili di gelekele' i-ngidi minilizave.

Ido' ma nene ti' li gilaa' nahe: O'moso'mo isetine izo nasahili' o-lengede'mo ogo minaa' neine' ne'mo do akalo' o-lengedavo lutine di velepe' izi monovo goloso hulilizave losa nasahili' o-lengedaa' neingumu' nene lingine ha gililizanako gili hulisa O'moso'mo atoli'mine ogo nasahili' o-lengedo geto lihime lengemo lengebelamo isetine ize'mo vo minaa' neine' nemu' nene lingine gilavo haza nite' lolo' ogahe.
Laza ti' lo O'moso'mi velelo' gele olobo' o none: O'mosola inite' mamu' voku' lunivo ei' gele neido' vo daline' nene gele lemeleseive.

Ido' lukuvo naloningumu' nene gele mu'musi' oga' monovo do soto' ive O'mosomu' nene gili ele'vole' igi nizavo aza lavo muludingu' nene gulumo avile atoli'mine ogo lisivo hongu gehepeve lo neivo O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo lukuvo nalizangumu' nene gili mu'musi' ilizani' amuzo nene lengemavo ne'mo vauve ilisa gili mu'musi' igi minavoo.
Ido' a'mine Izesu'ni lohoto' zalo' biladaa nene za zuho ma miningu' nene evene' hamokisi ma mili-ngidamani' gonoso galese nene ma minine' ve.

Ne'mine igi mo lovo hizikeni' neine'za loposo nite' nesi ido' ezelo' medelo ato' suno do soto' oga' idi'mo evene' a'mine loposo niteli'mi maki've di mini avazaha'velokisi gubi' izi imi opo'ni laa' ave ngele'mize gopo ive soza polohete nesi nene ngivile' igisa di-ngidani' ve. A'mine ve seta' nene diisa ve'inesi haza nizasivo salfa gehenilo' olo' lo mino noso ohuno ne'mino molo miningu' nene di huli-ngidani' ve.

Mo ne'mine igi langisetine nene lihime ngimamilisaha mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizado' nene e'metilisave: Lengi' biluva' i-lingidaa' nave ingine ga'na hili nizavo ma nene di ve'ine milalo. Ido' nosomu' ga'na hili nizavo ma nene noso ngimilo. Lingine ne'mine i-ngidilizani' ne'mo nene ngovozo naba goloso nene engita dizavo olo' vele nene godo'nido' mili-ngidani' geleleseive.

Kilisito' gamazi've nene lutingu' vauve goloso elosa mine molo minivo minilo. Ne'mine igi otohato gamazi gehepeve li ge apize neme ne apize geme ido' ge hungo' molo neme ne hungo' molo geme lisa mono' nama ato ato' mono' godolouti' mono' nama nehe idise a'mene laa' naani' mono' nama nehe ido' O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo lo soto' ogo lo-lengemeline' mono' nama nehe neeve nene li O'moso nene isaa' neve li a'mine nama nene lutinguti' gehepeve li-imaa' igisa minilo.
Ido' vemoho' lengi' nene eledingine lutine ngimi mini gosele' ngebeleline' inite' i-ngidamilo.

Ido' Kilisito' evenele mali'mi zuhou' nene vene' gevono' ma nizavo ma engi' hize ele' o-ngedaa' gono nene mono' mulise gehe-ngedamo asi've nene hize ele' o-ngedo vise' ani' inite' ngemo minelive. Ne nanitekumu' ve. Mono' mulise ne'mo nene guhalihali igi minaa' naani' vene' gevono' nene hize ele' o-ngedaa' neine' nenako hize ele' i-ngidilizani' inite' vise' ikelizave losa nemu' nene a'mine engi' zuho asi've hize ele' o-ngedelive lo noluve.
Ido' gipele hize ele' o-do line' gamazi nene ti' lo neive: O'moso'mo minevo' minevo' oga' lemeni dameni nene mo leme neive. Ido' a'mine minevo' minevo' minaali'mi meleho nene ei' gipele ne neive.

Nemu' nene ingine O'moso'mi gipele di gili' li nizani' nete nene minevo' minevo' oga' ngemeni dameni nesi di nizave. Ido' ingine O'moso'mi gipele di gili' li di minamave nete minevo' minevo' oga' ngemeni dameni nesi mo damave.
Nemu' nene O'moso'mi gipele naza lihime monovoli'mi gelekele' ve minanguti' do kuluhize-lengedeloni' nene mo mudise haza gehepeve minilisave.

Ido' O'moso'mo gono nimidoti' nene inite' lamine' ne'mine soto' oga' neine' nenako nemu' nene naza ti' lo nolo-lingimuve: Naza lengi' lengele'mize lamine' olosa gono do minuvoni' ma'mo goboni mili-nidi nala' numungu' huli-nidikevo geni initeli'mi lulou' nouvoni' nemu' nene geni lengebelamivo minilo. A'mine geni initeli'mi lulou' nouvoni' nene lengikumu' ve losa nouvoni' nenako Paulo' lelikumu' gelavo dizave li neloti' lingine ningi gili longolize izilizado' o neive.

Nene nanitekumu' ve. A'ne'mine ve ingine nene Guvetesi ve Kilisito'nimu' gelekele' iga' navoba asi engi' oko'nine ne'mo lanite' giline' initetokovo' nene gelekele' iga' nave. Gamazi lanite' ine' gamazi soza saza gamazi lisa ingine golosomu' gilamaveti lu'ine nene golo izi ngele'mize gopo iga' nave.

Ne'mino ninge mate-ngedavo evene' ingine lisihe' amine' monovo danava goloso vai' lihime daa' monovo nene engita vai' goloso soto' ivo minani' ve. A'mine monovo goloso nene ne'mini nizave: Mumuzo' iga', evenekumu' lukehe iga', evene' mala inite' lamine' ma soto' o ngemavo ma a'mine vemu' ngizebolo' gohi molaa', evene' ngibili hilaa', lolize hizaa', evene' go'ine izaa',
leliku' omo minive O'moso'mi Sikalahuto' nene lehete o mino O'moso'mo gono lamine' gimido' nene gizebo lekeseve o minosa do minezo.

Ve ma ingine gomu' ngemeni dameni goloso'mi monovolo' igi mili ilizani' nene a'mine gomu' ngemeni dameni goloso'mi gihile've nene mudise vo ladise oga' nene dalisave. Ne'mine ilisaha O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mi emeni damenilo' e'meti igi mili minilizani' ne'mi gihile've nene a'mine O'moso'mi Sikalahutati' nene minevo' minevo' oga' ngemeni dameni nene dalisave.
Ido' Guvelesi vesi golo izikevo satalite ngibilikevo hilani' nenaze. Laza ingine adi'mine ogo Guvelesi ve golo izamolone.
Ido' evene' lute ngemaa' noogo ma hokolize' o-ngedamo mino ledenihe minamo lizebolo' molamivo mino lihime mili lidikevo ma a'minemu' gelamo minelesune.

Ido' loso'nido' lepese ne'mine izikani' nene ainidunu' lili' ani' gele vine' izikani' ve. Ido' a'mine inite' pateli nivavo holoke'ne'ninguti' nolo molani' nene hosi vailite lovou' kali ma gelelehe' igi loti' izi di nivavo gilili ngilili lo minaa' neine' ne'minosa minine' ve.

Ido' naza ma amo gamazi'ne nene ma lo-ngemamuvodiniko nenikumu' gili hulamavo lihime nene engita mo minamivo minadine'za idise nene ingine laza lihime nodune lo gelamo gopo minune li e'menga lilizani' aka nene ogo hize tile-ngedekuvoni' nenako olovo' ma amilisave.

Ido' lingine nene gopo moni minamii evene' ado' Izesu' evenele lili' ami heta minave nene nanite' di-ngidilizahe a'minemu' nene gatine gili nge li mini monovo laminekovo' i-ngidi evene' hize ele' i-ngidiliza gonotine lamine' soto' iline' nene mo diivo' minilo.

Laza ti' lo gele none: Lihime monovo goloso ne'mo okodela gono daa' ine' nene osu' lavo laza lihime monovolo' gohi gelekele' ogo minamoloningumu' nene lemeni dameni litehe nene Kilisito'nisi lohoto' zalo' bili nizani' ma neive.

O'moso'mi izipahala zuho ido' Satani'mi izipahala zuho engi' monovo danava ti' lo do kegeso ningelesune: Evene' ma ingine hehe li lamine' minamilizani' nene ingine O'mosolati' soto' igi minamave lo ningelesune. Ido' a'mine'mine ogo evene' ma ingine evene' muki' lu'ine ngimi nasahili' i-ngidamilizani' nene ingine O'mosolati' soto' igi minamave lo ningelesune.

A'mine lemeni dameni liteheli'mo gilido' e'metaa' ne'mo nene O'moso'mi lou' gamazi'mo lido' nene gele damo mino gele daline' amuzo'vesi nomivo mo keke' ngelo gele damoloseinako ne'mo nene O'moso biluva' o-daa' do soto' oga' neive.

O'ove. Ne neine'za O'mosomu' gilamavete soza o'moso ngimani' inite' nene O'moso imaa' naavoba sikalahu' goloso ngimaa' naanako nemu' nene sikalahu' goloso ngimani' initekuti' nisa lingine maka' gi'mizi minilizave losa gelamuve.

Izesu' evenele zuho ma Adiokia ebeku' minani' nete vovo'ningu' O'moso'mi gamazi li soto' igi apizi ngimaa' ave linge minani' nene gulive'ine Banabasi' ve ido' Simeoni' ado' gulive gohi ma Gonobu' ve lo minine' nesi ido' Lukio' aza Kilene ebekuti' ve ido' Manaeni' aza guvelesi ve Helodekisi uvoloho akunolo gili gana gana naba asive nesi ido' Saulokisi ve.

O'moso'mi gamazi gili disa'mave nete nene a'mine ne'mine monovo goloso daa' nani' nenako nemu' O'moso izebolo' molavo lihime ngemeline' nenaze. A'mine ne'mine monovo goloso nemu' nene gotine izi soza saza gamazi nili-lingimavo ma nene a'mido' gili ngimamilo.

Ne'mine iga' ave nete evene' linge ma vene' izipaha'inesi muki' nene ngele'mizi gopo iga' nave. Ee, ingine go'ine izekunivo moni limilizahe li gili lamilizado' o minine' gamazi nene li ladanga mono' apizi ngimi ngele'mizi gopo iga' nave. Ido' ne'mine iga' nanako nemu' nene engi' gamazi do'mo lemoo o've lo-ngedelone.
Lengi' nene mo guluvi' li lamine' nizaha lengi' vaito' nene ne'mine amave. Vaito' guluvi' amave line' nene eze biluvaliti a'ningu' do molo-delivemu' nene ha gele minine' nenako nemu' live.

Izesu' imine' molo ti' lo line': Naza lamineto' ti' lo nolo-lingimuve: Ve ma ingine sipisipi izeliti gesi minguko dizilisa nene gatenguko dizami aka atota gesi goholou' dizaa' nave nene mo a'mine sipisipi gizebo ve'ine minami gizengize ve goloso nizave.

Ingine aka lisihe' nene huli vi gopo igi nimonani' nene Bosole' gipele Balaamu' vine' akalo' nene e'metikeve. Ado' monovo golosoloti' meni dalingumu' umo hilive ma'mi monovolo' e'metikevosa nene noluve.
Ne'mine ikevo alinge' nene misubo me'ningesi Zuda vesi ido' engi' gizebo vesi di nubo igi aposolo divi ledivi' igi geheni hulo hulo' ogo ngebelelone li li hukani'.

Ido' gohi gamene sitohamo' ivo ti' lo lo-imine' ve: Zohane' gipele Simonizo, gaza nene mo luka neme nabe. Ne'mine lo luka neme nabe neme nabe gamene sitohamo' line' nemu' nene geni belavo ti' lo line' ve: Guvekasi ve, gaza nene inite' mukikumu' nene ha gelaa' naine' nenako naza lu'ne geme nouvoni' nemu' nene ha gele nane. Lavo aza ti' lo lo-imine' ve: Sipisipi ize'nelo' nene noso' nite' ngemo gizebo ozo.

A'mine numuno ebeku' nene goloduvo ele vine' inite' hamokisi ma dizamoloseive. Ee, lovozo monovo nehe soza monovo nehe nevo'mine monovo igi mili iga' ave nene a'mine numuno ebeku' dizamavo asi sipisipi angale'mi buku've ado' minevo' minevo' ngemeni dameni dalizaveti gulive'ine neine' bukuu' gulive'ine gizikave engikovo' nene a'mingu' dizilisave.

A'mine vene' nene genegana gulehe' ngenge'nisi ido' gumi kala pepoli ve laa' nani' gulehekisi minine' ado' meni've dizo minine' genegana nene ngolo mino ido' gonolise've ato ato' meni've dizo minine' inite' ado' ngolidunu' nehe gulehe' kalehe' gehenidunu' nehe ido' ngalulu' laminedunu' nehe nevo'mine initedunu' nene gonolise ogosa minine' ve. Ido' anau' ngolidunu' lili' ani' kapu ma do miningu' nene vaini noso ne'mino ovozo monovosi pasidia' monovo've golososi nene vai' lo minine' kapu do minine' ve.

Ido' lingine ne'mine mana'mine inite' igi mili minaa' naani' nene ngivile' ivosa inite' naba nene lutine ngemaa' monovo nene di otuhi igi mili minilizave. A'mine lute ngemaa' monovo ne'mo nene monovo lamine' muki' nene asabu' ize neivosa laminovo' minelonido' do hamo' o-ledaa' neive.
Li-imikesivo a'mido' Izesu' ti' lo lo-ngimine': O'mosolati' ve gihile neni' nene di hozi li-nidikevo Guve'nesi ve mineloni' gamene nene mo avito' ogave.

Ido' vene' vemoho' lili' ikeni' nete vene' vemoho' masi gopo ingamilo laa' noogosa gei' nene ne'mine oga' noolosane. Gaza soza o'mosomu' nene muso gaka dizavo olovo' oga' noogosa soza o'mosoliti numunguti' inite' gumine oga' noolosane.

A'mine lou' gamazi ne'mo nene aka velo do upuho' o-davo lihime monovo ne'mo nene mumuzo' oga' monovo muki' nene vauve elo lu'neu' do soto' o-nidine' ve. Ee, lou' nene ma minamidiniko lihime monovo ne'mo nene ogo molo monaa' initekisi ma amo hilive ne'mino haza minidinako nemu' nene noluve.
Zuda veti a'ningutikisi ido' heta ato' veti a'ningutikisi do gu' ize-gedo minelesuve. Ne'mine ogo a'mine heta ato' vetida nogimiseluve.

Lazasi gozopo' nene a'mine'mine ogo negi hizo ladani ogo gamazi gele hulo gopo minune' ve. Ne'mine ogo inite' goloso ato ato' lumo helaa' ine' ido' lanite' gelaa' une' inite' nemu' gelekele' o-do mino evene' igi mili iga' nani' ne'mine ogo molo mineloninako lo gituho' no mikile' oga' une' ve. Ne'mine ogo nonivo evene' muki' biluva' i-lidi minikevo lazasi biluva' o-ngedo minaa' une' ve.

Gaza lo-giduvoni' gamazi mene e'mete gehepeve iline losa naza O'moso'mi velelokisi Izesu' Kilisito' velelokisi ido' O'moso'mo do kegese-ngidine' angelo'veti ve'nidokisi nene nolo-giduze. Goni' gamazi'ine olihe gele-ngedamo bubu izo mo lamineto' lihime dikeve ido' damave lo mo lamo ido' goniku' sisitemi nesi nene mo amo goni' neve nene mo monovo lisihetokovo' do molo gele-ngedelesane.

Ido' gonolo' ve ngele'mize milavemu' nene ngele'mize milavete ti' li gilaa' nave: Gote izami lunidokovo' e'meti gono di minilizani' o neive. Ne'mine li gilaa' nani' nenako nemu' nene Guvelesi ve'mo eze gonolo' gizebo ve lele'mize molani' nenako lelikumu' nene ne'mine lo gele noloseive.
Ne'mine ikevo Petolo' nene ve ma gulive Simoni' aza ize losuvo do lamine tamine' oga' ive ei' numungu' maka' Zopa ebeku' gamene ha'na minine'.

Lingine muki' nene do nubuho ogo O'moso'mo neni' kekeize numu'ne ve lavo ei' Sikalahu've nene lengiku' mino molo neive ma nene nizave. Lingine a'minemu' nene gilamani' nevoba mo gili nizani' ma neive.

Nemu' nene neze zuho lingine Izesu' vanise lepo helo O'moso imine' ne'mo lihimete nene mudise apase-lidine' nenako nemu' nene golise gelamo O'moso'mi kekeize atoli'mine lo minine' numuno lulou' nene ha vo dizelonido' o neive.

Ido' Izesu' aza gohi ti' lo lo-ngimine': Naza mo lengi' hulo-lengedo volosuve. Ne'mine okuvo lingine nenikumu' vise' igi minilizaha mo ningami mini lihimetine apasamo ha neivo hililisave. Ido' neni' ningamilizave noluvoni' nene nanitekumu' ve. Neni' voloda nene lingine ngeli vamilizani' ogavosa noluve.

Ne'mino neine' nenako nemu' nene lingine O'moso'mo lengi' nene do kegeso do eita ogosa lulo lengeme neive ei' evenele nizani' nenaze. Lingine me'mine monovo nene di otuhi igi mili minilo. Ado' muludine hukavo evene' mulumo'ine ningaa' monovosi ido' nasahili' o-ngedaa' monovosi ido' okode do lemo minaa' monovo nesi ido' muludine laminekisi hongu lo minaa' monovo nesi ido' lingizebolo' molani' inite' ikevo ma goloso gelamo zou lo minaa' monovo nesi nene di otuhi

Ve ma ingine neni' gono'nelo' gelekele' ilisa ilizave nene neni' mo ne'metaakovo' ilizado' o neive. Ne'mine igi mini ingine nene naza zaala zaala minelohe inginesi nene makakovo' minilisave. Ve ma ingine neni' gono'nelo' gelekele' ilizave muki' nene neni' me'neho'mo do naba o-ngedeleseive.
A'mine ve nene ei' vene' izipahala zuholo' gizebo lamine' ogo ngele'mize akalo' oga' neivo a'mine izipahala ingine me'nibinemu' gilavo dizavosa peleseve' izami gamazi'velo' gili daa' ave minelive.
Nemu' nene lutinedunu' ge hize ele' o-nede ne hize ele' o-gede li lutine di amuzo mili mini monoku' ge do amuzo molo-nede ne do amuzo molo-gede li idise iga' nani' ne'mine i diivo' vi minilizave.
Nemu' nene mono' gamazi api' ogo gilunidoti' gamazi ti' lo gele'mo gele'mo ogo minune: Laza lute ne geme ge neme lo bizo minelone.

Nemu' nene ti' lo gele nouve. Idise a'mene api' ogo soto' o-lengede'mo novine' geni inite' ne'mi lulou' nizani' nenako nemu' velo' vami ido' vene' dami haza minani' aleve ingine minani' ne'mini hazavo' minilizani' nene lamine' oloseive losa gele nouve.
Ido' ve ma minine' gulive Nikodemo' nene Halisaio' mono' laa' aveuti' mino Zuda veti kanisoleliti muliseuti' ve mino ve naba ne'mine minine'.

Ido' a'mine'mine ogo pasidia' vene' Lahaba' aza monovo lamine' ogavo O'moso'mo ezemu' gilivo lisihe' ine' ve. Isilaele' aleve Kanaha misubo dizi dalisa nizavo guve'inesi ve Zosuva' aza evene' ma misubo amamaka' mili ningilizave lo ngimiselavo vi a'mine Kanaha vene' Lahaba' neida vikevo aza ngele'mize numu'veu' molo Kanaha evene' nete ningi ngibilikelizave lo aka atota ngimiselavo vani'.

Ne neiha vene' ingine Guvelesi vemu' gele mu'musi' i mini lu'ine ngemaa' monovolo' e'meti mini ido' lihime monovomu' olovo' i mini vene' lamine' gehepeve gili mini nizavo izipe gidaa' ilizangu' nene lukuvo ngemeleseive.

O'moso aza Isilaele' aleve lezemu' eze zuho minilizave lo avotemotine do kegese-ngedo Aigita misubouko venenga ve gili nizavo do amuzo molo-ngedo neivo hizi hutile' ani'. Ne'mine ikevo goboni mili-ngidi minanguti' amuzo molo ngele'mizo ebe' hadivelo' novivo
Ne'mine ogavo O'moso luteu' ningaa' ive'mo Zuda ve leli' eze Sikalahu' limine' ma'mino heta ato' ve nongemo ninge goloso o-ngedamaa' ine' monovo nene lelebizine'.
O'moso'mo vene' longo' amilo ido' evene' ngibili hilamilo nesi line' ma neive. Nemu' nene gaza vene' longo' amaba evene' ma bele heleline' ne'mo mo lou' gamazi avuto' oga' anive lolo' olosane.
Naza minevo' minevo' ngemeni dameni ngemekuvo ingine mo keke' vi tolovo igi hahasi mo amavo evene' malitesi ipe' igi a'neuti' ma di vamilisave.

Ne'mine ikevo hongu lo lamino minaa' monovo do soto' oga' ive O'moso ne'mo nene mine ha'na amo hize ele' o-lengedo neivo Satanisi ei' zuhosi ngivile' gehepeve igi lingine lisi hupi' izi-ngidani' geleleseive. Guvetesi ve Izesu' nasahili've nene lengita minivoo.

nevo'mine mana'mine monovo nene mo ha di soto' ilisave. Ido' mono' nene vi gilaa' ilizaha oko'ine losuvolotikovo' gili mini mono' nene lu'ningu' amuzo molo gihile've do soto' ilingumu' nene o've li monoli'mi amuzo nene vasa izilisave. Nemu' nene gaza a'mine ne'mine mana'mine vesi nene bizami olovo' ogo minezo.
A'mine'mine ogo Kilisitoda nene evene' muki' laza oko'no hamo' ne'mine lolo' ogo ato ato' minamo ne hize ele' o-gede ge hize ele' o-nede lo minelonive nene none.

Gamazi mene gihile lamine' line' ne neive. O'mosomu' gili ele'vole' igi nizave ingine ga'ine hamo' gili inite' lamine' ato ato' evene' hize ele' i-ngidaa' ne'mine nene amuzo mili igi mili minilizave loo luvoni' gamazi mene amuzo molo lo-ngemeline lo nogiluve. Gamazi mene lamine' neinako evene' muki' hize ele' o-ngedelido' o neive.

Ne'mine ogavo mono' godolou' minine' gamazi ma nene gihile izine' ve. A'mine gamazi nene ne'mino neive: Abalahamu' aza O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ine' nemu' O'moso'mo gelo Abalahamu' nene lihime've nomive ve lisihe' ve line' Ido' evene' ingine ezemu' O'moso'mi zogo ve neive li lani'.
Neze zuho mate, lingine labana'vesi minive Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito'nimu' gili ele'vole' i nizanako evene' di kegesi evene' mamu' siza li-ngidi evene' mamu' ningi hulaa' nani' nene nanitekumu' ve.

Lu'ninguti' vomine gamazi laa' nani' nene gonoso galese ngolo' lo mininguti' unuvo goloso oga' neine' ne'minosa nene neive. Ido' gamazi laa' nani' nene evene' go'ine izisavo' nene laa' nave. Ido' sata' ume nete evene' ongovuso' ngibilaa' nani' ne'mino ingine gamazi laa' nani' ne'mo nene ngebelaa' neive.

Ido' a'mine'mine igi vemoho' nete lengi' okodinemu' gilaa' nani' ne'mine igi lengi' eledinginemu' gili lutine ngimilizado' o neive. Ve ma ingine ele'ningine lu'ine ngimi minaa' nave nene mo engi' oko'inesi nene ne'mine nii-dave.

Ne'mine ogo neine' nenako neloti' nene laza ti' lo gelelesune: Ve lisihe' lili' ilizani' akamu' vise' amave heta ato' ve ma nete a'mine aka nene ningi ikeve. A'mine aka nene ezemu' gele ele'vole' okunivo O'moso'mo ve lisihe' ve lo-ledaa' neine' akamu' nene noluve.
monoli'mi suno' gamazi O'moso'mo do soto' o-lede neine' nene di mini mono' gili nizado' nene ha e'metivo' minisa engi' lu'ningu' monovo goloso minivo ningisa'mave minilizave.

Ido' ve ma gono gihi-ngidaa' ave gizebo ve'ine nene gili ele'vole' ave nilizani' nene engito' gono daa' ave nete nene a'mine gizebo vete nene Izesu' evenele leze zuho neive li gilisa engikumu' gilavo lemavosa gonou' nene alaha' alaha' igi dikelizave. Asi leli' gono dunidi'mo hize ele' o-ngidive nene Izesu' evenele leli' zuho lute ngimunive nene nizave lisa gono engito' dalizani' nene gohi ma amuzo milisa di mini gelekele' lamine' gehepeve i-ngidilizave. Mene noluvoni' gamazi nene e'metilizave lo ga'ine do apize ngemezo.

Ne neiha Zuda ve linge ma nete nene a'mine O'moso'mo lehize-lidine' gamazilo' nene e'metamani' ve. Nemu' nene ve malite nene ti' li longo' ilisa gili nilisave: Ingine gamazi'velo' e'metamani' nemu' O'moso'mo a'mine gamazilo' e'meto amilido' o neihe.
Izi ledamani'za asi ami engikuti' mali'mo nene gohodunu' Izesu' losono gahevela nene hizo ngolosavo a'minguti' nene vanisesi nososi nene lite' losa limine' ve.
Neni' gamazi ma lo huko lo-lingiduvoni' ma nene ne'mino neive: Naza lu'ne lengi' lengeme nouvoni' ne'mine igi linginesi nene ge luka neme ne lu'ne geme livo' minilo.

Lingine okodidoti' gizedine adine ne'mine nehe nanitetine nolihe inite' hamokisi nene goloso nite' dalive li lihime monovoli'mi gono daa' inite' ne'mine nene lolo' i-damilo. Asi hiluninguti' nene otosa gosoho' lemeni damenilo' minevo' alevo' ogo none' nenako nemu' nene laza okodelati' gizede ade nevo'mine nehe ido' nanitete nolihe neve nene O'moso'mine emekunivo ei' gono daa' ine' inite've ne'mine lolo' ogavo monovo lisihe' laminekovo' ilive lii okodine muki' nene O'moso imilo.

Ne'mine lo line'za laza nene evene' ma ingine gili ele'vole' igi mini di vanguti' olovo' igi velepe' izi vii vi tolovo iga' nave ne'mine evene' minamo laza nene gele ele'vole' ogo mino mine do dizo minaa' lemeni dameni do minelonive nene none.

neloti' nene mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizado' nene e'meto Isilaele' aleve muki' nene do ngu' izeleseive: Isilaele' aleveti goto' numu'ine Zaioni gololoti' nene do ngu' izelive ma soto' oloseive. Soto' ogosa aza mono' gelamaa' monovo Zakobo' a'vopilemo' zuho Isilaele' alevetingu' minine' nene do huloloseive.

Zuda ve ingine neve gozopo' O'moso'mi gamazi li soto' iga' ave polohete nene ngibili hilani'. Ido' a'mine'mine igi Guvelesi ve Izesu'ni nesi bili hilani' ve. Ido' leze libili ga' limiselani'. A'mine Zuda vemu' O'moso'mo gilivo lamine' amine'. A'mine Zuda ve nete evene' muki' numudo' namado' ve nene lovo i ngimi minaa' nave.

Ido' laza Kilisito' gamazi've gihile laminekumu' nene mo gelo e'meto minaa' noolonivete lihime daa' initekumu' nene mo amolone' inite' neive lamo lihime doso' ne'mo Kilisito' vanise've lepo helo lihimete apase-ledeline' aka vele-lidingumu' nene o've lune' geleleseive. Ido' laza lihime daa' akalo' gohi volone' ne'mo O'moso'mo lihimete apase-ledeline' aka nene Kilisito' vele-lidingumu' nene o've lune' gelavo a'mine lihimetemu' golo hizo O'moso lehize-delone' inite' gohi ma minamoloseinako a'mine lihimete nene O'moso'mo ha do mineleseive.

Ne'mino mino laza nene goloso initete ne'mo lutesi mo hele vivo minune' gelavo minune'za O'moso'mo leli' mulumote gelo isete vauve elo izaa' ive minosa lulo atoli'mine ogo lemaa' neine' nenako nemu' nene Kilisito'ni aza hilinguti' do ote-dingu' nene goloso initete ne'mo lelikisi hilune' gelavo noninguti' nene makato' do ote-lidine' ve. Ido' Kilisito'ni nene Okulumokuko do dize-do evene' nabalitevo' minaa' ani' mo'mosito' ele'mize molangu' nene lelikisi a'mine'mine ogo do dize-ledo a'mine ne'mine mo'mositelo' lele'mize molani' gelave. O'moso'mo ne'mino do lu' izine' nene inite' mamukisi nomine' asi mo leli' do lamine' o-ledelove losa do lu' izine' ve.

Nemu' Kilisito' evenele laza okode do hamo' ogo noninguti' nene okode lingela lingela ne'mine mino vaito' bizo none' nenako nemu' mukito' lingine soza saza laa' monovo nene huli evene' ma gamazi li-ngimilizani' nene mo laminetokovo' li-ngimilo.

Ee, ingine nete heta ato' ve nene oko'ine lolovo huki huli-ngidi Zuda ve lolo' i-ngidilizave li amuzo mili lani'za laza ingine Izesu'nimu' gamazi lamine' nene di gopo igi li-lingimikelizave lo a'mine gamazilo' gizebo lamine' okunivo gamazi gihile nene lamine' ha minelive lo engi' gamazilo' nene mo gele ngemamune. Ee, gamene ngomosi nene mo keke' gele ngemamo Tito'ni oko'no lolovo nene ma huko hulo-damune.
Nemu' nene ve ma nolo atokuti' mono' gamazi lo soto' oga' olo ma nene alinge' do velepe' izo evene' gililizado' lo-ngemelingumu' nene do velepe' izo lo-ngemaa' amuzomu' nene O'mosola lilive.
Ido' Saulo' Izesu' evenele zuho ngebelelesa lovo gani lo minine' nene hulamo lovo' mino

Ido' idise nene naza mo geita nouve. Ido' naza me misubouko ha mino vekisine mene gamazi mene nolo-ngimuvoni' nene ingine lu'ningu' gulumo avile lisivo minaa' monovo nenitati' nene dikevo engita vai' lilive losa nene nolo-ngimuve.

Asi Kilisito' mulumo geni gihine' ne'mine nene linginesi gihi nilizani' nenako nemu' nene lingine Kilisito' labana'vesi gohi soto' iline' gameneu' nene luteu' gulumo avile lisivo mino lolize naba izeloningumu' ve li longolize izi minilo.
a'mine'mi lulou' gisili hizo ninge lamine' uvoni'. Gaha nama ato atoli'mine gize'ine a'ine neine' nominekisi ninguve.

Ne'mine igi minani'za idise a'mine nene hulisa ma me'mine monovo nesi nene hulilo: Ado' lingizebolo' mala' mala' nesi ido' evene' singehe' goloso minaa' nesi ido' lukehe lakehe oga' monovo nesi ido' dovo ledevoka laa' monovo nesi ido' gamazi goloso laa' nesi nene mo mudise hulilo.
Azasi inginesi hamo' gono di seli numuno gizaa' ave minani' nenako engi' numungu' dizo mino gono makato' di minani'.
Nemu' nene okodine heleline' akalo' mine molo neine' ne'mo nene lanite' gelo dalosa giline' goloso nite' nene mo di minilizave lo lihime monovo ne'mo nene do eita ogo do gelekele' o-lengedalize.
Evene' a'ne'mine ve Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' ei' velemu' ogo ga'ine do ti' lo nolo-ngidune: Ingine dalupizi mini engi' gono'nine di engitatikovo' nalizave.

Ne'mine ogavo a'mine avotemote ingine naku'ine ma Zosehe'nimu' livile' ogalinako li lukehe bili evene' ma ngimisa ei' oko'noloti' meni dani'. Dikevo a'mine ve nete ele'mizi Aigita misubosuko vani'za O'moso'mo Zosehe'nisi mininako ne'mo

Heteli engikuti' ve ma gulive Agabo'ni nene O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo do ote-davo misubo mukiku' ga'na naba soto' olosa neivo ne'mi gamazi lo-ngimine'. Ido' alinge' Kalaudio' Loma veti guve'inesi ve naba lolo' ogo neivo a'mine ga'na naba soto' ilingumu' line' gamazi gihile izine'.
Paulo' ti' lo lo hulo ezesi inginesi obuvo'ine hizi O'mosola lani'.

Ido' Kilisito' evenele zuho laza gomu' lemeni dameni golososi ido' a'mine'mo goloso initekumu' umo helo lanite' gelaa' ine' monovo'vesi nene mo lohoto' zalo' bele hilune' gelavo a'mine monovo danava goloso nene ogo molo amo minaa' noune.
Nemu' nene liti'muso monovo golosou' nomonosasi laza ezesi do hamo' ogo bizo none lo lolone' nene sozasi lokunivo ogo molo olone' nene inite' gihile nomoloseive.
Okulumo' ne godavo inite' ma lavolavo naba gidini minine' ne lumolati' lumolati' di uhu'vizi hulikevo misubola zou zou lo nolimivo ningine'.
Laza misubo ato atokuti' none. Palatia ve ido' Mede ve ido' Elame ve ido' Mesopotamia misubouti' ve ido' Zuda ve ido' Kapadokia ve ido' Podo ve ido' Asia ve

Guvelesi ve'mi evenele minilizani' votigilelo' mini mili mini Guvelesi ve'mo ninge lamine' daline' monovolokovo' nene e'meti minilizave. Ne'mine ikevo ne'mi gihile nene gono lamine' ato ato' muki' di nizavo O'mosomu' gili vevesaa' ani' monovotine nene naba o'mo vo minelive.

Gipe'ne Timoteoo, a'mine gono gamazi mene nolo-giduvoni' nene gei' monovoka do soto' ogo O'moso'mi veleti' gamazi ma gozopo' soto' ine' mamu' nene gele mino nolo-giduve. Ido' gaza a'mine gamazilo' mene noe'meto monoli'mi lovo lamineku' nene lovo hizeline losa nolo-giduze.

Neloti' gohi ma giluvoni' Okulumoku' nene evene' vai' golosolite gamazi nilani' no'ine naba ne'mine giluvoni' nene ti' li nilavo giluve: O'moso opo'ni nolune. A'mine O'mosote neve nene leli' do lu' izaa' ive mino Guvelesi naba mino amuzo ve neive.

Ido' lingine Zuda ve minamavesi gomu' monovo goloso palasa di soto' igi ido' lihimetinesi ve minaa' adi'mo lutine nene mo hele vine' gelavo minanguti' nene O'moso'mo Kilisito'ni hilinguti' do ote-dingu' nene linginesi makato' do ote-lingidine' ve.

Ido' Guvelesi vela gi'mizi mini lebeni noso've naa' niigisa sikalahu' golososi vi gi'mizi mini sikalahu' goloso ngimani' nosouti' nene nalizado' nomive. Guvelesi vela gi'mizi mini holomo'veloti' noso' nite' naa' niigisa sikalahu' golosola vi gi'mizi engi' holomolo' noso' nitekuti' nalizado' nomive.

Ido' vene' vemoho' gipe alu gopo ingaa' monovo ido' ne'mine monovo lute do goloso iline' monovo ato ato' nesi ido' inite' gohi gohi dalisa gilaa' monovo nene O'moso'mi evenele laza ogo molo amolonido' o neine' nenako lengi' vovotingu' a'mine monovo nene ngomosi mo soto' ogalize. A'mine inite' goloso nemu' nene li volelo' melo' igi gohi di gatido' milamilo.

Ingine inite' mamu' nene di gililizanipe di nalizanipe ne'mo lutine goloduvo eleleseive li laa' nahe. Naza lo-gemelove: Evene' lu'ine lamine' o noline' nene inite' mata' do lamine' o-ngedeleseiha evene' mono' gili huli mini lu'ine goloso o noline' nene lu'ine ga'ine ngemeni dameni goloso ine' nenako nemu' nene inite' mata' do lamine' o-ngedamo gohi do goloso o-ngedeleseive.

Ti' lo lo-ngemavo line' gamazi gilave muki' gopo ga'ine gili ti' li lani': Ve meve nene Zelusalemi ebeku' a'mine line' gulive laa' ave ngele'mize goloso palasa oga' ive ma nehe Olo. Aza nene mela ogo galapuso ngemo eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' ave nabala ngele'mizo volosa ani' ma neive. Nadi' ogosa eze monovo've do velepe' izive.

Ido' eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' ave ingine gomu' gono daa' ani' nene Okulumokuko gono gihile minine' ne'mi avazahalo' nene daa' ani'za Izesu' nene a'mine gono gihile nene nodavo ne'mo gomu' daa' ani' gono nene ngivile' ogo hozila neive. Ido' gomu' aleve lo huko-ngidine' gamazi neu' nene O'moso'mo inite' lamine' o-ledelesa lo huko-lidine'za leli' lo huko-lidine' gamazi gosohoku' nene ivile' ogosa inite' lamine' goloso o-ledelesa lo huko-lidine' nenako Izesu' aza lelikisi O'mososi kuku holo-ledo gamazi hulo eza ema ogo leli' gele dalone' gamazi ve lo O'moso'mo lo huko-lidine' gamazi lo do ogo limine' ne'mo O'moso'mo gomu' aleve lo huko-ngidine' gamazi nene ivile' ogo neine' nene gele none. Ido' a'mine votigilelo' a'mine'mine ogo Izesu' gono do neine' ne'mo misubouko eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' avete gono di minaa' ani' nene ivile' ogosa lamine' neive.

Nenikumu' ne'mine noluvoni' nene neemu' noluve: Naza minevo' alevo' ogo mine do voloni' nene Kilisito' nenita mine molo neivosa eikumukovo' nene minevo' alevo' olosuve. Ido' helo voloni' ne'mo nene minevo' alevo' ogo mineloni' nesi ivile' ivosa lamine' golosou' vo minelesuve.

Naza lengikumu' nene ti' lo gele mu'musi' o nouve: Lengiku' api' ogo gono lamine' nodave O'moso ne'mo nene gono do do vo neivo Izesu' Kilisito' aline' gamenela a'mine gono nene vo pele gehepeve oloseive.

Ido' ti' lo gele none: O'moso'mi gipele aza misubouko lemo ogave. Ogo gate do ngolo' lo-lidine' nenako O'moso gihile nene ningo gelaa' noune'. Ee, O'moso gihile nesi bizo none. Gipele Izesu' Kilisitokisi bizo none. Me ve nene O'moso gihile ido' minevo' minevo' ogo minaali'mi meleho neive.
Lingine evene' ato ato' mukikisi lovo lolize ami hongu li laminivo' minilizani' aka ma neivo ma nene a'mine akalokovo' nene e'meti minilo. Lengitati' neve nene lovo lolize di soto' amilo.

Ido' O'moso'mo inite' muki' ha olosuve line' inite' nene mo lamineto' oloseive lo mo gele none' ma nenako laza gele ele'vole' ogo O'moso'mo lemelove lo lo neine' initekumu' gizebo ogo minaa' noningumu' lo soto' oga' noune' nemu' nene golise gelo hulamo do gili' lo do minelone.

Ido' mo hulo-lengedeloni' o neine' nenako haza hulo-lengedamo hongu monovo nesi nene nohulo-lingiduve. A'mine hongu monovo nene me misubou' alevete hongu monovo di soto' iga' nani' ne'mine minamo nenitati' atoli'mine ogo minine' hongu nene nolingimuze. Lingine lengemeni balala livo mini goliselo' ve minamilo.

Nemu' nene laza gamene gamene vode vosa'mivo lute amuzo molo minivo ti' lo gele minaa' noune: Laza nene okode meesi ha mino Okulumo' numudela minosa Guvelesi vesi maka' minelonidoti' nene hoto' haza none.

Ido' ve ma ingine neni' laa' nouvoni' gamazi gilisa gili dami minaa' nave nene na'nise'ne lihime ngemesa'muve. Ee, naza me misubou' uvoni' nene evene' ize' molo-ngedo lihime ngemelesa amo do ngu' izelesa uvoni' nenako nemu' nene na'nise'ne lihime ngemesa'muve.

Gozopo' vomila minive Kaini' aza ine' ne'mine amolone. Aza nene ve goloso Satani'mi gipele lolo' ogo akunoloine bele hiline'. Ido' bele hiline' monovo nene nanitekumu' bele hilive. Ei' Kaini' ogo molo minine' monovo've nene goloso o vivo ido' nakunolo'mo ogo molo minine' monovo've nene lisihe' lamine' minine' nenako nemu' bele hiline' ve.
Ido' ailani muki' nene vi haha ikevo golosi nene limi ingi osu' li gohi ma minamavo ningamani' ve.

Ne'mo Abalahamu' eze nene mo ozoho molo vani goloso molo minidoti' nene a'vopilemo' mukiliti avo'nibo lolo' ine'. Ei' hamokuti' nene a'vopilemo' vai' goloso soto' igi okulumoto' sonohi' ne'mine ido' noso gahevela gepe ne'minisa soto' igi evenelitesi gati nanike' nilizahe li ningamilizado' ne'mine minani' ve.

Ogo voka' voka' iline' gamene mukito' Guvelesi ve naba minive helamaa' ive ado' evenelite ha ningelonido' amive O'moso hamo' minive nene do hozi lo opo'ni lo minevo' minevo' ogo minelone' nene oku' lamilihoo. Ne'mine ilihoo.

nolo nabauti' ti' lo lo-ngimine' ve: O'moso'mo evene' goni' o-ngedo lihime ngemeline' gamene nene mo ogaze. Lingine nene O'moso'mi golise've gili mini di naba i-di mini a'mine Okulumokisi misubosi ido' guvo nososi ido' noso hinipini' mukikisi do soto' ive nene gelekele' i-di opo'ni li minilo.

A'mine gameneu' nene Izesu' evenele zuho mo imine' mili'mi nivavo engikuti' evene' ma ado' nGiliki eveneliti gamazi'ninguti' laa' ave nete ti' li li mulu'ningu' goloso gilani'. Gamene gamene noso' nite' ize' mili ngimaa' angu' leze muliseuti' minani' geto' vene' ne ningi huli-ngidi noso' nite' mili-ngidisa'mave li mulu'ningu' goloso gili Zuda veti gamazi'ninguti' laa' ave ngelemilisa lani'.

Ido' ne'mine ilizave lo noluvoni' nene O'moso'mo ne'mine ilizave lo elese molo lengele'mize molani' nenako nemu' noluve.
