Ido' O'moso'mo ne'mine ine' nene Kilisito' azasi lingine neni' ogo molo uvodo' api' napi' igi igi mili minilizave lo avazaha pikisa ne'mine bele molo lengito' medelo mulumo gono gihine' nenako nemu' nene O'moso'mo linginesi ne'mine ilizave losa elese molo-lengedave.
Ido' lengita minune' gameneu' ti' lo lo huko lo-lengemaa' une': Ve mali'mo gono dalosa gelamivo ma noso' nite' malise i-dikevo namilive.

Ido' Izesu' ne'mine line' nene nemu' line' ve: O'moso'mo me misubou' ve lulo limine' nene atoli'mine goloso ogosa lulo limidi'mo ei' gipele nene mo hamo' gehepeve minine'za ve ma ingine eikumu' gili ele'vole' ilizave nene vi tolovo ami minevo' minevo' ngemeni dameni dalisave losa a'mine gipele hamo' nene lehize-lidine' ve.

Ne'mine li sikalahu' goloso mamu' vozo likevo sikalahu' goloso aza do velepe' izo ti' lo lo-ngimine': Naza Izesu'nimu' gele nouve. Ido' Paulo'nimukisi mo gele nouve. Ne'mino neiha lingine zamote nizave.

Ne'mine lavo gohi ma ninguvoni' nene a'mine gomu' ninguvoni' loposo nite' masi ido' misubou' misubou' guve'inesi ve naba' naba' nesi ido' engi' lovo hizaa' ani' ami'inesi nete nene a'mine mokono' hosilo' minivesi ido' ezesi maka' minani' ami'vesi nene lovo i-ngimilisa di nubo naavo ninguve.

Anau' milikevo ngele'mizo vo sipiu' nazasi maka' dizune. A'mine sipi nene Adalamitio ebetati' ogavo a'mine sipi nene Asia misubou' guvo noso gahevela numuno ebe' vai' minido' vilive likevo dizo vune'. Ido' Makedonia misubou' Tesalonika ebekuti' ve ma gulive Alisitako' nene lezesi maka' vune'.

Ido' Izesu' evenele ma nala' numungu' huli-ngidikevo minangu' nene lingine engikisi makato' nala' numungu' mini mulumo alumo gili nizani' gilivosa engikumu' gili mini hize ele' i-ngidi minilo. Ido' lingine ha vetinesi mini olihe ma hili vamanako lengikisi nene a'mine'mine igi goboni mili-lingidilizani' nene agae ma hize ele' i-lidavoo li minilisanako nemu' nene goboni mili-ngidavo minaa' navemukisi nene gili mini hize ele' i-ngidi minilo.

Lingine gono dalizangu' nehe gamazi lilizangu' nehe nadi' nadi' ilizahe a'mingu' nene Izesu' aza lengi' Guvetinesi ve miningumu' nene soto' ogo minelido' di milisa igi mili ei' Izesu'nimu' nene melehine O'moso isaa' neve li-di minilo.
Ido' mono' gilaa' nani' aleve lingine a'mine mono' apizi lingimaa' nave nene lengitati' inite' matatine lamine' nevo ma nolinguti' nene ize' mili lingela ngimilo.

Ogavo do goto' misubo lolo' ogo minamine'. O'moso'mo misubo ngomo ha nitekisi ma emamine'. Ee, misubo ma emamine'za azasi ido' a'vopilemo' zuhosi di minilizani' misubo ve lo salani gamazi lo-emo a'mine misubo lengemelove lo lo huko lo-dine' ve. Ido' a'mine ga'vopilemo' zuhosi lengemelove lo line' gameneu' nene Abalahamu' aza izipahala ma nomivo minine' ve.
A'mine Aigita ve aza leze zuho go'ine izo do goloso o-ngedo hililizave lo izipe namuno heta di huli' hulikovo' i-ngidilo lavo di huli' hulikovo' i-ngidaa' avo hilani'.
Ne'mine lavo Petolokisi ido' Izesu' izipahala ma nesi gonoso galesela vilisa di aka milasine' ve.
Ido' O'moso'mo ningavo ido' evene' ningikevo neze lu'ne gamene gamene laminekovo' veveso minelive lo neze monovo'nelo' gizebo laminekovo' ogo minaa' nouve.

Ido' engi' neve nene hepe' naba elo guvo noso velo gituho' galakala' ogo noso hemuvoloti' pipia' do ogo gahevela hutile' ogo hulaa' neine' ne'mine nene minaa' nave. Ido' ma nene sonohilite vilizani' aka'ine hulisa zovo' izi mala vaa' naani' ne'minisa nene nizave. A'mine soza mono' apizi lingimaa' nave engi' nene vi liti'muso atoli'mine gehepeveu' minevo' minevo' ilizave lo O'moso'mo salani molo-ngede neivo engikumu' ha gizebo o neive.

Neze zuhokizo, naza Kilisito' gamazi've lamine' lo-lingimuvoni' mamu' lo-lengemeloze. Gililo. A'mine gamazi nene evene' malitidati' giluvoba evenelitesi apizi nimamavo Izesu' Kilisito' asi've lo soto' ogo lo-nimine' ve. Nemu' nene evenelite di soto' milani' gamazi nomive li gililizave losa nolo-lingimuve.

Laza lemeni dameni litehelo' e'meto minune' gamenela nene laza lihime monovomu' lanite' gelaa' une' monovo nene lou' ne'mo do ote-davo okode mukita gono davo a'mido' e'metunidoti' gihile've nene helaa' akalo' mine molo minune' ve.

A'mine gamazi nene lo soto soto' ilinive aposolo lolo' iline lo O'moso'mo nele'mize molani' ve. Naza ne'mine noluvoni' nene mo sozasi lamuvoni'za mo lamineto' gehepeve noluve. Aza nene evene' heta ato' ve gamazi gihile lamine' apize ngeme ngeme' oga' anive lolo' ogo nanivo ingine gili ele'vole' ilizave losa nele'mize molani' ve.

Ido' lo-huko line' gamazi nene gele do noolonive laza O'mososi bizo lamine' maka' minekunivo O'moso aza luteu' minevo dovo' ogo minaa' neive. Ido' eze Sikalahu' lehize-lidine' ne'mo lo-lemavo O'moso aza luteu' minevo' dovo' neive lo gelaa' noune.
Evene' hamo hamo' lingine nene lengi' okodinemukovo' gilamisa lengi' zuho neemukisi gili mini evene' ngele'mize lamine' ilizangumu' amuzo mili minilo.

Lingine lengi' hamo hamokumu' nene di dizi limi gilami asi hamo' monovolo' nene di milisa minilo. Ee, lengi' okodine nene di dizami asi evene' limi minavesi nene bizi monilo. Ido' la'mo nene otohato ve none li okodine di dizamilo.

Ido' muludingu' ekese' goloso gelaa' ido' muludingu' olo' laa' monovo ido' lingizebolo' molaa' monovo ido' evene' geke' goloso li gotinguti' li-ngimaa' monovo ido' evene' divi ledivi' igi ngemenga laa' monovo ido' ne'mine mana'mine monovotine goloso muki' nene ogo molo ogalone li olovo' igi minilo.

Ee, O'moso'mo neni' nene lengikumu' gono doo a'mine gonolo' gizebo ve mineline lo gono nimido' do molosa a'mine Kilisito' evenele zuho mulise'mi gonolo' ve nene lolo' ogo nouve. Ido' ne'mi gonolo' ve lolo' ogo nouvoni' nene O'moso'mo ei' gamazi've nene lo-ngemo osu' gehepeve liline losa lo-nedavo nemu' nene gonolo' ve lolo' o nouve.
Ido' godolo zopovo nene mokono' hego gehepeve elo minavo vele gulo nesi nene olo' gulumo ne'minosa minine' ve.

Ido' laza ne'mino mulumo alumo geni inite' geho none' nene ha lengi' lamine' ilizangumu' ve losa nene ne'mine ogo none. Ido' ne'mine ogo none' nene O'moso'mi nasahili' ne'mo evene' mukita nene voka' voka' ogovo' neivosa a'minete nene O'moso opo'ni lika' lika' i'mi viivo' nizavo eze guvele nene vo naba goloso o'mo vo minelive losa nene ne'mine oga' noune.
Ve ma ingine neni' me'mele'nesi vanise'nesi ma nalizave ingine nene nenita mini mili nizavo naza nene inginela mine molo nouve.

Ne'mine lavo Mata' aza ti' lo lo-imine': Guvekasi ve, naza mo gele ele'vole' o nouve. Gei' nene O'moso'mo do lu' izelesa gimiselelesa live ei' gipele me misubou' aloseive lave ma nene nane losa gele nouve.
Ne'mine ogavo gamene gamene amuzo mili di gese' igi gili hamo' igi aposolo apizi ngimani' gamazi gili haza noso' nitekisi lebeni initekisi ni O'mosola li minaa' ani'.

Gaza nene monovo lisihe' laminetokovo' luka molo mino goloso inite' daa' monovomu' gosele' gebelavo mehenga emaa' nane. Ne'mine oga' nane' nenako O'moso gei' O'mosoka ne'mo eveneka ngivile' ogo gaza golize izo mineline lo a'mine mo'mosito' nene gele'mize molave.
ei' lavo Zohane' uvoloho Zakobo'ni luvono gitani'.
Evene' malite haza mono' gihile nomine' gamazi laa' nani' nene gele hulo mehenga emezo. Ne'mine gamazi li'mi vaa' naadi'mo nene mono' hulilizado' mini milikevo

Malite evene' mamu' mulu'ningu' goloso ogavo lukehe ngibili minaa' nave ingine nene evene' ngibili hilaa' ave nizani' gelaa' neive. Ido' evene' ngibili hilaa' avemu' lingine mo gili nizave. Ingine minevo' minevo' ngemeni damenisi minamave.

Noso' nite' ni osu' likevo Izesu' aza Simoni Petolo'ni nene ti' lo lo-imine' ve: Zohane' gipele Simonizo, vekise mete lu'ine nimani' nene ivile' ivosa luka neme nabe. Ne'mine lavo aza ti' lo lo-imine' ve: Guvekasi ve, mo lamineto' lane. Lu'ne geme nouvoni' nene mo gasi gele nane. Ne'mine lavo Izesu' a'mido' ti' lo line' ve: Sipisipi angale'nelo' nene noso' nite' ngemo gizebo ozo.

Luvoni' ne'mino neine' nene neloti' ningo gelelesune. Ve ma nene Sikalahuli'mo hize ele' o-divo mono' gamazi nene otohato gamazi laa' neive. Ido' ve gohi ma nene a'mine Sikalahu' ne'mo mono' monovo gelaa' amuzo nene lehize-davo laa' neive.

Ido' gohi Aigita misubola vani' gameneu' nene ingine Zosehe'nimu' Aigita ve nehe li ha gili nizavo aza nakunotine Zosehe' ma ne nouve lo uvolomotine lo-ngemo Halao' neida ngele'mizo vavo engikumu' nene Zosehe' zuho ve lo Halao' ningo giline'.

Mene nolo-lingimuvoni' gamazi neve nene mono' godolou' gamazi ti' li gizi nizani' malo' nene vo nodave: Ve ma aza minevo' alevo've lamine' minivo laminekovo' mine do dizelesa gelelive nene vele'mo gamazi gosoho' nasaha' lo gamazi goloso lalive lo velelo' nene gizebo lamine' ilive.
Ido' gili ele'vole' igi minani' aleve ingine lu'ine ga'ine mili hamo' igi inite' mata'ine di minani' nene gei' initeka ve neni' inite'ne ve lami mukito' inite'ine di minani'.

Ido' gomu' lo-lingimuvoni' mono' gamazi lamineli'mi monovomu' gohi lo-lengemelove luvoni' nene nemu' luve: Mono' gamazi lamine' gana' api' ogo gelo do go'zekuvonikovo' nene lo-lengemo neuti' nene dizo minine' gamazi ne'mino ve lo ti' lo lo-lingimuvoni' ve: Mono' godolou' Kilisito'nimu' gizado' e'meto leli' lihimetemu' hiline' ve.

Ido' a'mine Babelonia numuno ebeku' aleve ado' O'moso'mi evenelesi polohetesi ngibili hilikevo vanise'ine lepani' ne'mi lihime nesi ido' misubou' misubou' evene' ngibili hilika' hilika' ani' neti lihime nesi nene mo engita soto' neinako mo sime' nalisave.

Ti' li likesivo heta ato' ve ingine gili mulu'ningu' lamine' gili O'moso'mi gamazi'vemu' opo'ni li sizaga li-dani'. Ne'mine ikevo minevo' minevo' ngemenisi minilizave lo O'moso'mo gelo do gizeka' ine' aleve ingine gili ele'vole' ani'.
Ido' me bukuu' gizuvoni' gamazilo' hize ele' ive ne'mo nene ti' lo nolive: Ee, lamineto' naza mo geto alosuve nolive. Mo ne'mino miniliho. Guvekasi ve Izesuvo gaza ano.

Ido' neni' apize lingimuvo nenitati' dani' monovosi ido' neni' noluvoo gilani' monovosi ido' ningi nizavo ogo molo uvoni' monovosi nene lingine di gono veleu' mili igi mili minilo. Ne'mine ikevo hongu lo lamino minaa' monovo do soto' o-ledaa' neine' O'moso ne'mo nene lengikisi mine molo minelive.
Nene biluva' i-dilizave losa lamuve. Leze zuho ve li gala di di vevesi i-dilo.

Evene' hamolitesi gotine izi gihile've nomine' gamazimu' nene otohato gamazi lamine' ve li lengele'mize gopo igi a'mido' di gelekele' i-lingidikelizaze. Ehe' igi ningisa minilo. A'ne'mine gamazi li-lingimilizani' nene Kilisito' gamazilo' vo daline' gamazi li-lingimilizavoba asi haza evenelite ne'mine mana'mine initeliti monovomu' nene avotemotidati' li di dizani' gamazivo' nene li-lingimilisave.

O'moso'mo Izesu' Kilisitoda mine molo mino Okulumoku' hozi minevo' minevo' oga' iline lo elese molo-nidine' nene do gihile izo meni'ne ne'mine a'mine Okulumoku' minevo' minevo' oga' nene dalove losa daloni' makila nene amuzo molo loti' izo vo nouve.

Aza neve goloso nite' gozopo' do'mo vune' akaloti' do tine' molo lele'mizo ogo do lu' izelesa lelikumu' ogo hiline'. Ee, lihime'ine apaso do lamine' o-ngedekuvo neze zuho lili' igi mini lu'ine a'mida mili inite' lisihe' laminekumu' amuzo mili gili igi mili ilizave lo lelikumu' ogo hiline' ve

Naza mo lamineto' ti' lo nolo-lingimuve: Ve ma ingine neni' gamazi'nelo' gili di mini nimiselivemu' gili ele'vole' i-di minilizave nene minevo' minevo' minaa' ngemeni dameni nene mo di ti' ikeve. A'mine ve ingine nene gonito' vi otami asi lu'ine hele vivo minadoti' nene upuho' igi ve'ine gizikeve.

Ido' a'mine maka' gamazi lo-nemo minine' angelo' ne'mo nene a'mine numuno ebeku' gateni'vesi lave'vesi nene molo ningaakumu' ve lo maki molo ningaa' inite' angaba gavoso ne'mine ngolidunu' lili' ani' nene do minine' ve.

Ne'mine igi mili minadoti' gihile've soto' iline' nene vo tolovo oga' ne neive. Engi' O'moso'ine neve nene oko'ine'mo lanite' gelaa' neine' inite' mata' muki' nete nene lili' ikeve. Ingine ngovozo hililizado' o neine' initekumu' nene oko'ine di dizi mini lu'ine nene me misubou' initetokovo' mili minaa' nave.

A'mine mono' muliselo' gizebo ve nene monoku' olihe lodive amive evene' gosoho' ne'mine ele'mizi milalizani' nene ne'mine i-nidikeve loo oko'no do dizavo O'moso'mo Satani lihime molo-do mulumo gono emelesa neine' ne'mine ogo lihime molo-do mulumo gono emaalinako olihe monoku' lodive amive evene' gosoho' nene mono' gizebo ve lili' i-damilizave.

Lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' alevekizo, naza O'moso'mo nenikisi lengikisi do lu' izine' monovomu' nene luhuvo nite' ma gize-lengedeloho lo amuzo molo nogiluvodo' mene O'moso'mo eze evenele mudise levo levo lo mineline' mono' lehize-lidine' nene lingine zege' zege' igi hizi ele' ilizave lo luhuvo nite' lutine do oto ma gizeloni' ogavosa mene nogizuve.
evene' apizi ngimi O'moso'mo Izesu'ni hilinguti' do ote-dine' ne'mine ogo evene' masi do ote-ngedeleseive li lasingumu' gili goloso igi

Naza lihime ngemelesuve noluvoni' nene engi' lihime'ine nene eheto' eheto' mili'mi dizi vani' nene mo Okulumokisi do gelo neivo O'moso ne'mo a'mine goloso nite' dani' nemu' gala nogiline' nenako nemu' nene noluve.

Ne'mine ikevo Izesu' aza nGalilaia misubou' numuno ebe' ma Kana neu' gomu' haza nosodunu' vaini noso lolo' ine' numuno ebeta nene gohi vine' ve. A'mida vo neivo Kahanaumi numuno ebeku' nene guvelesi ve mali'mi gonou' ve naba ma minine'. A'mine ve'mi gipele nene inite' gize do minine' ve.
Monoku' mini gonotine di di vi minaa' naani' nene gosele' lengebelamivo mini Guvelesi ve nene lutine gilingili ivo gelekele' i-di minilo.

Izesu Kilisito'ni nene lingine mo ma ningamani'za lutine imi minikeve. Ido' idisesi mene oko'nolo' ma ningami nizangukisi nene ezemu' gili ele'vole' i mini lutingu' gulumo avile lisivo longolize izi minani' nene laza evenelitesi ngelo monovo ma lamolonido' o minine' longolize ado' Okulumokuti' atoli'mine ogo minine' ma ne neive.
Ido' O'mosola bizo none' ido' O'moso'mo luteu' minevo' dovo' ogo neine' nene ningo gele none. Ido' naniteli'mo ningo gele none. Eze Sikalahu've leli' limidi'mo nene ningo gele none.

Ne'mine lavo a'mida gomise ma minine' a'mingu' vaini noso ekese' ine' nene vai' lo neivo nosou' lupizisa lipi naa' ani' inite' ma disa lupizikevo vai' lo neivo hisopu ve laa' ani' gavosolo' hizi di dizi velelo' mili-dani' ve.
Ee, liti'muso melehi amuzolo' mino gelekele' o-do minuninguti' nene do lu' izo hulo lulo eme neine' gipele'mi gizebou' o-lede neive.

Neze zuhokizo, gatine do naza amuzo molo ti' lo nolo-lingimuve: Ehetine' neve. Lingine mono' ganakuti' gilado' vo damine' gamazi li-lingimi monokuti' limi ingaliza initekisi ido' hizi ho'lilizani' gamazisi lilizavemu' nene gizebo igi olovo' igi minilo.

Ido' ve malite evene' ma hize ele' o-ngedaa' amuzo lehize-lede noline' nene mo ha evene' hize ele' o-ngedo minelesune. Ido' evene' inite' ma apize ngemaa' amuzo lehize-lede neine' neivo ma nene mo ha apize ngemo minelesune.

A'mine gamene aline' nene lingine inite' hamokumukisi longo' ma i-nidamilisave. Naza mo lamineto' ti' lo nolo-lingimuve: Neni' ve'nemu' igi lingine me'nehida inite' mamu' lilizani' nene aza a'mine inite' nene mo lengemeleseive.

Ido' a'mine numuno ebeli'mi lave gesi've hizi di otikani' nene geheni ato atotunu' nene gonolise ikani' ve. A'mine naba' naba gehenguti' naba vanu geheni nene zavile geheni ado' zasipa geheni minine' ve. Ido' a'midoti' naba tuu geheni nene gumi lo guno amine' ado' sahila geheni ma nene minine' ve. Ido' naba tili geheni nene zavile gumi ne'mine ado' agate geheni minine' ve. Ido' naba fo geheni nene zavile gehepeve ado' emeladi geheni minine' ve.

Ido' inite' veveso lisihe' ogali'mi monovo ningi gili minisasi a'mine monovo lisihe' amilizani' nene lihime dalisave. Nemu' O'moso ivile' ami O'moso'mo gelo gele lemavo ma inite' ne'minesi ne'minesi ogo molo minelone li lilo.

Ne'mine likevo nolo ma nene O'moso'mi mo'mosi'velati' soto' ogo ti' lo line' ve: Lingine leli' O'moso'mi gonolo' ve ado' eikumu' golise've gilaa' ave evene' ngomo' naba' mukito' nene O'mosote opo'ni lilo.
Ee, laza misubou' okodesi noningu' mene Okulumo' numude nene do ti' ogo saketi ne'mino do ngolaloinako lo agae, agae lo le' izo minaa' noune.

Ido' ve ma aza alungo ma izeni i-dikevo mino alinge' nene vene' damo haza minelove lo lo huko nolingu' a'mine izeni elenahine nene ma duvo lo lulo amuzo molo oteline' ne'mo a'mine alumu' lihime dani' geleleseinako eikumu' lulou' gilido' do molo a'mine alu nene daloseive. Daline' ne'mo goloso amoloseive.
Zuda ve nete mono' mulise'ninguti' nene huli heta i-lingidilisave. Ee, gamene ma alosa neive. A'mingu' nene lengi' lingibili hililizave muki' nete O'moso'mi gono nodube li gilii lingibili hililisave.

Ido' ninguvoni' nene okulumoku' avazaha nite' naba gohi vode vilido' o minine' nene ninguve. Ado' angelo' seveni nete evene' di goloso i-ngidiliza nite' seveni di minani' nene ma ninguve. A'mine evene' di goloso i-ngidiliza nite' soto' ilizani' ne'mo O'moso'mo eveneliti lihime'inemu' izebolo' molani' nene osu' lo-deline' nenako a'midoti' nene evene' do goloso o-ngedeli inite' gohi ma soto' amoloseive.

Ne'mine lavo a'mido' nene Izesu' ti' lo lo-dine': Naza gamazi goloso ma luvoni' neivo ma nene a'mine gamazi goloso ne'mi monovo nene lo soto' ozo. Ido' naza nene mo laminetokovo' noluvoni' noline' nene gaza hazamu' nanimu' nonebelane.

Ee, ido' gono maka' daa' usive gihile geita nene ti' lo noluve: Alungo netise Izesu' gamazi lamine' nene di otilisa monoli'mi lovou' nene zege' zege' igi minasine' nenako nemu' nene gaza uva li di bizilisize. Hize ele' o-ngedelesane. Ee, inginesi nenikisi Kelemedokisi ido' gono maka' daa' unive lingesi nene makato' mono' gonou' nene zege' zege' une' ve. A'mine aleveti gulive'ine nene O'moso'mo minevo' minevo' ngemeni dameni ngemeliveti gulive'ine gize molaa' neine' buku'veu' nene gize neive.

Naza ne'mine noluvoni' nene nanitekumu' ve. Ingine a'mine vanise noso nongemanive engi' nene gei' polohetesi gei' eveneka lingesi ngibili hilikevo vanise'ine lepani' nenako a'mido' golo hizo vanise noso nalizave lo nongemane. Ee, engi' ne'mine noo-ngedaine' nene mo ne'mine o-ngedelinido' lisihe' i nizani' nenako mo lamine' ne'mine noo-ngedane.

Mo keke' ne'mine ma lamolosune. Laza nene hilunive gelo mino hilave nete inite' hamokumukisi upuho' isa'mani' ne'mino upuho' ogo lihime gohi damolonido' mine molo nonive nete nene lihime daa' monovo nene gohi do oto ogo molo minelonido' nene mo keke' nomive.

Ido' a'mine loposo nite' ado' gomu' minosa idise minamive nene a'mine guve'inesi ve sevenilo' imine' molo naba eiti (8) ne'minosa nene neive. Ne neiha aza neve nene a'mine guve'inesi ve seveni engikuti' hamo' neve nene ma mino mo sime' naline' akalo' mine molo neive.

Ne'mine o neine'za a'mine lou' gamazi'mi goboni alevelo' vo do neine' gamazi ma mono' godolou' gizi nizani' nene lo-lengemelove. Ti' li gizi nizave: Goboni alu'mi gipele aza goboni alu minamine' veneli'mi gipele nene meleho salani molo-dine' inite' dalinguti' nene linge ma mo keke' damoloseinako nemu' nene a'mine goboni alu nesi a'mine gipele nesi nene ngimiselo hulozo.

Ne neiha ingine heneni ve lolo' olone li gilaa' ave nene Satani'mo ngemengu' molo ngimimise' ogavo negi hizi do goloso o-ngedaa' neine' inite' mukikumu' nene ma dunivo li gilaa' nani' ne'mo nene vi Satani'mi gelevusou' bilaa' nave. Ee, evene' di goloso i-ngidi ngele'mize tolovo iga' nani' initekumu' nene ngumo helavo monokuti' limi ingi goloso iga' nave.

Ido' a'mine loposo niteli'mi komu've teni ningaine' nesi ido' a'mine loposo nite' nesi nene a'mine Babelonia numuno ebeto' medelo minine' pasidia' vene' nene ningi gosele' gehepeve i-dii inite' mata've nene tava li di huli-dii haza bakakovo' huli-mikii a'mingu' minani' aleve muki' nene mo ngibili osu' liisa olo' nedunu' vite' i-dilisave.
Ne neine'za ve ma ingine O'moso lu'ine imaa' nave nene O'moso'mo engikumu' nene ei' ve lo ningo gele neive.

Neloti' nene laza nadive lo gelelone. Zuda ve leli' nene evene' linge muki' ngivile' ogo lamine' nobe. O'ove. Ne'mino minamune. Mo Zuda vesi a'mine Zuda ve minamavesi nene mo lihime monovoli'mo nene adelo' do minivevo' none lo naza mo lo-lengemekuvoni' ma ve.
Likevo ne gameneu' bulumaka' angale naba avazaha ne'mine lili' igi a'mine avazaha o'moso nene guno gizi imilizani' inite' di igi imi mini engi' a'inedunu' lili' ani' initekumu' ngolize izi minani'.

Ne neiha a'mine evene' di goloso i-ngidaa' ani' initelite ngibili hilamavo evene' lumo ha minave nete nene lu'ine di velepe' izisa igi mili iga' ani' monovo nene hulilizanako hulamave. Ado' ve'ine ningisa'mani' ido' ga'ine gilisa'mani' inite' ido' aka monamilizado' i nizani' inite' soza o'moso ado' ngolidunu' nehe siluva' gehenidunu' nehe ido' ngoli gele vine' inite' gohi madunu' nehe ido' gehenidunu' nehe ido' zadunu' nehe nevo'mine initetunu' engi' a'inedunu' gono di lili' ani' inite' nene ngopo'ni li minaa' ido' sikalahu' goloso ngopo'ni li minaa' ani' nene hulamani' ve.

Nemu' nene laza Guvelesi vemu' golise gelelonido' o neine' nemu' nene gele mino evene' ingine leli' gamazite gililizangumu' nene ga'ine hizaa' noune. Leli' monovote nene mo O'moso'mo gele neive. Ido' monovotemu' nene linginesi ize' mili gilisa a'minemu' gili guni i-lidilizaho lo gelaa' nouve.

Ido' gomu' nene Zuda ve lazasi nene a'mine O'moso'mi gamazi gili hulaa' avete igi mili iga' adi'mine ogo laza muki' gomu' lemeni dameni goloso ne'mo umo hilido' e'meto okodesi ido' gatesi engi' lasido' ogo molo minaa' une' ve. Ido' evene' linge muki' minani' ne'mino lazasi nene O'moso'mo izebolo' molavo lebelelido' o minine' lemeni dameni golososi minune' ve.

Petolo' aza ti' lo lo-ngemosa gamazi muki' imine' molo ga'ine do ti' lo lo-ngimine': Evene' zuho goloso minani' mene O'moso'mo goni' o-ngedo ngebelelingu' nene lengikisi lengebelamivo lukuvo nalizangisi olovo' ilo lo lo-ngimine'.

Nene nanitekumu' ve. Lingine lengemeni dameni litehe'mo gilido' e'meti minilizani' nene mo mudise helaato' mini mili nizave. Ne neiha lingine O'moso'mi Sikalahuli'mi amuzodunu' nene okodine'mo monovo goloso ogo molo oga' ine' nene ma bili hililizani' nene mudise minevo' minevo' ogato' mini mili nizave.

Ido' mene noluvoni' nene mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizado' nene vo milise' ogave: A'mine vemu' gili ele'vole' ilizave muki' nene a'mine gili ele'vole' ilizadoti' nene gihile've dami ngovozo hililizavoba asi hilamilisave.

Gamazi lo ha'na ogo loloze. Gana' nene api' ogo ti' lo noluve: Lingine Izesu' Kilisito' gamazi've amuzo mili gili ele'vole' igi minani' monovotine nene misubou' misubou' buu lo nomonive likevo naza gelo Izesu' Kilisito' velemu' ogo lengi' mukikumu' tangezo' ve lo O'mosola noluve.
Ido' neze zuhokizo, O'moso'mo lulo lengeme neine' mate, aza neni' ve lo do kegese-lingidine' nene gele nounako nemukisi opo'ni laa' noune.

Lute ngemaa' monovolo' e'metilizave nete nene evenelite di goloso i-ngidilizani' lihime muki' nene di halekisavo' apasi-ngidilizani' nenako nemu' nene lingine igi mili ilizani' inite' mukikuti' ma dizo neine' nene lingine lutine ge neme ne geme li minilisa nene amuzo mili igi mili minilo.

Paulo' aza Italia misubouko vilive li li huki alinge' nene ami vanu hadeti neti gizebo ve ma gulive Zulio' aza gizebo o-ngedo ngele'mizo vilive li Paulo'nisi ido' nalato' ve linge masi anau' milani'. A'mine gizebo ve nene aza ami mulise ma guvelesi ve Kaesale'ni ve lani' muliseuti' minine'.

nama ma lani' nene ado' O'moso'mi gonolo' ve Mose' nama'vesi ido' sipisipi angale'mi nama'vesi nene li ti' li lani' ve: Guvekasi ve O'moso amuzo malehe gaza ogo molo oga' naine' inite' nene inite' naba atoli'mine vode vilido' o minine' inite' ne neive. Evene' zuho ato atoliti Guvetesi ve make gei' monovoka nene monovo gihile lisihe' gehepeve o neive.
O'moso'mi gamazi ne'mo lute do naba ogavo lukuvo naloningumu' ve li izipe namunolite aminemu' ngisavo iga' nani' ne'mine igi lingine a'mine lutine'mi noso' nite' aminemu' nene lingisivosavo' minilo.

Neloti' nene Okulumokuti' nolo ma soto' ogo ti' lo nolivo giluve: Gamazi ti' lo gizezo: Idise meloti' evene' ma ingine Guvelesi ve huli-dami eita ha gi'mizi mini hili vika' vika' ilizave nene mo ngolize izi lamini miniliza akalo' mini mili nizave. Ne'mine lavo O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo nene mo lamine' ve losa ti' lo line' ve: Engi' igi mili minaa' ani' monovo'ine'mi gihile've nesi nene engikisi maka' vo heteleline' nenako nemu' nene lihitehe' gono daa' ani' ma nene gohi dami ha mini gilivo' minilisave.

Lodomulo' izipe ido' vene' geto' muhele' igi minani' nene ngele'mize lamine' olone' ido' me misubou' evene' O'mosomu' gilamaveti monovo'ine dokunivo lute do goloso ogalive lo gizebo ogo minelone' nene O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo mono' ve gihile minelonidi'mo Meteho O'moso'mi velelo' hehe lamine' lo mineleseive.
Ne'mine noluvoni' nene evene' hamolitesi gamazi noso'vesi li-lingimii gotine izi lengele'mize gopo ikelizave losa noluve.

Ne'mine li nilavo ma giluvoni' nene O'moso'mo do soto' ine' inite' Okulumoku' nehe misubou' nehe ido' misubo lulou' nehe ido' guvo nosolo' nehe a'mingu' minani' inite' muki' nete nene nama ti' li nilavo giluve: Mo'mosi'veu' minivesi sipisipi angalesi ingine nene amuzo'inesi ve mini dizivo' minikesivo guve'ine monaa' neingumu' nene do naba o-ngedo ngopo'ni nolune' nene mo huko vamo minevo' minevo' ogo minelive.

Ne'mine ogavo angelo' naba tuu ne'mo nene pikuli hubu lo do nolo molavo golo naba ne'mine gele vine' inite' nene ma olo' lo neivo guvo nosou' di hulani' ve. Ne'mine ikevo guvo noso laka'ni seto hamo mininguti' lingela hamo' nene vanise nosovo' lolo' ine' ve.

Abuti' izi ehuso' igi di vi numuno si'mingala huli-di vi eze lihime'vemu' li soto' ave nete geheni huli bili' bili' ilisa ingine oko'nido' inite' ha'na ha'na ne kuluhizi gipe goso've ma minine' gulive Saulo' ne'mi gizeneu' di mulise milani'.
Ido' gohi ma ti' lo neive: Heta ato' ve lingine muki' nene O'moso opo'ni li minilo. Ee, evene' zuho ato ato' muki' ingine nene O'moso opo'ni li minilizani' o neive.

Nanitekumu' ve. Inite' muki' nene eitokovo' gelekele' i-dilizave losa asi'vevo' inite' muki' do soto' ogavo mo eitokovo' lehete i minaa' nave. Nemu' nene O'moso opo'ni lo minelone' nene huko vamivo ha miniliho.

Ongo go' lavo Izesu' nene mono' noso holo-ngedaa' ive Zohane' neida navo ningo ti' lo line' ve: Aizo, ningilo. Lihimetemu' belaa' noune' sipisipi angalelo' medelo O'mosolati' minive me misubou' aleveti lihimete apase-ledaa' ive ma ve.

Ido' Isilaele' aleve lovo di Zeliko ebeku' olihe alisa navo a'mine ebeku' minine' pasidia' alu Lahaba' aza api' ogo O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo minine' ne'mo Isilaele' ve sita' a'mine numuno ebe' Zeliko nene amamaka' mili ningi alisa vasive nene do lamine' o-ngedo numu'veu' ngele'mize molavo nemu' nene alinge' Isilaele' aleve nete igi Zeliko aleve O'moso'mi gamazi gili hulani' ngibili gese' angu' nene Lahaba'ni nene bilami iseve izi-dani' ve.

Ido' gumine gizengizelo' ve ingine hazamu' ami asi gumine damine igi ngibili di goloso ilisavo' iga' nave. Ne'mine iga' naha neni' uvoni' nene ne'mine olosa amo asi neni' sipisipi ize'ne nene minevo' minevo' ngemeni dameni nene ingine dalizani' votigile ivile' ivosa lehize-ngedekuvo di ti' igi lamini gehepevevo' minilizave losa uvoni' ve.

Ido' Izesu' evenele leli' goto' numude nene Okulumoku' nenako ingine ne'mine igi minaa' naani' nene mo edamive. Ee, do lu' izelive Guvelesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' aza Okulumokuti' alingumu' nene gilingili ogo gizebo ogo none.
Nemu' nene O'moso opo'ni li di naba i-dilizangisi Kilisito' aza lengikisi lengele'mize lamine' idi'mine igi lingine ge nele'mize lamine' o-nede ne gele'mize lamine' o-gede li minilo.

gaza vo engita gi'mizo leze Zuda veti monovo di engikisi okodine lutine O'moso'mi velelo' lamine' ilive li di lamine' ilo. Ne'mine ikevo O'moso gizi imilizani' inite' meni hize-ngedanivo gizi vata' niigi godo'ine zopovo huki matava ili di hulilizave. Ne'mine ikevo mukilite ningi geikumu' lani' nene hazamu' soza gamazi li-gidi lani' nene gililisave. Ido' Mose' lo huko line' gamazi nene gazasi gele daa' naine' nesi gililisave.

Ne'mino engi' me'nibo lolo' ogo minine' nene laza O'moso'mi noso okodela mulunive linge maliti meteho nesi neive. Ado' laza nene avoteho Abalahamu' O'moso'mi noso oko'nola nomivo mino gele ele'vole' ogo minine' monovo'velo' e'meto mino O'moso'mi nosovo' nene okodela mulunivoba asi gele ele'volekisi o noniveti meteho nesi nene neive.
Ti' li opo'ni li O'moso gelavo di kegesaa' zohiku' ngele'mizi milikevo Matatia' ivile' ogavo aposolo leveni minangu' nene di gi'mizi-dani' ve.
Ve ma lou' gamazi've avuto' angumu' nene O'moso'mo gele hulo lihime'ine hulo-ngedelive nene ngolize izilizado' lisihe' i nizave.
A'mine ve seta' neve nene gomu' polohete Zekalia' line' oliva za setakisi ido' lamu livi' seta' misuboli'mi Guvelesi ve'mi velelo' minaa' nasive ma nene nizasive.

Lingine monovotida gili evene' goloso none li agae agae li longovozo hili mulumo gili ive ilo. Ee, gize zohi' igi longolize izaa' nani' nene huli mulumo gili muhele' igi ivevo' igi agae agae li minilo.

Zogone lamine, evene' ma goloso nite' di nizavo ma a'mido' nge'metamozo. Inite' lamine' di nizavo ma nelokovo' nge'metezo. Ingine inite' lamine' di minaa' nave nene O'mosolati' soto' ani' ve. Ido' ingine goloso nite' di minaa' nave ingine mo O'mosomu' ningi gilamave.

Ne'mine ogo Abalahamu' oko'nola O'moso'mi noso nomine' mino O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo minine' nemu' nene O'moso'mo ve lisihe' ve lo-dine' nene do soto' olosa a'mine noso nene ei' oko'nolo' nene molani' ve. Ne'mine ine' nenako Abalahamu' aza O'moso'mi noso oko'nida nomine' minisa O'mosomu' gili ele'vole' ilizadoti' nene O'moso'mo ve lisihe' ve lo-ngedeliveti me'nibo lolo' ine' ve.

Ido' ne'mine noluvoni' nene nemu' noluve: Ve'inesi mini lihime monovolo' gelekele' igi mini hilangu' nene a'mine monovosi huko vavosa hilave nene lihime monovo'mi gelekele' ve gohi ma minami haza minaa' nave.

Neve nene laza mo Izesu' helaato' mine molo mino monaa' ine' ma'minosa nene nomonune. Ne'mine oga' noune' nene lelitoti' nene Izesu' minevo' alevo've neine' ma nene evene' muki' ningilizave losa nene ne'mine oga' noune.
Ido' linge ma muki' nete nene engi' inite'inemukovo' gili minisa Izesu' Kilisito' gono'vemu' nene ma gilisa'mave.

Ido' Abalahamu' aza O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' oga' ive minine' ne'mo nene O'moso'mo gipa ma gedelesane lo lo huko-dine' nenako nemu' aza go'ne ngelo izamoloseinako mo gedelesuve lo gelo gele ele'vole' ogo minine' ne'mo elenaho Sala' aza gohuno vene' neivo ido' Abalahamu' aza ozoho molo izipe gedeli gamene osu' lavo ne'mini minasido' nene O'moso'mo Sala'ni izipe molo emeline' amuzo emavo Isaka'ni gidine'.

A'mine nimiselive'mi lulolo' ogo molo oloni' nene ma ne'mino neive: Naza gizebo lamine' okuvo a'mine neni' niminguti' nene hamolitesi ma vi tolovo amavo alinge' gamene nabala nene muki' gohi do ote-ngedeline losa gele neive.

Ne'mini minani' neiha Kilisito' evenele zuho laza nene ti' lo gele none: O'moso ei' hamo' nene neive. Aza nene Meteho inite' mata' muki' do soto' ive ne neive. Ido' laza nene eze lulolo' ogo molo olone lo eito' lehete ogo minaa' unive ne neive. Ido' Guvelesi ve nene hamo' neive. A'mine ve Izesu' Kilisito' nene O'moso'mo eito' gele medele mino inite' mata' muki' nesi ido' leli' nesi do soto' ive ne neive.

Ido' Timoteo' aza lingisi minadati' lezela ogo hetelo lingine Izesu'nimu' gili ele'vole' igi minani' nemu' vetete' ogo lo-lemave. Ido' lelikumu' gilikevo gamene gamene lamine' ogo minaa' ivo laza lingine ningelone lo minaa' une' ne'mino linginesi a'mine'mine igi lezemu' ningelone li gili minaa' ani' nesi lo-leme osu' lave.
Ne'mine ikevo gizebo ve naba aza soto' ogo heteleline' gameneu' nene lingine meni dalisave. Ado' geleso osu' lamiline' palaisi labana'vesi neine' nene dalisave.

Ido' a'mine noluvoni' monovomu' mene mo gele mu'musi' o none' nenako nemu' nene laza gamazi laa' noune' nene do hito gepe' gamazi ne'mingutikisi lamo asi mo gamazi lamine' sotokovo' lovo' kiselevo' ogo laa' noune.

Ne neiha a'mine ve nene ize gulo ido' nama gaha ga'ine nomivo minani' ado' evenelite ngimiselo ngebelaa' ido' ngebelaa' olonido' soto' igi minaa' naani' ne'mini mini ingine gilamani' initekumu' nene divi' ledivi' igi laa' nave. Nemu' nene ize gulo nama gaha ngebelaa' noune' ne'mine ogo O'moso'mo a'mine ve nene do goloso gehepeve o-ngedeleseive.

Zuda' aza ne'mine gamazi line' nene goho' gahali' alevemu' nene mulumo'ine gelosa lamive. Asi aza nene engi' moni milani' benilo' gizebo ve mino guminelo' ve minine' nenako a'minguti' nene do haleke' haleke' ogo minaa' ine' ve.

Ido' O'moso'mo lulo lemaa' neine' nene ningo gele ele'vole' o none. Lulo lemo nasahili' oga' monovo nene O'moso'mi emeni dameni gihile neine' nenako ve ma ingine lu'ine ve ma ngimi'mi vi minivi' divi' i'mi vilizani' nene ingine O'mosola bizi nizavo O'moso nesi engi' lu'ningu' minevo' dovo' ogo mineleseive.

Setehano'ni bili hilisa goboni mili-ngidikevo Izesu' zuho hutile' igi vanguti' ingine linge ma Hoinikia misubou' vi minani'. Ido' linge ma sipiu' dizi vi ailani ma gulive Kipilo nela vi minani'. Ido' linge ma vi Adiokia ebeta minani'. Ingine muki' vi mini evene' ato' ma li-ngimami Zuda vevo' Izesu' gamazi've li-ngimani'.

Ido' lamine' inite' gohi gohi dalone' aka nene neine'za ingine giladi'mine ogo me misubou' inite' nevoba asi laza do none' inite' nene leli' votigilelo' mo vo do neive lo hongu lo lamino minosa mono' monovolo' e'metaa' noune' ne'mo luteli'mi heneni nene vai' goloso do soto' o-ledaa' neive.

Ido' O'moso'mi evenele zuho lovo o ngemo ngivile' ilingumu' nene O'moso'mo gele emo evene' zuho ato ato' misubo ato atoku' mini'mi monave no'ine ato atokisi oko'ine ato atokisi minavelo' nene gizebo ogo mineline' amuzo nesi nene imine' ve.

Ne neiha lingine inite' ma di goloso ikevo a'minemu' lihime lingimi gavoso nilingibilavo lingine hongu li mini ha gihilizani' nemu' nene longopo'ni lilizado' minilizahe. O'ove. Longopo'ni lamilisani'za lingine inite' lisihe' lamine' ma ikevo gavoso nilingibilavo lingine hongu li ha gihilizani' nene O'moso'mo ningivo lamine' oloseive.

Ido' Kilisito' vanise've ne'mo lihimete muki' gilite hulo-ledaa' neine' nenako Izesu' aza nene evenekisi O'mososi kuku holo-ledo gamazi hulo eza ema ogo leli' gele emelone' gamazi ve lo gosoho' gamazi O'moso'mo lo huko-lidine' nene do ogo limive lolo' ogo neive. Ido' ne'mine ine' nene O'moso'mo izipahala zuho minilizave lo elese molo-ledo lele'mize molave leli' nene minevo' minevo' inite' lemelove lo lo huko-ledo salani molo-lidine' inite' daloningumu' ve losa ne'mine ine' ve. Ee, O'moso'mo gomu' lo huko-lidine' gamazi nene avuto' ogo lihime duningumu' a'mido' golo hizo Izesu' hiline' ne'mo nene a'mine lihime nene apase-lidine' nenako ne'mo nene a'mine salani molo-lidine' inite' dalone' aka nene ngolo' lo neinako ha dalosune.

Ido' lihime daa' monovo naba o'mo vo minida nene a'mine naba o'mo vine' votigile nene ivile' goloso ivosa O'moso'mi nasahili' nene atoli'mine ogo soto' ogo minine' nenako nemu' nene laza nadive lolone. O'moso'mo nasahili' gohi vauve elo o-ledeline' aka nene do soto' oloseize. Lihime nene daakovo' ogo minuke'zo lolobe.

Ido' lingine nene ekese' gamazi nesi lami ido' dingani gamazi nevo'mine nesi lami ido' ha gize' zohi' gamazi nolube li monovo laminekumu' di gopo igi lami ido' monovo golosomu' nene vetete' igi lami O'moso opo'ni li minilo.

Ne'mine lavo ve'nela hosi ma omo minine' nene oko'nolo' lani gise holo neine' gele vine' minine' ve. Ido' a'mine hosilo' minive'mi gulive nene Helaa' ve lo minine' ve. Ido' ve ma gulive Gonoso Galese ve lo minive nene mo avito' mehenela ezesi maka' vasine' ve. Ne'mine nasivo engi' nene O'moso'mo misubou' aleve mulise seta've seta've minanguti' mulise hamo' nene ngibililisingumu' amuzo ngemekuvo ingine a'mine amuzo di mini a'mine aleve nene lovo'mo ma ngebelelive ido' ga'na'mo ma ngebele helelive ido' siki initeli'mo ma ngebele helelive ido' loposo initelite nene ma ngibili hililizave likesivo ngibili hililizangumu' nene O'moso'mo a'mine amuzo nene ngimine' ve.

Nemu' nene a'mine salani inite' dalone' nene mo O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' olonidotikovo' nene haza gidini doso' o neive. Ee, a'mine lo huko-lidine' inite' nene O'moso'mo haza nasahili' o-lididi'movo' nene Abalahamu' a'vopilemo' zuho muki' ado' Mose' lou' gamazi'mi gesi mingu' nonivesi ido' a'mingu' minami Abalahamu' aza O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' idi'mine igi gili ele'vole' ilizavesi nene laza mukito' dalonido' lisihe' o minelive losa lehize-lidine' nenako gele ele'vole' olonidotikovo' nene haza gidini doso' o neive. Abalahamu' nene a'mine ne'mino dalonive mukiliti meteho nene neive.
Ne'mine igi goni' i-nidi lihime've apaso bele helelone' votigilelo' lihime dahe damihe li vise' aha aha nomivo nala' numunguti' kuluhizi-nidilisa lani'za

Nemu' nene O'moso'mo evene' mamu' neni' ve lo do kegese-ngedeline' nene angise'ine giladoti' nehe ido' ingine igi mili minaa' naadoti' nehe nene ma do molo do kegese-ngedesa'mive. Asi O'moso'mo evene' muhelete ningosa isete izaa' neine' monovo've ne'movo' nene ei' ve lo do kegese-ngedeleseive.

Ido' ma nene engikuti' vene' vemoho' gopo' napa ingi'mi monikevo O'moso'mo gamene hamokukovo' evene' 23 tauseni ngebele hiline' nenaze. Laza nene ingine adi'mine ogo vene' vemoho' gopo' napa ongamolone.

oko'ne mukita nene ato' monovosi minaa' neivosa nene mo ningekuve. A'mine monovo ne'mo nene lu'ne ga'neu' minine' monovo lamine' nene lovo o emo mino a'nelo' nesi nene do mino a'mine oko'nela minine' lihime monovolo' nene do gelekele' o-nedaa' neive.

Ido' ezemu' nene haza ve ve li lingine ningi huli-damilo. Lengita navo ma hongu gamazivo' li-imi mini neni' nouvoda alingumu' ve li aka've vili-di imiselilo. Leze zuhosi mela eze alingumu' nene gizebo o none.

Neze zuho mate, ve mali'mo monovo lamine' ogo molo minamo naza Izesu'nimu' giluvoni' nene gele ele'vole' okuve lo liline' nene haza nite' lolo' oloseive. Ne'mine ogovo' gele ele'vole' o do vilidoti' nene O'moso'mo do u' izamoloseive.
Ne'mine lavo Zelusalemi aleve linge nene ti' li li minani': Me ve nene leli' ve nabalite bililisa gilave ma nene neive. Olo.
Ne'mine losa vele mu'nive hubu lo-ngedo ti' lo lo-ngimine' ve: O'moso'mi Sikalahu' mene dalo.

Ido' ne'mine noluvoni' nene nemu' noluve: Ingine O'moso'mo evenekumu' evene' lisihe' ve lo-ngedaa' neine' monovomu' nene gili imami mini angise'ine di soto' ani' monovolo' di mili evene' lisihe' ilisa igi mili minaa' nani'za O'moso'mo evene' lisihe' ve lo-ngedeline' monovolo' nene gelekele' amave.

Ingine O'moso'mi gipelemu' gili ele'vole' iga' nave nene lu'inedunu' gilikevo ele'vole' oga' neive. Ido' ingine O'moso'mo line' gamazi gili ele'vole' ami nizave nete O'moso'mo gipele hize ele' o-do line' gamazi nene gilikevo gihile izesa'minako nemu' O'mosomu' sozalo' ve ve lani' gelaa' neive.

Naza mo lamineto' gehepeve nolo-lingimuve. Ve ma ingine nenikumu' gili ele'vole' i minilizave muki' nesi nene naza ogo molo nouvoni' inite' ne'mine nene ha igi mili ilisave. Ee, ido' naza nene me'nehida voloni' nenako ne'mo nene ingine naza uvoni' inite' nene ivile' ivosa atoli'mine inite' naba nesi ha ilisave.
Ido' gelekele' gipe alu nene lo-ngemanivo ingine me'ningine mulu'ine di lamine' i-ngidi gamazi di tibizi li-ngimami inite' mata' mukito' nene gelekele' i-ngidi gamzai'ine diivo' minilizave.

O'mosolati' nasahili' lamine' nene lengi' zuho malite ningi huli aka malo' vikelizave li ge gizebo o-nede ne gizebo o-gede li minilo. Ido' lengi' zuho mali'mo lengi' vovotingu' mino za mali'mo gihile ekese' ine' izaa' neine' ne'mino mino monovo goloso ato ato' do soto' ogo lengita geni do soto' o-lengedo neivo lengikuti' evene' lingela muki' nene a'mine'mine igi monovo goloso dikevo lutine do gopo ogalive li gizebo lekeseve igi minilo.

Ido' Izesu' evenele minamave nete ezemu' gamangi mili-daa' avevo' nene mono' gizebo ve lili' i-dilizave. Mono' gizebo ve nene ne'mine ve minamiline' nene evene' malite monovo goloso ogave li elemikevo Satani'mo emengu' molo ivile' ogavo lihime daalive losa noluve.
Ne neiha Kilisito' aza leli' hamo hamo' lehize-ledelesa giline' votigilelo' nene leli' muki' hamo hamo' nene monoli'mi amuzo lehize-ledave.

Neloti' nene angelo' naba tuu ne'mo vo ei' lapese'veu' minine' inite' goloso ma nene lepe hulo guvo nosou' ogavo a'mine guvo noso nene evene' hilaveti vanise'ine ne'mine lolo' ogavo a'mingu' ve'inesi minaa' ani' inite' muki' nene hili gese' ani' ve.

Ido' gonou' ve lingine gizebo vete nete lezemu' ningi lamine' gililizave li engi' ve'nido' nene gono amuzo mili daa' nave gili gono di minisa ido' alinge' gizebo vetine nete ningamavo gono gilizevo igi di minaa' nani' ne'mine nene amilo. Kilisito' goboni ve gihilelite gono dalizani' monovo lisihetokovo' nene e'meti O'moso'mo gilido' nene e'meti gizebo vetine nete gono lingimilizani' nene lutine laminetotikovo' dalo.

Ido' ne'mine igi li-ngimili ma nene humedame ami hongu gamazi laminekovo' li-ngimilo. Ido' lingine Kilisito' evenelelite ilizado' o neine' monovo lamine' igi mili minaa' naangumu' divi ledivi' igi laa' nave nene a'mine lengemenga langumu' nene ngovozo hililizangumu' ve li monovo lisihe' lamine' gehepeve neive li lutingu' gili nizadokovo' nene e'meti minilo.

Ee, me'neho aza lulou' gele neine' nene gipele neni' ningisa nenikumu' gili ele'vole' ilizave muki' nene minevo' minevo' minaa' ngemeni dameni ngemanivo di nizavo alinge' gamene nabala nene gohi do ote-ngedelesane losa gele neive.
Ne'mine likevo aza nene neni' nopo'ni lami O'mosovo' opo'ni lilo lamivo O'moso'mi angeloli'mo belavo oko'no ginine hizavo hiline' ve.

Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' ei' O'moso've mino ei' meleho minive nene opo'ni lolone. Aza nene mulumote gelaa' monovoli'mi meleho mino hize ele' oga' monovo muki' do soto' o-ledaa' neine' O'moso nene neive.
Ne'mine ilizangumu' nene noluvoni'za evene' linge ma nene mo a'mine aka lamine' nene huli zovo' izisa gihile've nomine' gamazivo' li volelo' melo' iga' nave.

Naza Loma ebetasi vo Izesu' gamazi lamine' lo-lengemelove luvoni' nene a'mine gamazi ne'mo O'moso'mo Izesu'nimu' gili ele'vole' ave do ngu' izeline' amuzo've nene do soto' oga' neivosa nemu' nene naza a'mine gamazi lamine' nene lo soto' olosa novozo helamo nolize izo laa' nouvoni' nenako nemu' luve. Ee, a'mine gamazi lamine' ne'mo nene O'moso'mo do ngu' izeline' amuzo've nene gomu' Zuda vela do soto' o-ngedosa Zuda ve minamave nGiliki ve nevo'mida nesi nene do soto' o do novive.

Numuno do oto gizaa' simeni lamine' nene ngeli ato' keke' mo lolo' amilisave. Numuno do oto gizaa' simeni lamine' nene mo neize. A'midokovo' nene numuno di oti gizilizave. Naza nene O'moso'mi numuno gizo do otaa' simeni nene Izesu' Kilisito' ei' hamo' nene neive losa noluve.

Ido' ne'mine li mono' godolou' gizani' nene Kilisito'nimukisi eze evenele zuho mulisemukisi nene li gizani'za a'mine nene mo lengi' vene' vemohotasi nene vo do neize. Mukito' lingine lengi' okodinemu' gilaa' nani' ne'mine igi venetinemu' gili lutine ngimikevo vene' lingine nete vadinginemu' nene evene' nabate mo gelekele' o-ngedelonido' o neive li vadingine gili ngimi mini di vi minilizave.

Ee, lingine O'moso'mi noso lengita nomine' mini lengemeni dameni litehe nene hulamii goloso nite' di minadi'mo lutine hele vine' minanguti' nene Kilisito'nisi maka' lengi' lutinesi nene O'moso'mo do vele gizine' ve. Ne'mino Kilisito'nisi makato' do ote-lidine' giline' nene aza goloso nitete muki' do hulo-ledosa nene ne'mine ine' ve.

Ido' O'moso'mi veleti' gamazi geikumu' line' nene nilavo ido' mono' gizebo ve nene gonou' gele'mizi mili a'nine godokalo' nimilavo gonou' amuzo O'moso'mo lehize-gidine' nesi nene damanivo haza minaalive.

Ido' neloti' gohi ma ninguvoni' nene Okulumo' gosoholi'minesi ido' misubo gosoholi'minesi nene ninguve. Ido' gosoholi'mine ninguve noluvoni' nene Okulumo' misubo litehe nene mo mudise vi haha ikesivo guvo noso nesi nene gohi ma minamine' nenako nemu' nene gosoho' ve noluve.
Muludingu' gulumo avile lisivovo' minilo.
Ne'mine igi mulumo ekese' gili minilizani' gameneu' nene evene' nete helaa' akamu' vise' ilisaha mo ma ningamilisave. Ee, mo helelobo li gili minilisaha helaa' ne'mo nene olovo' o-ngedeleseive.

Laza nene Izesu' hilinguti' gohi otine' nene gele ele'vole' o none. Nemu' ti' lo gelelone: Tine' molo aline' gameneu' nene Izesu'nimu' gili ele'vole' igi hilave inginesi O'moso'mo ngele'mizo aloseive.
Ido' evene' malite Izesu' aza lamine' mo O'moso'mi gipele neive li li soto' ave nene O'moso'mo engi' lu'ningu' minevo' dovo' ogo neivo ingine O'mososi bizi nizave.

Ido' nemu' nene lingine gomu' monovo goloso igi mili minaa' adoti' ha minine' lengemeni dameni litehe ne'mo nene leli' gote izo lele'mize goloso oga' neine' initekumu' nene umo helaa' neine' nenako nemu' lingine a'mine gomu' lengemeni dameni nene mo di hulilo.

Ee, neni' nene a'mine gesi'mi gateni nouvonako a'mingu' neniku' imi hili gesi minguko dizilizave muki' nene inite' mali'mosi do goloso o-ngedamivo laminekovo' minilisave. Ne'mine igi mini dizi limi igi noso' nite' ningi ni lamini minilisave.

Ido' linge ma nene gehenidunu' huli huli' igi ngibilaa' avo hilaa' ani' ve. Ido' linge ma nene ngibili giti seta' iga' ani' ve. Ido' linge ma nene bainati mite' nedunu' ngibili hilaa' ani' ve. Ido' linge ma O'mosomu' gili ele'vole' ani' nemu' ngimiseli hulikevo oko'nido' inite'ine nomivo sipisipi losuvo ido' meme' losuvo nedunukovo' oko'nido' ngili moni oko'ine losuvo'mi inite' noso' initekisi ido' genegana'inesi muki' nene nomivo nimonavo goboni mili-ngidi di goloso i-ngidaa' ani' ve.
O'moso aza nene ve lisihe' lamine' neive li lingine gili nizave. Gili nizanako evene' ingine monovo lisihe' lamine' igi mili minaa' navemu' nene O'mosolati' soto' ani' ve li gililisave.

Nemu' nene Guvelesi ve'mo ti' lo lo leme neine' ve: Gaza nene heta ato' veliti lamu livi'ine ne'mine lolo' ogo mineline lo gele'mize molokuve. Ado' misubo lumola minave nesi lukuvo nalizani' aka nene gei' ngelebizeline lo gele'mize molokuve.

Laza nene monovo goloso suno' daa' naani' ne'minemu' nene mo amolosune lo mo mehede emekune. Laza evene' ma nene go'ine izo O'moso'mi gamazi lamineli'mo lido' lamo do ato' ogo lo-ngemesa'mune. Asi evene' muki' leli' monovote nene ize' mili ningi hehe lilizangumu' ve lo O'moso'mi velelo' mino gamazi gihile laminekovo' nene lo soto' ogo ngelebizaa' noune.

Ido' meleho O'moso'mo evene' muki' livile' ogo dize minive ve li ningilizave lo ana zamela ele'mize molo gozopo' lo huko-dido' e'meto eze Sikalahu've emavo lehize-lidine'. Ido' idise gili ningi nizani' inite' ado' eze Sikalahu've lehize-lidine' nene gili ningi nizave.

lengemeni dameni gosoho' di otuhani' ma neive. A'mine lengemeni dameni nene O'moso'mo lingine eikumu' gili vevesi osu' li minilizangumu' ve lo ei' a'mine lengemeni dameni do soto' ive'mi avazahalo' gehepeve nene gohi do gosoho' o'mo voovo' neive.

Ido' Izesu' nene a'mine gamazi gelosa ti' lo line': Inite' gize dani' nene mudise helelive losa nevoba asi O'moso'mi guvele monelive losasi ido' neloti' nene O'moso'mi gipele neni' nene di hozi li-nidilizangumu' ve losasi nene inite' gize dani' ve.

Ido' O'moso'mo evene' do ngu' izeline' amuzo've nene Izesu' gamazi ne'mo do soto' oga' neive luvoni' nene nemu' luve: A'mine gamazi laminekuti' nene O'moso'mo evene' do lu' izelido' do lisihe' o-ledaa' neine' aka've nene soto' ogavo ningo gelekune. A'mine aka nene ne'mino neive: Evene' ma laza Izesu'nimu' gele ele'vole' ogo minelone' ne'movo' nene O'moso'mi velelo' evene' lisihe' lamine' lolo' ogo minelesune. Ee, gele ele'vole' olonidotikovo' nene O'moso'mo do lu' izelido' lisihe' ogo minelesune. Neve nene mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizado' nene vo dave: Ingine O'moso nenikumu' gili ele'vole' igi minilizadoti' evene' lisihe' lamine' lili' ilizave nene do ngu' izekuvo minivi' minivi' ilisave.
Di vada nene Izesu' asi've ei' lohoto' za've geho numuno ebekuti' leme heta ogo vo ebe' ma gulive Godolo Amuzo Ebe' ado' Zuda veti gamaziuti' nene Goligota ve laa' ado' nene hetelavo

Ido' O'moso'mo nasahili' o-ledo amuzo lehize-ledine' nene hamoli'minevo' lehize-ledamo ato atoli'mine lehize-lidine' ve. Nemu' nene O'moso'mo ve ma lehize-lede noline' amuzo nene O'moso'mi veleti' gamazi lo soto soto' oga' amuzo noline' nene laza mo la'lisete gele ele'vole' o nolone' votigilelo' nene do molosa O'moso'mi veleti' gamazi nene lo soto soto' ogo lolosune.

A'mine ve'inesi ha minaa' ani' initekuti' ma neve nene laioni gulo gele vine' minine' ve. Ido' ezeloti' minive nene bulumaka' ne'mine gele vine' minine' ve. Ido' ezeloti' minine' inite' nene evene' gote vete gele vine' ne'minesi minine' ve. Ido' a'midoti' neve nene nolise naba patelo nomonine' emeni damenisi minine' ve.

Nemu' nene lingine evene' ga'ine gili nge li mini igi mili isa'mave nete iga' ani' ne'mine ami asi evene' ga'ine gili nge li mini monovo laminekovo' igi mili iga' nani' ne'mine igi monovotine igi mili mini di vilizado' nene gizebo lekeseve igi minilo.

Ido' ingine muki' ngovozo hilamilisave noluvoni' nene Zuda vesi heta ato' vesi nene ato atoli'mine minamavo engi' sitato' gizebo oga' ive nene Guvelesi ve ei' hamokovo' mino hize ele' o-ledelive li ezela laa' nave ato ato' muki' nene atoli'mine ogo nasahili' o-ngedaa' neine' nenako nemu' nene noluve.

Ne'mine iga' nani'za ezemu' gili ele'vole' igi minave nene ve lisihe' ve lo-ngedosa Kilisito' aza lou' gamazilo' e'metaatoti' evene' lisihe' lolo' oga' aka nene mo mudise hize tiline' nenako nemu' ingine nene mo ladani nave.

Inite' mukikumu' muludine otavo gituho' namii mini asi a'mine inite' mukikumu' nene O'mosola li voku' laa' igi ido' isaa' neve laa' igi mini inite' mamu' longo' ilisa gilani' initekumu' nene O'moso li-imaa' igi minilo.

Ido' Zuda ve ingine goloso initekumu' lanite' gili di soto' i'mi vikevo O'moso'mo do soto' ogo lihime ngimine' inite' luvoni' nemu' lingine gili ingine adi'mine igi goloso initekumu' lanite' gili a'mine'mine ikelizave losa O'moso'mo alinge' soto' olonivemu' aka lelebizo ne'mine ine' ve.

Ido' a'mine kii' nedunu' nene a'mine galese'mi akahe've nene si'zo godavo a'minguti' nene sokile vai' goloso hosoni vite' ikevo sokile dizaa' ine' ne'mino dizo okulumotokisi ido' ho' velelokisi molo hito do liti'muso izine' ve.

Mali'mo ne'mine iline' nene ve gonoloho noso molani' nene avuto' ogo elenahine longo' ogo a'mine ve gonolohi inite've do gopo o-dalive. Ne'mine ilizave nene Guvelesi ve'mo lihime ngemeleseive lo gomu' ogo lo-lingimune' ma ve.

Ee, ne'mino neine' nenako nemu' nene evene' ma ingine Kilisitoda mini mili nilizave nene mo O'moso'mo do gosoho' gehepeve o-ngede neine' nenako ne'mo ingine gomu' igi mili minani' monovo'ine ma nene mo osu' lavo ngemeni dameni'ine nene, aizo, mo gosoho' gehepeve lolo' ogave.

Ido' gamazi mene noluvoni' nene neemu' noluve. Me'neho aza gipele neni' nene lulo neme neine' nenako nemu' nene aza ogo molo oga' neine' inite' muki' nene nelebize osu' laa' neive. Ido' ne'mine oga' neine' nenako nemu' nene lingine upuho' igi golize lilizave lo idise ogo molo nouvoni' inite' mene ivile' ivosa atoli'mine suno naba goloso nelebizavo olosuve.

Ido' gomu' gumine daminelo' ve minave ingine idise a'mine monovotine nene hulisa lengi' adinedunu' gono laminekovo' disa inite' vise' igi minilizani' aleve hize ele' o-ngedelone' votigilelo' nene inite' pata' do soto' molalone li gono amuzo mili di minilo.

Ido' gamazi hamo' gohi ma neine' neve nene ne'mine lo noluve: Lingine nenikumu' ve li O'mosola laa' naani' malo' nene O'moso'mo gele lengemo neni' neve nene lengita nimiselavo alosuve losa gele nouze. Ongaloni' numuno lulo nene ma do va'va' o nimikezo.

nemu' nene evene' ma mono' gamazi ve li soza gamazi ato ato' li-lingimilizani' ne'mo gatine hizalize. Lute hize ele' oloseive li noso' nite' naakumukisi li-lingimilizani'za lute hize ele' o-ledaa' neine' inite' nene noso' nite' nevoba asi O'moso'mo nasahili' o-ledaa' neine' ne'mo lute amuzo molavo ne'mo nene lamine' iline' nenako a'mine noso' nitekumu' li-lingimilizani' gamazi gili daa' nave nene a'mine initeli'mo ngele'mize lamine' amaa' neine' nenako ne'mo gatine hizalive.
Neze zuho mate, inite' mamu' amuzo molo nolo-lingidune: Guvetesi ve'mo ngele'mize molavo lengita mono' gono di gizebo i-lingidi mini lengele'mizi hehe li nizavemu' nene gili lamine' igi minilo.

Ido' izelehoi melehoi ne'mine lasine' nene Zuda ve naba nete nene gomukuti' gamazi ne'mine li li hukikani' ve: Ve malite Izesu' nene O'moso'mo do lu' izelesa imiselelesa live ve li lilizave nene Zuda ve leli' mono' muliseuti' do hulo-ngedelesune. Ne'mine li li hukikani' nenako nemu' nene izelehoi melehoi ingine a'mine Zuda ve nabamu' golise gili minisa nene ne'mine lasine' ve.

Ne'mine noluvoni' nene neemu' noluve. O'moso'mi noso gihile neve nene leli' okode losuvo'mi initeto' nene gele medelamuba asi O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo hize ele' o-lididi'mo O'moso gubi' ize emo Izesu' Kilisito'nimu' lolize izo mino ezelo' gele medele minaa' nounive netevo' nene do none.

Ido' a'mine lo huko line' gamazi nene ti' lo neive: Izesu'nimu' nene aza O'moso'mi gipele mino O'moso'mo do lu' izelive lo imiselelesa live nene neive lo laza gele ele'vole' ogo lute ge neme ne geme lo mineloningumu' lo-limido' e'meto olosune.

Neloti' ma ninguvoni' nene loposo nite' gohi ma misubouti' dizo nohetelivo ninguve. A'mine loposo nite' nene sipisipi angaleliti komu'ine ne'mine setakisi minine' mino gamazi've line' nene sata' gili vani' loposo nite' naba gize'ine a'inesi minani' nete gamazi laa' nani' ne'minosa line' ve.

Neze zuhokizo, lingine gatine gili guni ami izipe namuno lili' igi minani' nene hulilo. Ne neiha goloso inite' nene izipe namuno ngomolite nene ngeli damilisanako linginesi goloso inite' nene dami izipe namuno ne'mini minilisani'za nemu' lamuve. Lingine gatine gililizani' nene izipe namuno gatine gilami evene' lodivete gili vevesaa' nani' ne'minisa lingine gatine gili vevesi minilo.
Lengikuti' ve ma mulumo geni initeku' mino ma O'mosola lilive. Ido' mali'mo mulunou' lamine' goloso gelo mino ma O'moso opo'ni nolo nama lilive.

O'moso'mo vetine zopovo si'zilizave lo geni initeli'mi lulou' lengele'mize molaa' neine' ne'mo nene lengele'mize lamine' oloseinako nemu' nene lingine lutine gopo o vivo lutine'mi gizene ana've nene gulu' gelo izo bele vivo lutine gilizevo ogo minaa' neine' nene gohi di oti-di gonou' ele'mizi milalo.

Ido' lingine meteho ve li O'mosola laa' nani'za evene' muki' ize' molo-ledaa' iline' nene gopo evene' mala ninge lamine' o-ledoo mala ninge goloso o-lede minosa nene ize' molo-ledeline' nevoba asi leli' hamo hamo' nene ogo molo olonido' olonido' do molo meni lamine' lemelihe goloso lemelihe iline' nene mo a'mine o nolone' inite' lisihe' o nolidokovo' nene lisihe' ogo golo hizo lemeleseive. Ne'mine iline' nenako lingine olihe goto' numudine Okulumokuko vi minami venenga ve gili me misubouko minilizani' gameneu' nene ezemu' lengehelele izivosa mini monovo lisihe' laminekovo' igi mili minilo.

Ee, lingine gomu' nene lengita geni inite' ato ato' muki' soto' ivo a'mingu' amuzo mili gili ele'vole' igi minani' nenako ne'mi gihile've dalizangisi idise lengehelele izavo a'mine gili ele'vole' ani' nene hulikelizaze. Ha gili ele'vole' igi di minilo. O'moso'mo lemelove lo salani molo-lidine' inite' nene dalone li ma a'mine geni inite' soto' o-lengemelinguti' nene olovo' igi limi ingami amuzo mili gili ele'vole' igivo' minilizani' nenako nemu' nene a'mine gili ele'vole' ilizani' monovotine nene hulami di gili' li di minilo. Amuzo mili gili ele'vole' igi minilizani' nene O'moso'mo menitine naba lengemeleseive.

Gele ele'vole' oga' monovo nene ne'mino neive: Laza O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' o noo ma aza lemelove lo salani molo-lidine' initekumu' gizebo o none' nene olihe damo ido' a'minesi nene ma ningamune' nenako nomihe ido' lemamilihe lo gate sita' gelamo a'mine inite' nene mo ha noloseinako lemavo dalosune lo a'minemu' nene gele ele'vole' ogovo' minelesune.

Nemu' nene naza Guvelesi ve'mi velemu' ogo gamazi mene amuzo molo ti' lo nolo-lingimuve: O'mosomu' gilamave heta ato' ve ingine nene gihile've nomine' initekumukovo' ga'ine gilaa' nani' nenaze. Lingine engi' monovo'nido' nene gohi nge'metamilo.

Ne'mine ine' nenako nemu' nene lingine noso' nite' ma naakumu' nehe malise ogakumu' nehe evene' malite ne'mine ne'mine ilizave lii monovotinemu' ize' mili lii lengemenga lilizani' nene gili ngimamilo. Ido' a'mine'mine igi evenelite holise' minaa' ani' gamene ado' kilisimasilo' kilisimasilo' noso' nite' naba naa' ani' gamenelokisi ike'ni gosoho' soto' ine' gamenelo' gamenelokisi ido' saleleu' saleleukisi nene lingine holise' minaa' naahe minamaa' naahe ne'mine naavo evene' malite a'mine monovotinemu' ize' mili lii lengemenga nilavo ma nene gili ngimamilo.

Nemu' nene O'moso'mi mo'mosi've'mi velela mini gamene gamene go' liha liti'muso iziha kekeize lo neine' numu'veu' nene eze gono've di-di nizavo mo'mosi'velo' minive aza engikisi maka' mino alete molo-ngedaa' oloseive.
Paulo' numunguti' leme heta ogo gipe ne dizo abuti' izo noongo evene' ti' lo lo-ngimine': Lingine ive nama igi muludine hukamivo. Ve ne haza neive.

Nemu' naza O'moso'mo ei' ve lo do kegese-ngede neine' alevemu' nene mulumo geni inite' muki' nene ha gehe'mo vo minaa' nouve. Ee, a'mine aleve Izesu' Kilisitoda igi gi'mizilizadoti' lukuvo ni labana've di ti' igi ezesi minivi' minivi' ilizangumu' ve lo nenita soto' oga' neine' mulumo nite' muki' nene ha gehe'mo vo mino mono' gamazi lo-ngemaa' nouvoni' nene hulosa'muve.

Lingine nene isetine ve li lute ngemaa' monovo di soto' igi ge nabuti' ize ne gabuti' ize li adido' disa minaa' ilo. Hongu lo lamino minaa' monovo neve nene Kilisito' evenele minave lengi' mukita minivo. Moda a'nesi' ve.
Ido' Kilisito'nimu' nene evene' naba lamine' ve li ezemu' lengehelele izivo mini ei' gala gilido' e'meti lingine nene ge gelekele' o-nede ne gelekele' o-gede li minilo.

Nemu' nene lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' zuhokizo, lingine a'mine ne'mine ilizangumu' nene mo gili nizani' ma neize. Lingine monoku' lamine' mine ngi li nizanguti' nene mono'ine nomivete di zovo' zava' izaa' naani' monovo'ine ne'mo nene gelelehe' o-lengedavo limi ingikelizaze. Ehe' igi ningisa minilo.
Lingine Guvelesi ve'mi evenele nizanako nemu' nene vene' lengi' nene vadinge lilizani' gamazilo' nene gelekele' igi gili daakovo' igi minilizado' o neine' nenaze. Gelekele' i-ngidi minilo.
Ido' lihime di'mi nave nene evene' mukiliti ve'nido' nene ngelemezo. Ee, evene' linge nesi nene nemu' golise gili lihime dami hazavo' minilizangisi evene' mukiliti ve'nido' nene ngelemezo.

Nemu' nene laza ge ize' molo-nede ne ize' molo-gede lo minaa' monovo nene hulo gohi amolone. Asi lingine ti' li gili minilo. Leze zuho ma nene limi ingikelizaze. Laza ngele'mize goloso oga' monovo nene amolone.

Ido' engikuti' linge ma nete ololi'mo lo'vote-ngedelesa ine' amuzo've nene di hongu li-daa' ani' ve. Ido' linge ma nene lovo ve nete bainati mite' nedunu' ngibilaa' ani'za ingine olovo' lamine' ikevo bainati mite' ne'mo ngebelamaa' ine' ve. Ido' linge ma ingine gilizevo minanguti' nene amuzo ve lili' igi minaa' ani'. Ido' misubo mauti' ve igi lovo i ngimaa' angu' nene linge ma nete amuzo mili mini ngimiseli di vaa' ani' ve.

Gamazi nene mo osu' nolivo naza ti' lo noluve: Izesu'nimu' gele ele'vole' uvoni' nemu' goboni mili-nidi neni' oko'nelo' nibilani' hu'ne nene Izesu' ei' noso've ne'mino asi've molo-nedavo nouvoni' nenako nemu' nene gohi lihitehe' inite' igi geni nebeleli akalo' nele'mize milalizave lo gelamuve.

Ido' neloti' gohi ma ninguvoni' nene amuzo malehe angelo' mali'mo geheni naba' naba ma ganadise geheni ne'mine nene ma do oto hulo guvo nosou' ogo ti' lo line' ve: Babelonia numuno ebe' naba ma nene ne'minisa nene mili hulikevo evenelitesi nene gohi ma ningamilisave.

Ne neiha lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' alevekizo, lingine neve nene monotine gili ele'vole' iga' nani' ado' O'mosolati' atoli'mine gehepeve o neido' nene mine gili' li mini monoku' naba ilizangumu' nene ge hize ele' o-nede ne hize ele' o-gede li mini O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo amuzo lingimivo minilizadoti' nene O'mosola li mini

Me misubou' minine' monovo danava goloso nene di otuhi minamilo. Asi O'moso'mo lutine gatine do gosoho' o-lengedavo ne'mo nene a'mine gomu' lengemeni dameni do hulosa nene do ato' o-lengedavo minilo. Ne'mine ilizani' nene O'moso'mo igi mili minilizave lo gele neine' monovo ado' monovo lamine' ei' gilido' gehepeve vo daa' neine' monovo ado' aza a'minemu' lanite' gelelido' lisihe' o neine' monovo nene igi mili minilizani' nenako neloti' nene ei' gelaa' neine' monovo nene ningi gililisave.

Ido' naza ve goloso lolo' ogo nouvodo' aposolo nele'mize molangumu' luvoni' nene naza O'moso'mi evenele zuho do goloso o-ngedaa' uve mino aposolo lolo' ogo minelodo' lisihe' amo aposolo minangu' lemo mino gize'ningu' nouvoni' nemu' nene luvoni' ve.

O'moso gelekele' o-damo misubouko minevo' dovo' oga' sunolo' nehe ido' me misubou' minine' inite' golosolo' nehe nene lutine milamilo. Evene' ma ingine lu'ine a'mido' milani' nete lu'ine nene Meteho O'moso imisa'mave.

Ido' a'mela luvoni' ne'mino ne'mine monovo goloso iga' nave muki' nene O'moso'mo lihime molo ngimika' neine' nenako nemu' evene' ma lingine evene' mamu' lihime dikeve li-ngidaa' nave muki' lingine a'mine lihime dikeve li-ngidaa' navete iga' nani' inite' goloso ne'mine nene linginesi iga' nani' nenako O'moso'mo evene' lihime ngemeline' gamenelo' nene lingine lengi' isetine izelive li-imilizani' gamazi ma minamoloseive.

Ee, monoku' guve'inesi ve minani' nete gamazi ma ne'mino imine' molo lo-ngemeline li li-nidamani' ve. Asi monoku' evene' naba numuno langise ne'mini oti minave ve li li-ngidaa' ave Zakobo' ve Petolo' ve Zohane' ve nete lelikumu' nene lingine leli' daa' une' gono ma'mini daa' asive nene nizasive. Nemu' nene laza Zuda vetida mene gono nodunivo lingine nene heta ato' vetida vi gono dalisive li Banabasingisi adelo' dani' ve. Ido' ne'mine li adelo' dani' nene ti' li ningi gilani' nemu' adelo' dani' ve: Petolo' aza oko'ine lolovo huki hulaa' ave Zuda vela aposolo gono dangu' hize ele' o-daa' ive O'moso ne'mo naza heta ato' vetida gono do nouvongu' nene a'mine'mine ogo hize ele' o-nedaa' neine' nene soto' ogo minavo neloti' nene a'mine aposolo ingine Izesu'nimu' gamazi lamine' nene Zuda ve lo-ngemeline lo O'moso'mo Petolo'ni imiseline' ma'mino neze nene Zuda ve minamani' heta ato' vetida vo Izesu'nimu' gamazi lamine' nene lo-ngemeline lo O'moso'mo nimiseline' nemukisi ido' nasahili' o-nedo aposolo lolo' o-nidine' nemukisi nene ningi gilani' nenako nemu' nene heta ato' vetida vi gono dalizo li adelo' dani' ve.

Ido' Izesu'ni nene mo lohoto' zalo' bili badisa ami nene sita've sita've minani' nenako Izesu' genegana've nene ize' sita've sita've mili ize' hamo hamo dika' dika' ani' ve. Ne'mine ani'za lulou' ngolaa' ine' inite've nene olusoku' no'novo've nomine' mo veletati' gala'muda home limivosa lolo' ani' minine' ve.
Nemu' nene gaza evene' ma apize ngemaa' naine' gamazilo' nene geikisi gele dalinako gele dosa'mane. Ee, gaza gumine amozo lo evene' lo-ngemaa' noogosa gaza nene gumine oga' noolosane.
O'moso'mi Sikalahu' nene O'moso'mo lehize-lengedavo lutingu' minevo dovo' ogo minive ei' kekeize numu've nene lengi' okodine nene neive. Lengi' initetine nomive. Nemu' nene gilamani' nehe.

Ido' ne'mine oga' noune' nene Kilisito' lulo leme neine' monovo've ne'mo nene do ote-ledavosa nene oga' noune. Ee, laza ti' lo ize' molo gele none' nenako nemu' nene ne'mine oga' noune: Ve hamo' nene evene' mukito' medelo hiline' nenako nemu' nene evene' muki' nene mo hilani' gele neive.

Nemu' nene neze zuho, O'moso'mo ei' ve lo Okulumoku' voloningumu' lengele'mize molave lingine nene leli' monoku' nene O'moso'mo ei' velemu' ogo imiselavo ave aposolo mino eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' ave naba ne'mine minive naba Izesu'nimu' nene gatine gili minilo.

Ne'mine ogo aka lengelebizuvoni' ma neive. Laza Guvetesi ve Izesu line' gamazi mamu' gelo gono amuzo molo do evene' gulupese hize ele' o-ngedelone lo ne'mi aka'vesi lengelebize osu' lo nouvoni' ma neive. Izesu' line' gamazi nene ne'mino neive: Inite' limikevo dosa muludeu' lamine' gelelesune. Ne neiha inite' ngemeko nemu' muludeu' lamine' gilune' ne'mo nene ivile' o neive.

Ido' vene' vemoho' gopo' napa ingalizani' nene O'moso'mo lihime ngemeleseinako evene' muki' nene vene' vemoho' lili' iga' monovomu' nene gili lamine' i mini di gopo ami lisihe' lamine' igi mini eledingesivo' ido' vadingesivo' ingalizave.
Gomu' vo hetelo gubi' izo gava hizo gonoso galese lulou' ningine' nene Izesu' oko'nolo' asabu' izani' banisi nene a'mingu' haza neivo ningine'za lulou' nene ma dizamine' ve.

Ne'mine lavo a'mido' nene go' pa'na pa'na ogo nolo nolo molo go' ngilili ngilili nolo mimi' naba ma ine' nene mo naba goloso ive. Evene' me misubou' api' ogo soto' ogo mine do dizo idiselasi nonido' nene a'mine mimi' naba goloso ne'mine nene ma amine' ve.

Ne'mine lo-nemavo naza nene opo'ni lo do naba o-delove lo gizeneuko lemo go'ne hizo unguvoni'za aza nene ti' lo lo-nimive: Naza nene haza O'moso'mi gonolo' ve gei' ne'mino minuve gei' zuho gehepeve ado' Izesu' gamazi've di mini hizi ele' iga' ave lengikuti' ne nouze. Gaza ne'mine o-nedamo asi O'mosovo' nene opo'ni lo do naba o-dezo. Mene noluvoni' nene nanitekumu' ve. O'moso'mi veleti' gamazi li soto' iga' ave muki' nete nene Izesu' gamazi'vevo' hizi ele' iga' naanako nemu' nene noluve.

Ee, gomu' a'mine otohato gamazi nene suno' minine'za idise leli' nene mo gelekune. O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo inite' muki' nene do soto' oga' neive. Ido' O'moso'mi monovo danava hito neine' nesi nene do soto' ogo ningaa' neine' nenako O'moso'mo a'mine Sikalahu've nene imiselavo a'mine ne'mo nene O'moso lute emaa' une' aleve leli' do va'va' o-lidine' inite' lamine' nene idise lelebizave. A'mine inite' lamine' do va'va' o-lidingumu' nene mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizani' ma neive: Evene' hamolitesi ve'inedunu' ningamani' initekisi ido' li soto' amavo a'minemu' ma gilamani' initekisi ido' ga'ine gili hehe laa' angu' ogo soto' amivo olihe gilamani' initekisi nene O'moso'mo leli' lute emaa' une' aleve nene do va'va' o-lidine' ma neive. Ne'mine li gizi nizani' ma neine'za idise nene Sikalahuli'mo a'mine gamazi nene lelebizavosa lo soto' oga' noune.
Ne'mine olosuze. Lengi' nene Izesu' Kilisito' zuholiti sunolo' e'meti longolize naba izi minisa ele'mize lamine' ilo. Lingine nene ne'mine vemu' gilavoo dizosa minelido' o neive.
Ido' izipe lengi' nene izetingine metingine gelekele' i-ngidi minilizani' nene Guvelesi ve'mo gilivo mulunou' lamine' oloseize. Gamene gamene gelekele' i-ngidivo' minilo.

Ido' ne'mine noluvoni' nene nemu' noluve: Leli' luteu' nene ti' lo gele ele'vole' ogo none: Me misubou' aleveti vovo'ningu' ogo molo une' nene me misubou' aleve gilavo otohato monovo ve laa' nani' monovolo' nene e'metamo asi O'moso'mi nasahili've ne'mo hize ele' o-ledo neivo monovote nene do zovo' zava' izo soza nite' amo O'moso'mo gilivo lisihe' iline' initekovo' nene ogo molo minune' ve. Ido' lengita nene a'mine monovolo' nene e'mete gehepeve ogo ogo molo minune' ve. Ido' luteu' nene ne'mine lo gele ele'vole' ogo minaa' noune' nenako leli' monovotemu' nene lolize izaa' noune.

Evene' ma ingine neni' gamazi'ne di mini a'mido' gili di minaa' nave nene mo lu'ine laminetoti' nimaa' nave nene nizave. Ido' a'mine lu'ine laminetoti' nimaa' nave nene me'neho lulo ngemeleseive. Ne'mine neivo nazasi nene lu'ne ngemo neni' nemeni dameni ngelebizelesuve.

A'mine laa' ani' gamazi ne'mo nene okodeloti' monokumu' lanite' gelo amuzo molo e'metaakumukisi ido' leli' okode nene lanite' gelamiline' inite' o-do do limune' gelo minaakumukisi nene laa' neine' nenako a'mine neve nene otohato gamazi gele neine'za a'mine lemeni dameni litehe ne'mo lanite' giline' monovo nene do leme-doo e'metamo mineloningumu' nene mo keke' hize ele' o-ledesa'mive.

Luka ngemaningumu' nene a'mine aleve nete Izesu' evenele mulise milangu' li soto' igi gopo'ni laa' nave. Ido' a'ne'mine aleve lengita igi nivavo ma O'moso'mo gelavo lisihe' lamine' ilido' do molo akala vilizangu' inite' ma vise' ilizani' inite' nene do soto' ogo ngemo ngele'mizo viline' nene lamine' oloseive.

Ido' gihile've nomine' getipe gamazi ado' gamazi monovo gilamavete laa' nani' gamazi ne'mine li mono' monovomu' gamazidunu' ge hulo ne hulo laa' ne'mo nene lovo lolize do soto' oga' neine' nene mo gele nane' ma neive. Nemu' nene gaza a'mingu' vo holamo mehenga emezo.

Ee, laza mukito' Mose' inite' velelo' hitosa minaa' ine' ne'mino minamo asi mukito' nene vete haza soto' o neivo mino gapogapoli'mo silingenge'ni gohi do tine' molo hulo mala oga' neine' ne'mino Guvelesi ve'mi monovo've vode vaa' neine' monovo've nene lelitati' hulo evene' mala oga' noune. A'mine monovo've lamine' goloso lelita minine' nene vo naba o'mo voovo' neivo laza nene ei' Guvelesi ve'mi emeni damenilo' gehepeve lisihe' ogosa medelo minaa' noune. Ido' ne'mine noune' nene O'moso'mi Sikalahuli'mo nene oga' noune.

Ido' neve nene inite' ngomoli'mo okodida sihononi ne'mine hitine' nene do lamine' oga' neine' nenako inite' naba Kilisito' vanise've ne'mo monovotine goloso labuluvo oga' akau' lengele'mize molaa' neine' neti lihime lutine gatingu' nene gilite hulo-lengedo minevo' minevo' O'moso gelekele' i-di gubi' izi imi minilizado' nene do lisihe' o-lengedelido' nene mo lisihe' gehepeve o neive. Ee, O'moso'mi minevo' minevo' Sikalahu've ne'mo Kilisito'ni hize ele' o-davo aza oko'nolo' lihime hamokisi minamine' mino oko'no've hulo O'moso imine' nenako ne'mo nene leli' lute do lamine' o-ledelido' lisihe' o neive.

Laza Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito'nimu' gele ele'vole' okunivo O'moso'mo leze lehize-lidine' inite' Sikalahu've nene a'mine ma'mino engikisi lehize-ngidine' ma ve. Nemu' naza amuzo malehe noosa eze o've lo-delohe.

Ne'mine igi mini O'moso'mo ei' ve lo meni hizi ve leli' nene alinge' mudise do lu' izo lele'mize eita ilingumu' ve lo noso molo ei' Sikalahu've lehize-lidine' nenako nemu' lingine O'moso'mi Sikalahu' aza nene goloso gelo muhele' ogo mineline' inite' ne'mine i-damilo.

Nemu' nene li-lingimikevo ganakuti' gili dani' monokumu' nene gohi gatine gilisa a'mido' e'meti mini lutine di velepe' izilo. Ido' ne'mine ami upuho' igi ma otamilizani' nene naza guminelo' ve alizani' gamenemu' gilamavo iga' naani' ne'minosa nene alosuve. Lingine nene naza aloni' gamenemu' ma gilami nizavosa nene lengita ogo hetelelesuve.

Izipaha'ne zuho mate, ingine monovo lisihe' lamine' igi mili i minaa' nave nene Izesu' aza ve lisihe' lamine' minine' ne'mini evene' lisihe' lamine' nizave. Nemu' malite ato' gamazi li lengele'mize gopo ikelizave.

Lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' mate, O'moso'mi gamazi lo soto' oga' unive polohete none li sozasi laa' ave muki' soto' igi misubou' misubou' nimonanako nemu' engikuti' ve ma lengita igi soza gamazi li-lingimikevo gili ngimikelizave. Nemu' nene linginela igi Sikalahuli'mo lele'mize akalo' o-lede neive li mono' li-lingimaa' ave muki' gopo gili-ngimaa' nani' monovotine nene hulilo. Gopo gili ngimami gamazi muki' nene O'mosolati' nehe atokuti' nehe li gili ningilo.

Neze zuhokizo, gamazi nene mo gize lengemekuvoni'za ma neine' nene lo-lengemeloze. Gililo. Guvelesi vemu' nene longolize iziisa nene minilo. Gomu' lo-lingimuvoni' gamazi gohi gize lengemaakumu' nene naza giluvo gosele' nebelamive. Ido' gohi gize lengemeloni' meve nene lengi' gopo aka vilizadoti' nene alete molo-lengedeline' nenako nemu' nene ti' lo nolo-lingimuve:

Lingine igi di nubo ilizangu' nene ve linge ma gomu' igi heteli nizavo ga'na ngolavo alinge' alizavemu' gilami gomu' imi mini noso' nite' nalizani' ne'mo Guvelesi ve'mo lihime lengemeline' akau' mini milikelizanako nemu' nene noso' nite' ngomo numu'nidati' gomu' nikisavo' nene alizave. Ido' nemu' gamazi gohi ma lo-lengemeloni' neine' nene naza lingine nizada alongu' nene lo-lengemelesuve.

Ne'mine likevo Pilato' aza ti' lo line' ve: Langisetine nene ele'mizi vi lengi' lou' gamazitine'mo lido' e'metisa goni' i-di lihime imilo. Ne'mine lavo Zuda ve ingine ti' li lani': Ne neiha leli' lou' gamazite'mo lido' nene mo bele helelonido' lisihe' o neiha Loma ve lingine evene' lihime ngimi ngibili hilaa' nene leli' Loma vevo' ne'mine olosune li mo o'ove li-lidi nizani' ma neive li lani'.

Ne neiha lingine nene polohete lolo' oga' amuzo nehe mono' laa' amuzo nehe evene' do lamine' o-ngedaa' amuzo nehe ne'mine amuzo ato ato' muki' mini'mi vanguti' dizo noline' amuzo nene do minelone li amuzo milalo.

Ido' aza ne'mine ve'mo eveneto' medelo mino O'moso inite' lehize-daa' ivete naba mino goloso ogo minunidoti' lele'mize lamine' ilido' lisihe' o neine' nenako ha do lu' izo lele'mize lamine' oloseive. A'mine ve nene aza ve lamine' atoli'mine ogo mino lulo do gopo o-deline' inite' hamokisi eita ma nomine' mino lihime daa' nani' aleve ne'mino minamo atoli'mine gehepeve ogo mino okulumo' nesi ivile' ogo osu' lo dizosa neive.
Ee, nanite' nanite' soto' o-nedelihe a'mine mukiku' nene do amuzo molo-nedaa' ive Kilisitoda nene lehete o mino ele'vole' ogo ha ogo molo minelodo' o nouve.
O'moso'mo ne'mine igi minilizave lo gelo ti' lo laa' neive: Vene' vemoho' gopo' napa' monaa' nene huli evene' kekeize ve, ve lisihe' lamine' minilizave lo laa' neive.
Ido' O'mosola li minilizani' nene hulami laakovo' igi minilo. Ido' ne'mini O'mosola li minilizangu' nene lutine okise ongamivoo gilingili igi O'moso nene isaa' neve li-di minilo.
Ne'mine lavo Mose' aza gelo golise Midiani misubou' vo venenga ve gelo minine'. Mino vene' do gipele sita' gidine' ve.

Lingine mo gili nizave. Leze monovola nene godotela inite' ma do geheso' nene monovo ne'mino neive: Evene' leze gizebo vete ma neive losa godotelo' nene inite' ma gehaa' noune. Ne neine'za O'moso ne'mo vemoho' nene ei' avazaha ei' ne'minosa lolo' ogavosa ne'mo nene vemoho' ivile' igi miniliza inite' nene ma minamani' ve. Nemu' nene ve mali'mo O'mosola lilihe O'moso'mi veleti' gamazi lo soto' ilihe ne'mine noilingu' godololo' inite' ma gehe mino liline' nene ei' godolo nene do u'musupo lizine' geleleseinako nemu' nene inite' ma gehamosa lilive. Ne neine'za O'moso'mo vene' nene vemoho' avazaha ne'mine lolo' ogo hize ele' ilingumu' ve lo do soto' o-dine' ve. Nemu' nene vene' ma aza O'mosola lilihe O'moso'mi veleti' gamazi ma lo soto' ilihe ne'mine noilingu' godololo' inite' ma gehamo liline' nene ei' godolo've ma nene do u'musupo lize-deleseinako godololo' inite' gehosavo' lilive. Ido' vene' ma aza godololo' inite' ma gehamiline' nene monovo golosolokovo' monaa' ani' alu nene godo'nido' inite' gihamaa' naanako aza nene engi' ne'mine mineleseinako godolo zopovo nene monovo golosolo' monaa' ani' alu huki-ngidaa' ani' ne'mini huki-dilisave. Ido' vene' aza godo'ne zopovo huki-nidikevo novozo helo minalove lo gelo ma godololo' nene inite' ma gehelive.

Kilisito' elese molo-lengedo lengele'mize eita ine' nene lingine lutine hamo' ogavo hongu li laminivo' minilizave losa ne'mine ine' nenaze. Lingine ne'mine mana'mine inite' ilisa gilii ma nene gomu' a'mine initekumu' ize' mili di ningi Kilisitodati' hongu lo lamino minaa' monovolo' nene e'metilizani' aka vele-lengedeline' initekovo' ilo. Ne'mine igi mini O'moso isaa' neve li opo'ni li minilo.

Ido' O'moso'mo Izesu'ni imiselo mulumo alumo gelo helelive line' nene nanitekumu' ve. Izesu' nene do lu' izeline' gono dalido' olihe lisihe' gehepeve amo minine' nenako nemu' mulumo alumo gelo heleline' ne'mo a'mine leli' do lu' izeline' gono nene dalido' do lisihe' gehepeve o-delingumu' mulumo alumo gelo helelive lo O'moso'mo imiseline' ve. Ido' izipahala vai' lele'mize molo atoli'mine ogo do lamine' o-ledelesa gono do'mo vo mininguti' nene O'moso aza leli' gomu' molo lemo akate velo do lu' izelive Izesu' mulumo alumo gelo helelive lo imiseline' ne'mo nene monovo do lamine' goloso ine' ve. Ee, inite' mata' muki' ei' inite've eikumukovo' mini di dizilizave lo do soto' molave evene' naba O'moso aza Izesu'ni nene do lu' izelido' do lisihe' o-delesa mulumo alumo gelo helelive lo imiseline' ne'mo nene monovo do lamine' goloso ine' ve.

Ido' gamazi gohi ma lo-lengemeloze: Linginela lingizebolo' molavo lovo hizi minaa' nani' nene naniteli'mo ve. Lingine lanite' gili ahu' lani' inite' nete lutingu' lovo di soto' ikevo ne'mo lovo hizaa' nave.

Evene' muki' nete lengi' muliseu' nene vene' vemoholite iga' ani' monovo goloso ma soto' neive li li'mi nimonave. A'mine inite' nene mono' gilamaa' avetingukisi isa'mani' inite' atoli'mine goloso ve. A'mine inite' nene evene' ma lengi' muliseu' neiveli'mo melehi elenahine dave.

Lengita lengemengu' soto' o lengemaa' neine' nene atoli'mine soto' o lengemamive. Evene' mukita soto' oga' neine' ma'mino nene soto' noo lingimive. Ido' O'moso'mo leze nene hulo-ledamoloseinako lingine ezemu' gili ele'vole' gehepeve i mini ezela lehete igi minilo. Aza nene lingivizeline' lengemengu' ma soto' o lengemeline' nene ma ninge mate lingimikamoloseive. Lengemengu' ma soto' o lengemeline' nene lingivizamivo amuzo mili ha mine gili' li minilizave lo aza nene olovo' ilizani' aka vele-lengedeleseive.
Naza hulo-lengedekuvo evene' malite gulo hadene lili' igi vovotingu' heteli Izesu' evenele zuho lutine di gopo i-lingidilisave losa gele nouve.

Lengi' goboni mili-lingidi mulumo nite' i-lingidivi' i-lingidivi' igi minaa' navo mulumo gili minangu' nene Izesu'nimu gili ele'vole' anitine nesi hulami amuzo mili minaa' ani' ve. Ne'mine ani' ne gelo O'moso'mi evenele zuho muki' mini'mi monada lengikumu' longopo'ni lo gulivetine do hozi laa' noune.
Evene' hamolitesi O'moso mo ningamune. Lute ne geme ge neme lo minelone' nene O'moso'mo lezesi bizo luteu' neivo lute imune' nene apa nite' amivo laminetokovo' lute eme gili' lo minelesune.

Ido' Izesu' monovomu' gililizani' nene aza mo hize ele' o-ledeline' nenako nemu' nene lingine monoku' amuzo molaakumu' gosele' lengebelavo lutine nene vo gilizevo ogalive li lihime daa' ave nete Izesu'ni biluva' i-daa' angu' amuzo molo minine' mamu' nene gili minilo.
Ee, ezela gi'mizo mino ei' hilidi'mine ogo lazasi maka' hilune' giline' nenako nemu' nene aza hilinguti' otidi'mine ogo lazasi nene ha ote none' gilivosa minelesune.
Ido' ma nene ti' li gizi nizani' ve: Heta ato' ve lingine O'moso'mi evenelesi makato' longolize izi minilo.

Ne neiha O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo ti' lo lo soto' ogo lo-leme neine' ma neive: Alinge' nela nene evene' ma ingine mono' gihile di mini minilizanguti' nene hulisa go'ine izaa' nani' sikalahuta nene vi gi'mizi sikalahu' golosolati' minine' mono' gamazi apizi ngimaa' naado' nene e'metilisave.

Gei' gizebou' minani' evene' nene gamazi do gosoho' ogo ti' lo lo-ngeme ngeme' ogo minezo: Ingine ngamanisi ido' ngamani gono di lelito' gizebo igi minaa' avesi gelekele' i-ngidi gamazi'ine gili dalizave. Alinge' gono lamine' atoli'mine atoli'mine nasahili' oga' gono ne'mine soto' iline' nene ha dalone li amuzo mili gili minilizave.

Ne'mine laa' naani'za ado' mene lo-lengemeloni' gamazimu' nene gelalone li ga'ine hizi ngi likeve: Ado' O'moso'mo lavo Okulumo' nene gozopo' aka'mila soto' ivo misubo nesi nene nosouti' soto' ogo noso veleta gala'muda minavo oluso' minine' ve.

Ee, Kilisito' azasi nene mulumo alumo gelo hiline' ve. Aza nene ve lisihe' minine'za O'mosola do bize-ledelesa evene' goloso leli' lihimetemu' lelito' medelo hiline' ve. Ido' a'mine gamene hamokovo' hiline' a'ne'mo nene leli' mukiliti lihimete nene mo osu' lilido' vo dani' ve. Aza neve nene evene' leli' okode ne'minesi neivosa nene bili hilani'za sikalahu've nene O'moso'mo do upuho' o-davo vele gizosa

Ee, O'moso'mo lo-lidine' gamazi ma li-ngimikevo gilisa a'mine gamazi gili huli mehe'ine ma imado' nene golo hizo lihime atoli'mine ogo ngemelido' o neine' nenako ingine nene a'mine aka lisihekumu' nene ma gilami minadiniko a'mine lihime do dizo ngemeline' votigileloti' nene lemosa lihime ngemelido' minadinako ne'mo nene mo lamine' ngomo ma idine.

Leze zuhokizo, Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' ei' velemu' ogo ti' lo lo huko nolo-lingimune. Izesu' evenele zuho linge ma nete mono' gamazi lo-lingimune' nene gili huli ha gopo moni gono damani' nene inginela vi gi'mizami mini abaza' igi minilo.

Nemu' nene laza ti' lo gele none: Me misubou' lihime soto' ine' nene ve hamoli'mo do soto' ogavo a'mine lihime ne'mo nene helaa' monovo do soto' ine' ve. Ne'mine ogavo evene' muki' nene lihime daa' noune' nenako helaa' nene leli' mukita soto' o limine' ve.
