A'mine ve ingine O'mosomu' gili ele'vole' igi minadi'mo O'moso'mo hize ele' o-ngedo neivo engikuti' linge ma nete amuzo mili misubo mala mala vi O'mosomu' gilamave nene lovo i ngimi ngivile' igi engita di gelekele' i-ngidani'. Ido' engikuti' linge ma nete engi' misubo'ningu' nene monovo lisihe' laminekovo' minelive li evene' di lisihe' i-ngidaa' ani' ve. Ido' O'moso'mo ne'mine mana'mine inite' do soto' o-ngedelove lo lo huko-ngidine' gamazi nesi nene engita gihile izaa' ine' ve. Ido' engikuti' evene' linge ma nete loposo gulo laioni nete ngibililisa ikevo ma a'mine laizoni nete libilikelizave li evene' nete aka'ine nene hizi tili-ngidaa' ani' ve.
Ido' libililisasi nene vise' i-lidaa' nani'za O'moso ne'mo ma hulo-ledesa'mive. Ido' libilikevosasi nene lemo ongaa' nouba goloso gehepeve nene ma dosa'mune.

Lingine nene vene' ma va'ningine huli ve gohi malo' vaa' ave ne'mine mini O'mosomu' lungumo hiline' nene huli me misubou' ve O'mosomu' gili hulani' alevemukisi ido' engi' inite'inemukisi lungumo heleline' ne'mo O'moso mehedine imaa' ido' lovo i imaa' o neine' ne gilamahe.
Ne'mine ikevo Asia misuboukosi mono' li-ngimamilizave lo O'moso'mi Sikalahuli'mo aka hize tile-ngedavo Piligia misuboukosi ido' Galatia misuboukosi mono' gamazi lamine' li-ngimi' ngimi' i'mi vani'.

Ne'mine lavo angelo' naba vanu ne'mo vo ei' lapese'veu' minine' inite' goloso nene lepe hulo misubouko ine' ve. Ne'mine ogavo evene' ma ingine loposo niteli'mi maki've di mini a'mine loposo niteli'mi avazahalo' gubi' izi imi opo'ni li minaa' aveti oko'nido' nene huso goloso galasa gehepeve nene izeka' izeka' o'mo vine' ve.

Ido' a'mine buku nene do anau' ogavo a'mine ele'vole' igi ve'inesi ha minaa' nani' inite' seta've seta've nesi ido' gizebo ve tuvedi fo'a (24) nesi nene a'mine sipisipi angale'mi velela nene limi go'ine hizi ingani' ve. Ingine hamo hamo' nene musiki molaa' inite' gulive hapu nesi ido' ngolidunu' lili' ani' luduno lapeseu' nene gizikevo unuvo lamine' oga' ine' inite' vai' lo minine' nesi nene di minani' ve. Ido' a'mine unuvo lamine' oga' ine' inite' nene O'moso'mi evenelelite O'mosola laa' naani' gamazi neve nene minine' ve.

Ve malite Izesu'nimu' nene aza do lu' izelive lo O'moso'mo imiselelesa live neive li gili ele'vole' ilizani' nene O'mosolati' soto' igi izipahala zuho lili' igi nizave. Ido' ve ma ingine lu'ine me'nibine imi ma izipahala zuhosi ngimilisave.

Laza leli' okode do dize dize' ogo ne givile' o-gede ge nivile' o-nede lo mino ge mulu'neu' hizo do goloso o-nede ne mulungau' hizo do goloso o-gede lamo lamino mino a'minguti' ma livile' igi minilizangumu' nene lukehe ngebelamo minelesune.

Gaza vemoho' ozoho ne'mine nene gamazi amuzonga lo-emamo gei' maho gehepeve gele neivosa gala do gamazi lo-emezo. Ido' izipe goso've nene nakuna gehepeve ne'mine gili minavosa ga'ine do gamazi lo-ngemezo.

O'moso'mi evenele minamaveti zuhoti vovo'ningu' minilizangu' lingine igi mili ilizani' nene mo monovo lisihe' laminekovo' nene igi mili minilo. Ee, ingine lengikumu' evene' goloso ve li divi ledivi' i-lingidi laa' naha ne'mine i-lingidi minilizangukisi monovo lamine' igi mili iga' ilizani' nene ningi mini' mini' ilizadi'mo O'moso'mo monovo'nido' ogo do ningeline' gamenelo' ingine nene a'mine monovote laminekumu' O'moso opo'ni lilizangumu' ve li monovo lisihe' laminekovo' igi mili minilo.

a'mine Halisaio' monokumu' gilingili ogo minuvodi'mo nene Izesu' evenele zuho goboni mala' mala' o-ngedaa' uvoni' ve. Mose' lou' gamazi've ne'mo ve lisihe' minilizave nete nene ne'mine ne'mine ilisaave lido' nene e'mete osu' lo naza nene a'mine lou' avuto' amo gamazi'ne nomine' minuvoni' ve.

Ne'mine ikevo umungive nene nani gamenelo' lamine' gele nolihe lo a'minemu' gelelesa longo' o-ngidine'. Ne'mine ogavo ingine ti' li li-imani': Oko'nolo' olo' line' nene aize' holise' vanu kiloku ne'mido' nene hulo-dive.

A'mine gamenelo' sigisi kilokuloti' holise' minilizangumu' di va'va' iga' ani' gamene neivo ido' a'mine holise' nene holise' naba goloso neine' nenako Zuda ve nete a'mine holiseku' nene a'mine ngibilave lohoto' zalo' ha minikelizave li Pilato' lavo gize'ine amuzo di ledisa lohoto' zaloti' apasi di mili-ngidilizave li ezela lani' ve.

Ne'mine lidoti' nene Pilato' aza Izesu'ni kuluhize-delesa aka vise' o'mo vine'za Zuda ve ingine geke' geke' li ti' li li minani' ve: Gaza ve mene ma kuluhize-deline' nene ve ma ingine guve'inesi ve lolo' ilisa ave nene Kaesale' mo'mosi've dalisa biluva' i-daa' nani' nenako gei' nene Kaesale'ni hize ele' i-daa' aveti zuhouti' nomo nolosane.

Ne'mine lo Izesu' imine' molo ti' lo line': Lingine lutingu' nanite' soto' o-ledelivo li gili lengemeni balala loka' loka' ivo nizani' nene mo alamilo. Asi O'mosomu' gili ele'vole' igi nenikumukisi nene gili ele'vole' igi minilo.

Ne'mine mana'mine inite' nanite' nanite' ne'mine soto' ilihe. A'mingukisi lingine nene Kilisito' gamazi lamine' gilavete igi mili minilizado' lisihe' o minine' monovolokovo' nene e'meti igi mili minilo. Ne'mine igi nizavo naza ogo ninge-lengedelohe ido' hota mino lengikumu' gamazi gelelohe oloni' nene lingine ongovango lamii ha lutine di hamo' i mini monoku' oti pehe li mini monoli'mi lovou' nene maka' makato' lutine gatine hamo' minivo biluva' i-lingidaa' avete ne'mine mana'mine inite' i-lingidilizangumu' nene lengehelele izamivo gili ele'vole' i nizani' gamazi lamine' di otilisa nene makato' amuzo mili nizavoo ningo gelelove. Ne'mine igi minilizani' ne'mo a'mine biluva' i-lingidaa' ave vi tolovo ilizangumu' nene ngelebizosa lingine lukuvo nalizangumu' nene lengelebizeleseive. Ne'mino soto' iline' nene O'moso'mo laavosa eitati' nene soto' oloseive.

Lengi' nene gomu' apizi neni' nene lengi' ve li ma di ti' amave. Asi neni' neve lengi' do ti' uvoni' nene vi gono dikevo minevo' minevo' iline' gihile nene izelive losasi ido' lingine neni' ve'nemu' igi me'nehida voku' nanitekumu' lilizahe a'mine inite' nene lengemelive losasi do ti' o-lingiduvoni' ve.

Ido' Adamu' gipele Kainiki Abeliki ingine inite' oloku' gizi O'moso imasinguti' Abeli' aza nene O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo minine' ne'mo uvoloho Kaini'ni nene ivile' ogosa monovolo laminekisi minidoti' inite' lamine' oloku' gize imine' ve. Ne'mine ogavo O'moso aza mo lamine' ve lo dani' nenako ne'mo Abeli' aza ve lisihe' minine' nene mo lelebizavo ningo nogilune. Ido' Abeli' aza nene mo helani' ma neine'za O'mosomu' ne'mino gele ele'vole' ogo minine' ne'mo gamazi've nene ha minivo gelaa' noune.
Lingine lelikumu' nene Kilisito' gonolo' ve mini O'moso'mi gamazi suno' minido' gizebo igi li-ngimi ngimi' iga' ave ma nene nizave lisa gili minilo.
Ido' hepe' nabali'mo gohuno za do mo'mongo' ogavo gihile've di'mozaa' naani' ne'mino okulumoto' minani' sonohi' nene misubouko di'moze' moze' ani' ve.

Ido' Mose' miningu' minave nene O'moso'mo lihime ngemo ngibiline' ma'mino lengebelalize. Nemu' nene neze zuho lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' mate, soza o'moso nene gelekele' i-ngidami ido' noso' nite' ngimilizanguti' nesi nami ngopo'ni laa' monovomu' nene olovo' igi mehedine ngimilo.
Ido' goloso monovo ne'mo nene lingivile' ogalize. Asi monovo lamine' igi mili minilizani' ne'mo nene monovo goloso nene ivile' igi di limi-di minilo.

A'mine noluvoni' gamazi mene lo ga'ine ogo lo-ngemo mono' gamazimu' nene lovo lolize amilizave lo O'moso'mi velelo' nene ga'ine do lo-ngedezo. Ne'mino lovo lolize oga' ne'mo nene inite' gihile ma do soto' amosa asi a'mine lolize gamazi gililizave nene ngele'mize goloso oloseive.

Lingine O'mosola vi gi'mizilizani' nene aza linginela a'mine'mine ogo gi'mizeleseive. Lingine goloso inite' daa' nave a'mine inite' alo' hulilo. Ido' O'mosola volohe goloso initeta volohe li ve'nehe' ka'nehe' nilani' nene huli lutine noso izi di lamine' ilo.
evene' ma siza li-ngidi evene' ma ningi gosele' ilizani' nene lihime dalizani' o neive. Ido' ne'mine ilizani' nene O'moso'mo lo huko line' gamazi avuto' iga' ave minikeve loloseive.
O'moso'mo lengele'mize molani' nene vene' vemoho' gopo' napa' monanguti' lutine nene goloduvosi minilingumu' ve livoba lutine nene guluvi' lamine' lisihe' minilingumu' ve lo lengele'mize molani' ve.

Lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' mate, lute ngemaa' nene O'mosolati' neine' nenako nemu' laza lute ne geme ge neme lo minuke'zo. Ingine evene' lu'ine ngimi nasahili' i-ngidi minilizave nene O'mosolati' soto' adite ilisave. Ingine O'mosomu' mo ningi gili nizave ve.
Ne neiha evene' linge ma evene' mamu' mulu'ningu' goloso ogavo lukehe ngibili minisa laza labanaku' none li laa' nave nene ingine olihe labanaku' ami liti'musou' ha nizave.

Ido' lingine Kilisito' evenele lili' igi eze gulive di minangumu' lingilimaa' navo ma nene guvelesi neine' O'moso'mi Sikalahu' neve nene lengito' omo mino mine do viline' nenako nemu' nene lingine longolize izi minilizado' o neive.
Ningo ngopo'ni lo Paulo' aza heta ato' vetida eze gono do'mo nomonivo O'moso'mo inite' muki' ogo molo ine' ne'mi gamazi vetete' ogo osu' lo lo-ngimine'.
Lengikuti' ve mali'mosi neni' monovo goloso do noloni' nene ngelo ma do soto' amoloseinako nemu' nene naza gamazi gihile noluvoni' nenako nanimu' gili ele'vole' amave.
Ido' ne'mine lo neloti' alinge' gamazi gohi ma ti' lo line': Ido' evene' engita lihime minine' mamu' nesi ido' lou' gamazi avuto' iga' nani' mamukisi nene gohi ga'ne gelamolosuve.

Neze zuhokizo, naza amuzo molo ti' lo longo' noo-lingiduve: Lingine Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito'nimu' ve li ido' O'moso'mi Sikalahuli'mo lute ne geme ge neme lo minaa' monovo do soto' o-ledaa' neingumu' ve li naza amuzo molo O'mosola laa' nouvodi'mine igi linginesi imine' mili nenikumu' nene amuzo mili O'mosola li'mi vi minilo.
Ne'mine lavo a'mida minave muki' ingine ti' li li-imani': Laza ma gebelelesa gelamuniko sikalahu' golosoli'mo do dudu lo-gedavo negi gamazi nolabe.

Ido' a'mine gamenelo' nene mo hepe' noilivo gelekele' vesi ido' pilisi vesi nene olo' si'nibulo' nene ingi vite' iki lahizi minani' ve. Ne'mine igi nizavo Petolo' nesi nene a'mida ote mino lahizo minine' ve.

Satani ne'mo gotine izo do gopo'napa o-lengedo lingivile' olosa iline' nene lingine mo limi ingami ha ele'vole' igi oti minilizangumu' ve li O'mosolati' lovo hizaa' inite' muki' nene di okodida igisa minilo.
Ne'mine lavo Petolo' aza ti' lo lo-imine': Guvekasi ve, idise nene nanitekumu' ge'meto vamolove. Gaza libililiza akalo' volosa noliline' nene naza nene geikumu' oko'ne nene ha hulolosuve.

Ne'mine ikevo Izesu' Kilisitoda gi'mizi nizani' ne'mo O'mosolati' hongu monovo've ado' leli' evenelitesi gelaa' noune' nene ivile' goloso ivosa atoli'mine neine' ne'mo nene lutido' gatido' nene alete molo-lengedo gizebo oloseive.
Vete nahunodunu' Guvetesi ve Metehine opo'ni laa' noune. Ido' O'moso eze gidini do soto' ine' evene' nene a'mine vete nahunodunu' gamazi goloso lo-ngedaa' noune.

Nene luvoni' nene me misubou' aleve O'mosomu' gilamani' heta ato' aleve ma gopo'napa monanikisi ido' mumuzo' iga' avesi gumine gizengize vesi ido' soza o'mosomu' ngopo'ni laa' avesi mudise huli-ngidi mini kegesi minilo luvodini ne'mine ve misubo vaito' mini'mi monaa' nani' nenako huli-ngidi mini kegesilisa huli-ngidi zaa' misubola vadine. Lingine misubo muki' huli mala ngeli vamilisanako ma mini kegesilizave luvodini ngeli ne'mine amilizado' luvodine.
Ido' gozopo' nene na'nise'ne neve Nasalete ve Izesu' mono' do goloso olosa gono naba dalove lo ga'ne gelaa' uvoni' ma neive.

Ingine vene' ma ningani' nene ma duvo lii gumine dika' dika' igi lihime daa' monovo nene engitati' osu' losa'mivo monoku' amuzo'ine nomive nene lihime monovou' ngimimise' igi di vaa' igi mini mumuzo' oga' monovomu' api'napi' igi save naba di minani' nenako nemu' nene O'moso'mo usi' ize-ngedelido' i nizave.

Ido' monimu' sipisipi izelo' gizebo gono daa' ave sipisipi me'ninge minamani' nete nene loposo gulo navo ningilizani' nene sipisipi ize huli-ngidi golise vilisave. Ne'mine ikevo a'mine loposo gulo nene ogo sipisipi ize ma belo gelelehe' o-do novivo sipisipi ize linge nene hutile' igi vilisave.

Neze zuho lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' mate, gamazi mene gililo. Lingine muki' nene gamazi gelaakumu' lite' li di nene igi minilo. Ne neiha gamazi laakumu' nene zou li gili minisa lilo. Ido' linginela lite' lo lingizebolo' molamivo.

Ido' a'mine'mine ogo Guvelesi ve'mi gamazi've lamine' nene di vi li soto' i ngimaa' ilizave ingine nene li soto' i ngimilizavelati' noso' nite'ine di nalisave lo asi've Guvelesi ve'mo lo hukine' ma neive.
Naza me misubou' uvoni' nene labana' ne'minosa uvoni' nene ve ma ingine nenikumu' gili ele'vole' iga' nave muki' nene liti'muso monovou' mini mili minikelizave losa uvoni' ma neive.

Ne'mine ogosa a'mine ve nene alinge' mono' numuno nabau' neivo Izesu' ningo ti' lo lo-dine': Ningezo. Gaza nene mo lamine' ogange. Gomu' goloso ogo minaine' nene ivile' ivosa goloso gehepeve ogalinge. Gaza nene lihimeka hulo gohi damozo.
Inite' igi mili ilizani' muki' nene haza igi mili ami nasahili' ido' mangi ido' lutine ngemaa' monovotidotikovo' nene igi mili minilo.
Lingine lutine nimi nizani' noline' nene naza lo-lingimuvoni' gamazi nene gili di minilisave.

Ee, O'moso'mi gamazi Izesu' lo-lingimine' nene hulikelizaze. Gizebo lamine' igi minilo. Ingine O'moso'mi gamazi misubou' mene Mose' lo-ngimine' gili hulave nene O'moso'mo ngebelelinguti' olovo' igi golise viliza aka'ine ma minamivo aza lihime ngemaa' neine' nenako nemu' O'moso'mi gamazi nene Okulumokuti' lo-limine' nenako gele hulolone' nene laza O'moso'mo lihime lemelinguti' nene mo keke' ngelo olovo' amolosunako nemu' nene a'mine gamazi nene gili hulikelizaze. Gizebo lamine' igi minilo.
Mo lamineto' gomu' lingine heta ato' ve mini O'mosomu' gilamani' gameneu' nene soza inite' O'moso gihile lamine' minamado' nene gelekele' igi minaa' ani'za
Gana' Zuda ve lengikumu' ve lo gipele do ote-do imiselavo lingine goloso nite' di'mi vi minanguti' nene lengi' hamo' hamo' do ti'ne-lengedo no'noho' ize-lingidine' ve.
Aza inite' muki' ine' nene Zudaia misuboukosi Zelusalemi ebekukisi ine' ne la'lisete ninge none' ma ve. Lohoto' zalo' bilani'za

Agae, neze zuhokizo, Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' ei' velemu' ogo gatine doo gamazi ti' lo nolo-lingimuze. Gililo. Lingine gamazi ato ato' li vi eza ema vamilo. Mukito' lingine gohi di bizii igi lutine di hamo' igi hamo' lutidokovo' minilo.
Ee, lingine gomu' O'moso huli hoto' i-di mini monovo goloso igi minadi'mo nene lutine gatingu' O'moso biluva' i-di minani'za

Nemu' nene gaza umungive goso've lavo'ine lemaa' neine' initekumu' nene lavonga lemamivo golise ogo mehenga emosa gaza lu'ningu' goloso monovo nomivo mini Guvelesi vela lika' lika' igi ezelo' lehete i minave mukikisi nene maka' bizo mino lisihe' lamine' minaa' monovosi ido' Guvelesi vemu' gele ele'vole' oga' monovosi ido' lute ngemaa' monovosi ido' hongu lo lamino minaa' monovosi nene imiselo dalosa amuzo molozo.

Nemu' nene Kilisito' hilinguti' O'moso'mo do ote-dingu' nene lengikisi lutine helavo minanguti' nene maka' do ote-lengedavo nizani' nenako nemu' nene lingine Kilisito' O'mosoloti' lemo mino ana hulaa' ida neida Okulumoku' minine' monovo danavavo' nene dalone li gili mini gono di minilo.

Ne'mine igi minadoti' naba vani angelo' ne'mo nene pikuli hubu lo do nolo molavo osupo gihilesi olokisi nene vanisesi gopo' napa o minine' nene soto' ogavo misubouko mili hulikevo do'mozine' ve. Ido' do'mozine' ne'mo nene misubo laka'ni seto hamo mininguti' linge hamo' nene lo'voto osu' lavo ido' za lingelatikisi nene a'mine'mine votigilelo' ma lo osu' lavo misubolo' guvise navise ngomo' naba' muki' nesi nene lo osu' line' ve.

ti' li lani' ve: Guvekasi ve O'moso amuzo mukili'mi meleho gozopotati' mine do ogo idisesi ha minanive gaza amuzoka naba do ti' ogo api' ogo me misubou' gizebo ogo naningumu' nene isaa' neve lo gopo'ni nolune.

Ne'mine lavo Izesu' ti' lo lo-imine': Gaza O'moso'mo lehize-lengedaa' neine' initekumukisi ido' nosomu' voku' lo-giduve neni' monovo'ne nemukisi nene ma ningo gele minaine' neidiniko gaza voku' laanivo naza nene noso hinipinikuti' dizaa' neine' noso minevo' minevoli'mi izelehosi minine' noso nene gimuvodine.
Ne neiha minevo' alevotine'mi izeleho Kilisito' ogo soto' pizeline' nene linginesi a'mine'mine igi lengemeni dameni okodine atoli'minesi maka' soto' ilisave.

Linge ma gize nouvoni' neve nene Izesu' nene O'moso'mo do lu' izelive lo imiselelesa live O'moso'mi gipele ma nene neive li gili ele'vole' ilizave losa gizuvoni' ve. Ido' lingine a'mido' gili ele'vole' ilizani' nene lingine minevo' minevo' lengemeni dameni nene eitati' dalizave losa gizuvoni' ve.

Laza nene O'mosolati' soto' une' nenako ingine O'moso ningi gilaa' ave nene leze gamazite gili daa' nave. Ido' O'mosolati' soto' amave nete leze gamazite gili hulaa' nave. Ne'mine iga' nanako nemu' O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo do soto' ine' gamazi gihile lamine' nesi ido' gopo gamazi ado' O'moso'mi Sikalahuli'mo do soto' amine' gamazi nesi nene do kegeso ningo gelaa' noune.

Lingine lutine ge neme ne geme li minaa' nangumu' nene di nubo igi makato' noso' nite' naa' nangu' nene a'mine ne'mine ve ingine imi mini ngovozosi hilami mini noso' nite' sau sau li naa' nani' ne'mo nene a'mine noso' nite' nalisa mulise milaa' nani' mulisetine nene di goloso iga' nave. Ido' engi' neve nene hepeli'mo limuso hubu lo do vavo goline izamivo ma hize ele' o-ledesa'mine' ne'mino monoku' nene ma hizi ele' i-lidisa'mave. Ido' ma nene za ma gihile izaa' naani' gameneu' malite gihile izamaa' naani' ne'mino monoli'mi gihile di soto' amavo za ma luhive gili hulikevo mo goko' laa' neine' ne'mino engi' lu'ine nene mo mudise hele gehepeve ogave.

Ne'mine ikevo gebili nabili inite' gizi davesi ngele'mizi vi Petolo' ogo novivo mumuno'mo nesi linge ma avuto' ngebelavo lamine' ilizahe li holomosi ingaa' ani' initekisi di vi akalo' huli ngimika' ani'.

inite' linge muki' ne'mine disa Kilisito'nimu' gili ele'vole' iga' nani' nedunu' nene ve golosolati' olo' lo minine' elese aline' nene bili lihizi di hulilizado' i minilizani' nenako nemu' nene a'mine gili ele'vole' iga' nani' ne'mo nene lepese naba ne'mine lolo' ogavosa di minilo.
Ne'mine mana'mine gono dalizangu' nene eveneliti gono di-ngidamii asi Guvelesi ve'mi gono nidi-dani' gilivosa lutine laminetoti' gehepeve nene di minilo.

Ido' lengikuti' vene' vemoho' gopo'napa ingi monikelizave. Ido' lengikuti' evene' ma Esau' ne'mine mini O'mosomu' ga'ine molavo me misubou' initekumukovo' gili minikelizave li ge gizebo o-nede ne gizebo o-gede li minilo. Esau' aza nene Isaka' gana' gipele mino melehido' medelo mino melehi inite'velokisi nene medelo minelido' minine'za gamene ma a'mine uvoloho Esau' aza ga'na helo nakunolo Zakobo' noso' nite' gize vata' ogo minine' nenako a'minguti' nene linge ma nemavo nalongisi ve lo haza misubou' inite' noso' niteto' nene melehido' medelo mineline' mo'mosi've nene nakunolo Zakobo'ni eme molani' ve. Ee, Esau' aza O'mosomu' gala molavo me misubou' initekumukovo' gele minive mino haza noso' nite' nene gamene hamokovo' nalosa ido' nene inite' naba melehido' medelo mineline' mo'mosi've nene Zakobo'ni imine' ve.
Ne'mine lavo ingine gohi geke' li ti' li lani' ve: Ve neve nene kuluhize-damo Balabasi'ni nene kuluhize-dezo. A'mine Balabasi' nene ngamani lovo o ngemaa' ive minine' ve.

engi' zuho biluvaliti a'ningu' ngele'mizi milaa', inite' bubu izi di goloso iga', engikumu' gilavo dizaa', ido' O'mosolo' lu'ine milaa' nani' nene ivile' ivosa oko'ine'mo lanite' gelaa' neine' initeto' lu'ine milaa',
Ne'mine ingumu' nene O'moso'mo do'mo dizo dizo mo mo'mosi' nabalo' goloso hozine hulo-doo ei' gulive do hozi lo-dine' ne'mo nene gulive ato ato' muki' nene ngivile' ogosa minine' ve.

Laza Izesu' Kilisito' amuzo'vemukisi ido' alingumukisi lo-lingimune' nene heluno gamazi ma gili nge li mini lado' nene e'metosa lo-lengemamune. Asi a'mine amuzo've atoli'mine minine' monovo've nene leli' vete gulo ne'mo ningavosa nene lo-lingimune' ma neive.

Ido' luhuvo nite' muki' ei' gizingu' nene a'mine ne'mine initekumu' gizidaa gizida nene a'mine hamoli'mine gamazi memu' nene mo azasi hamo' gamazivo' gize'mo vo neive. Ido' a'mine luhuvo nite' gize'mo vingu' nene gamazi linge ma monovo've geto gele lamine' amolonido' o minine' gamazi nesi nene gize neive. Ne'mino neine' nenako mono' monovo gili vevesami lu'ine amuzo molamive ingine mono' godolou' gamazi linge'mi monovo nesi nene di zovo' zava' izaa' naadi'mine igi a'mine Paulo' gamazi've nesi nene a'mine'mine igi di zovo' zava' izaa' nave. Ne'mine iga' naadoti' nene angise'ine meni'ine goloso nene di soto' iga' nave.

aposolo seta' Pauloki Banabasiki ingine gili upuho' goloso igi inite' lolo' ilizani' nene goloso nite' ve li evene' ningi gililisave li genegana'ine di boloti loti' izi vi evene' mulise nizangu' heteli geke' li

Ido' Kilisito' lengi' evene' ato ato' lengele'mize lamine' ine' gamazi noluvoni' nene nemu' noluve: Kilisito' aza O'moso'mo gamazi laminetokovo' laa' neine' nene do soto' ogo O'moso'mo Zuda veti avotemotinemu' lo huko lo-ngidine' gamazi nene do gihile izelesa gelekele' ve lolo' ogo O'moso'mi noso okodela mulunive Zuda ve lelita nene gono dani' ve.
Evene' malite O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo mono' ve none li lilizani' nete gamazi laa' ado' gizebo isa'mani' nene evene' a'ne'mine ve mono' ve nobe li engi' lu'ine golo izi soza lilisave.

Naza ti' lo lo-lingimuvoni' gamazi mamu' nene gili minilo: Gelekele' izipe ne'mo nene gizebo o-do minive guvelesi ve've nene ivile' o-do minesa'mive. Neni' goboni mili-nidaa' ave nilizani' nene lengikisi goboni mili-lingidilisave. Ido' neni' gamazi'nelo' gili di minaa' ave nilizani' nene lengi' gamazitinesi nene gili di minilisave.
Ne'mine ikevo Zuda ve ezemu' gili ele'vole' avemu' nene Izesu' ti' lo line': Lingine neni' apize lingimuvoni' gamazilo' e'meti mini di vi nilizani' nene neni' izipaha'ne zuho gihile nene nizave.
Ele'mize molavo neivo Aigita misuboukisi Kanaha misuboukisi ga'na naba soto' ogavo evene' muki' ga'nali'mo goloso ani'. Goloso ikevo avotemotesi noso' nitekumu' vise' ani'.
Ido' izipaha zuho linge ma meteho lo huko-lidido' gili di gamazi gihile've nene di mini nizavo ne'mi gamazi gelo mulu'neu' lamine' goloso gelekuve.

Ve ma ingine engi' zuho di guni gizebo i-ngidami minilizave muki' nene monovo goloso igi mono' huli osu' lisa Kilisito'nimu' gili ele'vole' amave nene ngivile' igi lihime daa' ave minilisave. Ne neiha ve ma engi' numu'ningu' ingaa' ave engi' zuho gehepeve di guni i-ngidami minilizave engi' neve nene engi' zuho gizebo i-ngidamaa' ave linge masi nene ngivile' igi lihime nene naba goloso gehepeve daa' ilisave.

Nemu' nene eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' ave ngele'mize milalizangumu' a'mine ve nene di lamine' i-ngidi oko'nido' nene vanisedunu' hibi' izi huli-ngidi ido' noso' izi-ngidaa' ani' ne'mino aza leli' lute nene ei' vanise'vedunu' hibi' izo hulo-ledo a'mingu' monovo goloso minine' nene do hulo-ledo ido' okode nene noso laminedunu' noso ize-lidine' gelavo mino lute lisihe' lamine' minidi'mo O'moso golo izamo ido' gate seta' gelamo ezemu' gele ele'vole' goloso ogo O'mosola ogo ezesi bizo minuke'zo.

Ee, ingine nene neni' monovo'nemu' nene ve'inedunu' ma ningami ga'inedunukovo' nene evene' malite li-ngimikevo ti' li gilani' ve: Leli' mono' gamazite osu' lilive lo leli' goboni molo-ledaa' ive ma'mo idise nene a'mine mono' gamazi nene gamazi lamine' ve lo lo-ngeme'mo nomonive.
Noso' nite' ni gili' likevo do amuzo molo-lengede minivo aka volone' nene okodine ngomosi ma do goloso amivo lisihe' ogo vo hetelelesune.
Ido' lingine nenikumu' ve li mulumo geni amuzo mili gihi'mi vi minaa' nangu' ahu' lamaa' naani' nemukisi nene mo ningo gele nouve.

Ti' lo lo-ngemezo: Ve ozoho ingine ga'ine gopo amivo mini ngemeni dameni vevese minivo mini ga'ine gili hehe li lu'ine ga'ine gizebo igi mini monoku' minaa' monovo'ine di lamine' igi evene' lu'ine ngimi nasahili' i-ngidaa' monovo'ine di lamine' igi geni initeli'mi lulou' mini ma ele'vole' igi hongu li minaa' monovo'ine nene di lamine' igi minilizave.
Gomu' O'moso'mi monovo gilamani' gameneu' nene lihime'ine molo-ngedamo ninge huline'za idi'nise nene numudo' namado' ve mukito' lu'ine di velepe' izilisave lo lo-ngede neine' ve.
Ido' Izesu'ni bili badikani' lohoto' za avita nene izelehosi ido' izelehi alunolosi Kelopasi' elenaho Maliakisi ido' Mangadala numudoti' vene' Maliakisi nene oti minani' ve.
Ido' oko'nolo' inite' ngolo minine' neve nene vaniseu' lupizikani' lavolavo do ngolosa minine' ve. Ido' gulive've neve nene O'moso'mi Gamazi've ve lo minine' ve.

Ne neiha soza o'moso ngimani' noso' nitekuti' nene ha nalonido' o neihe li nemu' gili lingine nalizani' ne'mo evene' ma ingine monoku' gilizevo ne'mine gili minani' nene monokuti' limi ingikelizaze. Monovotido' nene gizebo lamine' ilo.

Idise naza gei' maho lolo' ogo neni' gipe'ne gei' nene nane lo do ote-giduvoni' ve. Ido' Izesu'ni hilinguti' do ote-davo a'minguko gohi tine' molo vo gelesamiline' o neive. Nemu' nene O'moso'mo line' gamazi ma ti' lo gize neive: Ele'vole' gamazi lo Davidi'ni lo huko lo-duvoni' inite' lamine' nene lehize-lengedelesa nouve.
A'mine neni' gohi ningilizani' gamenelo' nene naza me'nehida mine molo nouvo ido' lingine nene nenita mini mili nizavo naza nene lengita mine molo nouvoni' nemu' nene mo ningi gililisave.

Ido' eze nene ningo gele none lo gelaa' noune' nene lamine' nehe. Nado gelelone. Leli' monovote do ningosa gelelesune. Eze gamazi lo huko-lidine' nene gele do minaa' noolone' nene eze ningo gele none lo gelaa' noune' nene lamine' gelaa' noune lo gelelesune.

Ne'mini nizangumu' nene lingine lihimetinesi ha neivo hililisave luvoni' ma neive. Ee, lingine nenikumu' a'mine neive ma ne neive li ma gili ele'vole' amilizani' nene lihimetine apasamo ha neivo a'minesi hililisave.

A'mine Babelonia numuno ebekuti' aleve nete O'moso'mi evenele Izesu' gamazi hizi ele' igi minave nene geli geli igi ngolize izi ngibilika' ngibilika' avo vanise'ine vai' goloso lepani' nenako naza ninguvoni' nene a'mine pasidia' vene' ne'mo vanise'ine nene vaini noso ne'mino geli geli ogo nadi'mo sipaki ine' gelo neivo ninguve. Naza ningosa vo'ne vaavo gamazi'nesi nomivo minuve.

Emavo Zakobo' ezelo' medelo minavo alinge' meleho aza gana've no'noho' ize-deline' no'noho' nene Zakobo'ni ize-davo Esau' aza me'neho no'noho' nene do tine' molo neni' no'noho' ize-nedelive lo ive ogo lulo do velepe' izeline' aka vise' ogo minine'za ma ningamivo meleho aza Esau' gamazi've gele huline' nene lingine mo gili nizani' ma neize. Nemu' nene lingine eze ine' ne'mine amilo.

Ido' evene' vai' di gese' igi minanguti' muki' ne'minete nene Izesu'nimu' nununga' ti' li li minani': Aza nene evene' lamine' neive li evene' linge nete nilavo ma nete nene evene' muki' go'ine izo do goloso neive li lani' ve.
Nili-ngimavo O'moso inginesi mino amuzo ngemavo evene' muki' engi' gamazi gili Guvetesi vemu' gili ele'vole' igi ezela vi gi'mizani'.

O'moso'mo leze luteu' ningavo eze gamazi lamine' nene ha li-ngimilizado' neive lo ninge-lede neivo lo-lengemaa' noune. Evenelite gilikevo lamine' ilive losa nomive. O'moso luteu' ningaa' ive'mo ningivo lamine' ilive losa lo-lengemaa' noune.
Ne neiha O'moso'mo lavo Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' aza hize ele' o-lidivo lihime daa' monovo nene ivile' ogo lihime damo minaa' noune' nemu' O'moso opo'ni lolone.
Vene' gevono' guhalihali gehepeve ogo minaa' neine' ne'mo nene O'mosolo' gele mu'musi' o mino holuka' nehe holise' nehe gamene gamene hize ele' o-delingumu' nene O'mosola lo minaa' neive.

Ne'mine o neine'za voku' lilizado' minamivo ganakuti' nene neni' ve'nemu' inite' mamukisi voku' lamavo mine do ogo idisesi nene ha none. Voku' lilo. Voku' lilizani' nene lengita longolize ne'mo nene vai' goloso lo minelive lo a'mine voku' liliza inite' nene ha lengemavo dalisave.

Ido' evene' malite gei' okonga nene meni hizikevo engi' inite' ne'mine lolo' ogo goboni gono do-ngede'mo vo nanivo O'moso'mo ei' ve lo gele'mize molavo ma goboni ve naningumu' nene gopo gaka gelamo a'mingu' nene ha minezo. Ne neiha a'mine goboni gonouti' apaso viline' aka ma soto' o-gedavo ma a'mido' e'meteline' nene lamine' oloseive.
A'mine aleve nene O'moso'mi evenele hizi ho'li-ngidaa' ave nene nizave. Ingine me misubou' initekumukovo' gelaa' neine' ngemenisivo' minikevo O'moso'mi Sikalahu' nene engita minesa'mivo ma damave.

Lingine Kilisito' nasahili' o-lengedavo ne'mo O'moso'mo ei' evenele ve lo lengele'mize molavo minanguti' lite' li mehedine imi evenelite mono' gamazi lamine' ve li gamazi ato' li-lingimani' gili ngimaa' nani' nemu' nene naza upuho' ogo aizo lo nogiluve.

Ido' lengiku' lovo lolize nene soto' ogalive li evene' mukita hongu monovo nene igi mili ngelebizi minilizangumu' nene amuzo milalo. Ido' ve ma ingine O'moso'mi evenelelite di minilizani' monovo lisihe' lamine' nene engita nomivo minaa' nave nene Guvelesi ve mo ningamilizani' nenako lingine hongu monovo igi mili ilizadoti' nene O'moso'mi evenele nounako li monovo lisihe' laminetokovo' e'meto volone li amuzo mili minilo.

Ne'mine likevo aza ti' lo lo-ngimine' ve: Alaha' mo ma dalisaze. Alaha' daa' golalezetine nene huli hela zamela ilo. Ne'mine lavo hulisa ingine gelelehe' ani'za a'mingu' nene alaha' vai' goloso likevo ngeli gelelehe' amani' ve.

Ne nanitekumu' ve. Okode lolovo huki-lidikevo minaa' nene haza inite' ve. Ido' okode lolovo hukamune' minaa' nesi nene haza inite' ve. Haza inite' neiha inite' gihile nene O'moso'mo lo huko-lidine' gamazi've gele daa' ne neive.

Ido' evene' ga'ine do gamazi lo-ngemaa' amuzo ma lehize-lede neine' neivo ma nene ha mo ga'nine do gamazi lo-ngemaa' olosune. Ido' ve ma nene inite' ize' molo ngemaa' amuzo lehize-de nolive ne'mo nene mo inele ogo ngemeleseive. Ido' ve mali'mo nene gomu' molo-ngemaa' amuzo do noline' nene a'mine gono've nene amuzo molo do mineleseive. Ido' ve ma aza nasahili' o-ngedaa' amuzo do nolive ne'mo nene nasahili' o-ngedaaku' nene olize izo minosa ne'mine ilive.

longo' o-ngedo ti' lo line': Lingine nene mono' gili ele'vole' igi O'moso'mi Sikalahu' lehizikeni' nehe lo longo' o-ngedavo ingine ti' li lani': O've. Laza O'moso'mi Sikalahu' neive li ma li-limavo gelamune' ve.
Ido' luhuvo nite' meu' gamazi gizo nolo-lingimune' nene ve mali'mo gele hulavo ma eze monovo ningi gili asi'vevo' mino ovozo helelingumu' ve li huli-di mehedine imilo.

Neze zuhokizo naza lamineto' noluze. Gililo. Misubou' okodesi minune' nedunu' nene O'moso'mo gizebo ingu' ngelo vo holamolosune. Misubou' okode vo tolovo iline' ne'mo vo tolovo ami inite' Okulumoku' inite' nene ngelo mo damoloseive.

Ne'mine igi unuvo goloso oga' neine' noso' nitekumukovo' nene gono dami asi minevo' minevo' ogo minaa' neine' noso' nite' minevo' minevo' lengemeni dameni do soto' o-lengedelingumu' O'mosolati' ve gihile neni' lengemeloni' nemukovo' nene vise' iga' gono dalo. Ido' ne'mine noso' nite' lengemeloni' nene me'neho O'moso asi've nene neni' ne'mine iline lo amuzo nemo nele'mize molani' nenako nemu' nene ne'mine olosuve.
Ido' inite' mamu' O'mosola voku' lani'za gatine goloso gili langisetine a'mine initeli'mi lanite' gililizangumukovo' voku' likevosa nene O'moso'mo lengemesa'mive.
Ne'mine igi mini lengita soto' iline' inite' mukikumu' nene Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' velemu' igi gamene gamene O'moso metehine nene tangezo' li-di opo'ni li minilo.

Mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizani' ma neive: Abalahamu' O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogavo nemu' O'moso'mo gelavo ve lisihe' lihime've nomine' lolo' ine'. Ido' O'moso'mo Abalahamu'ni inite' o-dine' nesi ido' lengiku' ele'vole' suno do soto' oga' ine' nesi nene hamo' monovo angumu' do soto' o-lingidine' nenako Abalahamu' O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ine' ne'mine igi lingine Izesu'nimu' gili ele'vole' igi minangumu' ve losa ele'vole' suno lengiku' nene do soto' oga' ine' ve.

Ido' a'mine numuno ebeku' nene O'moso'mi labanala'mo hize labana' ele-daa' neivo sipisipi angale neve nene a'mingu' livi' lamu've ne'mino neine' nenako holi'mo nehe ike'ni'mo nehe a'mine numuno ebeku' hize labana' elaato' nene ma minamasive.

Ne neiha lengi' lutingu' O'moso'mi Sikalahu' nene ma minevo' dovo' ogo noline' nene lingine lengemeni dameni litehe'mi gelekele' ve minami asi Sikalahu' ne'mi gelekele' ve nene nizave. Ido' ve ma ingine Kilisito' Sikalahu've di minamave nene Kilisito' zuho minisa'mave.

Ido' a'mine za'veloti' a'nava huko huline' ne'minisa minani' Isilaele' aleve ingine gili ele'vole' ami minadoti' nene huli gili ele'vole' ma ilizani' nene O'moso'mo gohi za'vela do gi'mize-ngedaa' amuzo nene ha do neinako gohi ha do gi'mize-ngedeleseive.
Ido' engi' ve'ninguti' nene soza gamazi hamokisi ma lamani' ve. Ee, lihime dikeve gamazi ne'minesi nene engi' oko'nido' ma dizamine' minani' ve.

Ne neine'za gamazi li'mi vani' mauti' hamo' lamine' ma lani' lo soto' ogo lo-gemelove. Mono' aka gosohokumu' angise'ine evene' ize' molo do gopo o-ngedaa' aka ve lani' nene a'mine akalo' nomono naza avotemote opo'ni li gelekele' i-dani' O'moso nene opo'ni lo gelekele' o-daa' nouve. Ne'mine ogo naza Mose' lo huko line' gamazisi ido' O'moso'mi gamazi li soto' ave polohetelite gizikani' gamazi nesi muki' gamazimu' nene gele ele'vole' o nouve.

Ido' linginela golo hizamani' dina' ma neivo ma nene geti golo hizi ngimilo. Evene' hamotasi dina' igisa haza huliki minamilo. Ido' lingine dina' nene di minami golo hizi osukovo' lilizave lo noluvoni'za linginela dina' ne'mine ma minaa' neine' ado' ngeli bekimi amilizani' o minaa' neine' nene ma neive. A'mine dina' nene lingine lutine ge neme ne geme li minilizado' o neine' inite' nemu' nene noluve. Ido' ne'mine noluvoni' nene evene' malite evene' ma lu'ine ngimilizave ingine ne'mine ilizangumu' nene O'moso'mi lou' gamazi'velo' mo e'meti osu' lilizani' nenako nemu' nene noluve.

Ne'mine ogavo evene' oko'nido' nene holi'mi olo' ahu've ne'mo lo'vote-ngedavo ingine nene ne'mino evene' do goloso o-ngedeline' amuzo'vesi minive O'moso'mi gulive nene divi ledivi' igi mini lu'ine di velepe' izi lihime'ine hulami O'moso di naba i-damani' ve.

Ido' lave gesi've neve nene naba zalo' goloso mino a'mingu' nene gateni've tuvelu'a neivo a'mine gatedo' gatedo' nene angelo' tuvelu'a nene mini'mi vani' ve. Ido' a'mine gateni hamo hamoto' nene Isilaele' gipele tuvelu neti nga'vopilemoliti mulise neti gulive'ine ma nene gizika' gizika' ikevo minine' nene ninguve.

Ne neiha lou' gamazilo' nene ngelo gele do osu' lamolone' o neine' nenako ne'mo O'moso'mo mudise vi tolovo ilisave lo usi' izo lo huko lo-lidine' gamazi'mi lulou' nene vo hulune' ve. Ido' laza a'mingu' vo hulunidoti' Kilisito' aza eze oko'no nene hulo meni hizo do tine' molo-lidine' ma neive. Ido' do tine' molo-lidine' aka nene ne'mino neive. Mono' godolou' gamazi ma ti' li gizi nizani' ma neive: Evene' zalo' ngibili badave nene O'moso'mo usi' ize-ngidive nizave. Kilisito' nene leli' lihimetemu' lohoto' zalo' bili badikevo lelito' medelo O'moso'mo usi' ize-dive lolo' ogave.

Ido' Kilisito' gamazi've lamine' nene evene' malitesi li-nimamavo Kilisito' asi've lo soto' ogo lo-nimive luvoni' nene nemu' luze. Gililo. Naza gomu' Zuda veti monovolo' e'meto mino ogo molo minaa' uvoni' monovo'ne nene lingine mo li-lingimikevo mo gili nizave. Naza nene ne'mine noogo O'moso'mi evenele zuho do goloso palasa ogo osu' lo-ngedelove lo ne'mine olosa do goloso ogosa goboni molo-ngedaa' uvoni' ve.
Lemo ogo a'mine sata' naba gele vine' loposo nite' ado' gomukuti' minine' gosihe' ado' Ve Goloso Satani nene analo' dokoo kilisimasi vanu tauseni (1000) minelive lo seni nala' naba nene ize-do
Ido' a'mine ebe' nabau' ve ma minine' gulive Simoni'. Aza gamene ha'na luso ve lolo' ogo mino naza guve'nesi ve nouve lo Samalia aleve muki' go'ine izaa' ine'.

ido' ezemu' ningo gelo hilinguti' otine' amuzo do neine' ne'mo nene nenitasi mine molo neivo mino aza gomu' mulumo alumo geni gehaa' ine' ma'mino nazasi nene makato' geho mino ido' eze hiline' monovo danava nene nenita minivo mino

Ido' gaza evene' ma do kegeso mono' gizebo ve lolo' o-ngedelo ma nene bubu izo anga godo'nido' hito do kegese-ngedamozo. Gaza bubu izo ingine monovo'ine golososi ma nolingumu' ne'mine oganivo engi' lihime nene geita dizalize. Lihimeka nomine' mineliningisi gei' monovokalo' nene gizebo lamine' ogosa minezo.

Ido' vene' eleni nizani' nene lo-ngemanivo ingine a'mine'mine igi mono' vene' lili' igi mini evene' ngemenga lami vaini noso geli geli igi namilizave. Ne'mine igi mini monovo lamine' apizi ngimi minilizave.
Nemu' nene ve ma aza izeni elenahine ma daline' nene lamine' oloseiha ve ma izeni elenahine ma damo minelidi'mo nene ivile' ogosa lamine' oloseive.
Ido' ne'mine igi O'moso'mi gamazi nene haza gatinedunukovo' gili minami gili di e'metilo. Haza gatinedunukovo' gililizani' nene langisetine lutine golo izilisave.
Neloti' nene Zuda ve nete Izesu'ni bililisa vise' i'mi vi nizani' nenako nemu' aza Zudaia misubou' nene monelesa gelamo nGalilaia misubou' nene mone mone ogo minine' ve.

Ne'mine oga' neine'za lengi' nene O'moso ne'mo Izesu' Kilisitoda do imine' molo-lengedave. Ne'mine ogo a'mine Kilisito'ni nene gateu' gamazi lamine' minine' ne'mi izelehine lolo' o-dave. Ido' lolo' o-davo asi've ne'mo nene lelito' medelo minevo' alevo've hulo helo O'moso'mi velelo' evene' lisihe' laminekovo' minilizave lo goloso inite' apase-ledoo O'moso'mi evenele lolo' o-ledo aza golosouti' mudise lele'mize lamine' oloseive.
Ne'mine ogo lapese mau' noso lekosa api' ogo izipahala zuholiti gize'ine noso' izeka' izeka' ogo gopololo' likekine' taulidunu' nene gilite ngimika' gilite ngimika' o'mo vine'.
Ne'mine ogo Izesu' akalo' nene e'metilisa vani' aleve goboni molo-ngedo hili osu' lilizave lo vene' vemoho' muki' nene a'nido' nala' izo hulo nala' numungu' o-ngedaa' uvoni' ma ve.
Ne'mine li evene' linge ma O'moso'mo do lu' izelive lo imiselelesa live ve lavo linge ma o've ei' nomive lavo evene' muki' nene hizi ho'li minani' ve.

Lengita O'moso'mi zuho mulise nizani' neve nene lu'ine'mi noso' nite' ngimika ngimika' igi gizebo lamine' i-ngidi minilo. Ne'mine i-ngidi minilizani' nene evenelite lutingu' hizavosa nevoba asi lutine'mo ne'mine olosa gele nolidokovo' nene e'meti ilo. Ido' ma nene moni heneni inite' ma dalone li gili minisa gizebo i-ngidilizani' ne'mo nene lovozo helaa' inite' goloso ilisaze. Mo ne'mine ami asi O'moso'mo lingine a'mine gonomu' lutine mili minisa gono dalizave lo gele neido' nene e'meti gono dalo.

Ido' a'mine helaa' ne'mi gavoso nene lihime daa' monovo ne neive. Ido' O'moso'mi lou' gamazi've ne'mo lihime damaa' ve lo lo neivosa lute ne'mo lihime daakumu' nene otaa' neive. Ido' neloti' lihime daa' monovo nene lelita amuzo molo soto' oga' neive.

Lengi' midingu' gono dave ingine gohise hili minamuno dolizi-lingidikevo lingine meni'ine lingela di haleki ngimamavo nemu' gono daa' ave ive nama ikevo inite' mukito' gizebo oga' ive amuzo'vesi minive O'moso aza gelave.

Nemu' nene lingine goloso monovo ato ato' muki' ado' evene' go'ine izaa' ido' lutingu' monovo goloso haleko neivosa evene' lamine' gili monaa' ido' evene' maliti initekumu' lavodine lemavo muludingu' goloso gilaa' ido' gamazi di goloso igi laa' monovo ato ato' muki' nesi nene ogalone li mudise huli osu' lisa mini

Vene' ingine va'ninge hilami ve'inesi minilizani' gameneu' nene va'ningine huli-ngidamilizani' o neine' nenako bizivo' minilisave. Ido' va'ninge hilikevo ve malo' volone lilizani' nene ha vilisaha a'mine vilizave nene Izesu' zuho minilizavelokovo' vilizave.

A'mine ve sita' netise nene hele noloninguti' otaa' nene luteli'mo mo otani' nenako nemu' nene gohi ma otamolosune lisa mono' gamazi gihileloti' nene zovo' izi visa evene' lingeliti mono'ine nene di gopo i-ngidikesive.

Ido' ne'mine noluvoni' nene nemu' noluve: Laza Kilisitoda vo gi'mizunive nene okode lolovo huko hulo nolobe huko hulamo nolobe nemu' O'moso'mo leli' do lu' izelesa gala giline' nene do atoli'mine ma amoloseive. Ne'mine amoloseiha asi Kilisito'nimu' gele ele'vole' o none' ne'mo lute ngemaa' monovo nene ogo molo minelone' neevo' nene inite' gihile neive. Ne'mino neine' nenako nemu' O'moso'mo leli' nene ve lisihe' lamine' gehepeve ve lo-ledelive lo gelo laza ne'mine ilingumu' gizebo ogo none' nene O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo hize ele' o-ledavo Kilisito'nimu' gele ele'vole' ogo minuningumukovo' nene evene' lisihe' ve lo-ledeline' nenako nemu' nene luvoni' ve.

Ido' ne'mino gele ngolo' lo gilidi'mo eze nene gono dalido' lisihe' gehepeve ogo mino gelekele' o-daa' unive mukikumu' nene minevo' minevo' oloningumu' ve lo mudise do lu' izaa' ne'mi meleho nene aza lolo' ogavosa

Idise mene Zudaia misubouko Izesu' zuho inite'ine nomivo vise' iga' ani' aleve nene hize ele' i-ngidi lingine moni di nubuho ilizangumu' gamazi ma loloze. Gililo: Galatia misubou' Izesu' zuho ti' lo lo-ngiduvodo' nene linginesi a'mine'mine ilo.
Ido' a'mine'mine igi vene' nete Guvetesi vela gelekele' i-daa' nani' ne'mine igi vadinge lilizado' gelekele' igi minilizado' o neine' nenako gelekele' i-ngidi minilo.

Ido' Izesu' aza gamazi gohi ma evene' lo-ngimingu' nene ti' lo line': Naza nene misubou' aleve hize labana' ele-ngedaa' uve ma nene nouve. Ve ma ne'meti minilizave nene lu'ningu' liti'muso ize minamivo a'mine neni' hize ele' o-ngedeloni' labana' ne'mo nene minevo' minevo' iliza aka ngelebizivo minilisave.
Lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' alevekizo, lingine Guvelesi ve Izesu Kilisito' aposolo'velite gomukuti' lani' gamazi mamu' gatine molalize. Gili nge li minilo.

Asi've nene evene' muki' minevo' alevo' ngemo ido' mutive daa' ani' ngemo ido' inite' muki' lehize-ngedaa' neine' nenako nemu' aza nene inite' matakumu' vise' osa'mive. o've. Nemu' nene evenelite gono've do inite' ma do soto' ogo emelonido' nomive.

Haza evene' nete gamazi ma hizi ele' ikevo ma nene laza a'mine gamazi mo lamineto' neive lo gelaa' noune. Ne neiha O'moso'mo gamazi liline' nene haza eveneliti gamazi ivile' ogo gihile lamine' izeleseive. Nemu' nene O'moso'mo gipele hize ele' o-do line' gamazi neine' nene gele ele'vole' olosune.

Ne'mine monovo goloso nene ogalone li lepesetine ne'mine Guvelesi ve Izesu' Kilisito'ni nene di kisi mini lengemeni dameni liteheli'mo lanite' gelaa' neine' monovo goloso dalizangumu' aka vise' iga' nani' nene mudise hulilo.

Ido' Isilaele' aleve ingine O'mosomu' gili ele'vole' igi minani' ne'mo O'moso'mo lido' e'meti Zeliko numuno ebeli'mi gesi gehenidunu' gizani' gesi ha'na nene go' laneme go' laneme nene gamene hamo hamo' di vodo vodo i-dika' i-dika' igi nizavo gamene seveni (7) ogavo a'mine gamene seveni (7) ne'mi lulou' nene gohi gamene seveni (7) ne'mine di vodo vodo i-dikevo a'mine gehenidunu' gizani' gesi nene ngululubizo lemo ongavo Isilaele' aleve a'mingu' dizi Zeliko aleve ngibili gese' ani'.
O'moso'mo Paulo'ni hize ele' o-davo inite' amadi'mine atoli'mine ine'.
Ne'mine likevo a'mido' Izesu' ti' lo lo-ngimine': Naza lamineto' ti' lo nolo-lingimuve: Lihime dalizave muki' nene mo lihime monovoli'mi gelekele' ve nizave.
Lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' mate, O'moso'mo lulo atoli'mine ogo lemaze. Nemu' laza a'mine'mine ogo lute ne geme ge neme lo minelonido' o neive.
Naza minevo' minevo' ogo lu'ne gosoho' do mineloni' aka nene nelebizanivo gezesi minusidi'mo lu'neu' gulumo avile liso minavo ne'minovo' minelesuve lo gizine' ve.

Naza gei' nanida olihe amuvo nanido' nene mono' godolou' gamazi nene gate ngemaa' ido' lu'ine do oto ga'ine daa' gamazi lo-ngemaa' ido' mono' monovo apize ngemaa' gono ne'mido' nene luka amuzo molo molo minoosa do do vo minezo.

Laza nene geni ato ato' gehaa' noune'za ne'mo nene aka vamaato' ma lele'mize molosa'mive. Ido' geni inite' lelita minaa' neingumu' nene gate muki' gelaa' noune'za a'mine ne'mo lute gate do gopo gehepeve ogo ma hize tile-ledesa'mive.
Ti' li lani'za ve linge ma nete a'mine di ledi mini gize' i-ngidi ti' li lani': Vaini noso gosoho' nisa sipaki igi mini nilave.

Ido' a'mine numuno ebeli'mi lave gesi've nene zasipa gehenidunu' gizani' mino ido' numuno ebe' nene mo ngoli lamine' gehepeve nedunukovo' gizikevo ngalasi guluvi' gehepeve ne'mine mino silingenge'ni've hulo minine' ve.

A'mine kekeize numunguti' nene a'mine evene' di goloso i-ngidiliza nite' seveni di minani' angelo' seveni nene limi heta ani' ve. Ingine genegana ngilani' nene lavolavo laminetunu' lili' ani' inite' guluvi' lamine' ve'ne ve'ne lo minine' nene ngilikani' mini loso'nido' nene ngolidunu' lili' ani' leti ne'mine nene izikani' ve.
Lengi' goboni mili-lingidilizavemu' nene O'moso'mo no'noho' ize-ngedelive li ezela lilo. Ee, usi' ize-ngedelive lamisa asi no'noho' ize-ngedelingumu' nene eita lilo.
Gizene've nene ngoli gele vine' inite' oloku' gizi di lamine' ikevo ve'ne ve'ne elo minaa' neine' ne'mino ve'ne ve'ne elo minine' ve. Ido' nolo've nene noso naba'mi gugu ne'minosa minine' ve.

Ido' naza gei' monovoka nene mo lo-ngemekuvo gilikeve. Ido' gohi ha lo-ngemelesuve. Nanitekumu' ve. Gaza nenito' luka naba goloso nemaa' naine' monovo ma nene engita neivo nazasi engita mine molo minelongumu' ve losa nene gei' monovoka gohi lo-ngemelesuve.
O'moso'mo ei' gipele gehepeve nene do a'manapa amo leli' mukikumu' nene lehize-lidine' ve. Ido' ne'mine ine' nenako inite' muki' nene lehize-ledamilivoba mo ezesi do lehize-ledeleseive.

Ado' ti' li li-lingimani' mamu' nene noluve: Gamene alinge' nela nene monokumu' gize abelenga laa' ave engi' lu'nidokovo' di mili monoku' nomine' monovo golosolo' e'metilizave ma soto' ilisave li li-lingimave.

Lingine nene O'moso'mo oliva za'veloti' a'nava've linge ma huko huline' mamu' nene ningedo' hangedoka li-ngidi lengi' okodine di dizamilo. Lingine nete nene a'mine zali'mi luhive've nene di ngi li-ngidisa'mave. Asi ei' a'mine za ne'mi luhive nete lengi' nene di ngi li-lingidaa' naani' nenaze. Okodine nene di dizamilo.

Lingine gamazi gihile gili ele'vole' igi monoku' mini gili' li nizani' nenako nemu' gizebo amuzo molo o-lengedo mino ne'mine mana'minemu' gili ele'vole' ilizave lolosa gelamune'za haza lingine muludingu' lamine' gili minilizangumu' lengele'mize lamine' olosa nene lengikisi maka' gono nodune.
Betania numudoti' ve ma minine' nene gulive Lasalo' ve. A'mine ve nene inite' gize do minine'. Ido' alungo seta' atelehoi alunoloi Maliaki Mataki nene maka' hamo' numudoti' minasine' ve.

Nemu' nene a'mine gamazi gele hulilive ne'mo haza eveneliti gamazi gele huluhe lo O'moso'mi gamazi gele huloloseive. Ido' gamazi've gele hulilingu' nene aza O'moso nesi vasa ize-deleseive. Ee, eze Sikalahu've lamine' lengemaa' ive O'moso nene vasa' ize-deleseive.

O'moso'mi Sikalahu' ne'mo ngele'mize akalo' o-ngedaa' ivemu' nene ti' li ningilisave: Ve ma ingine Izesu' Kilisito' aza evene' okode ne'mine lolo' ogo soto' ine' ve li li soto' milalizave nene ingine O'mosolati' nizave li ningi gililisave.

A'mine mono' di gopo igi laa' avemu' mene noluvoni' nene ingine a'mine'mine igi lihime disa vamu' ne'mine ningaa' naadoti' nene engi' oko'ine di goloso igi mini ido' ve naba'mi gizebolo' mini gamazi've gili di minaa' monovomu' nene gosele' igi hozila dizi minave naba angelo' nevo'mine nesi nene divi ledivi' i-ngidaa' nave.
Ido' monovo golosomu' nene olovo' o mino monovo laminekovo' ilive. Ido' hongu lo lamino minaa' monovomu' nene vise' ogo imisele do vo dalive.

Ido' ne'mine o-lengedeline' nene lingine mono' gamazi lamine' gilani' gili mu'musi' ani' nene huli vamii gili ele'vole' i mini monoku' nene ele'vole' igi mini mine gili' li minilizanikovo' nene ne'mine o-lengedeleseive. A'mine mono' gamazi lamine' nene li soto' igi misubou' misubou' numudo' namado' ve nene li-ngimikeve. Ido' neni' Paulo' nene a'mine mono' gamazi'mi gonolo' ve lolo' ogo nouve.
Ne'mine lavo nemu' nene Zuda ve ingine geheni bililisa geheni dani'za Izesu' a'mingu' vo haleko mono' numuno nabauti' nene heta lemo vine' ve.

lengemeni dameni gosoho' nene di otuhi lingine nene O'moso'mi emeni dameni ne'minesi mini gamazi lamineli'mi gihile've nene di soto' igi evene' lisihe' lamine' minaa' ido' O'moso gelekele' o-do minakumu' nene lutine mili minilo.

Ne'mine oloseinako O'moso'mi evenele ado' O'moso'mo lo huko line' gamazilo' e'meti Izesu'nimu' gili ele'vole' igi minaa' nani' alevela nene ne'mine monovo soto' o-ngedalize. Ingine O'moso'mo lo huko line' gamazilo' e'meti Izesu'nimu' gili ele'vole' igi minaa' naani' monovo'ine nene hulami a'mine ne'mine angumu' mulumo alumo geni nite' soto' o-ngedeline' nene ele'vole' igi ha gihi'mi vi minilizado' o neive.
O'moso'mo hilave engi' mulise'ninguti' do ote-dine'.
Neni' nene sipisipi izelo' gizebo ve lamine' gehepeve ma ne nouve. Sipisipi izelo' gizebo ve lamine' nete nene sipisipi ize'ine di ngu' izilisa nene golise ami oko'ine huli hililizado' o neive.
O'moso'mo lengi' nene ei' nasahili'veu' lengele'mize molalongumu' ve lo asi've lengikumu' neni' nene gono nimine' nemu' mo gili nilisave lo gele nouve.
Evene' malite gamazi di gopo igi li mono' mulise hizi ho'li nizavo ma do vevese-ngedelesa ga'ine do gamene hamope setape lo-ngemanivo gilamavo ma ize' molo do hulo-ngedezo.
Gamazi ne'mine lidi'mo nene Zuda veti lu'ine nene do sita' o-ngedavo gohi hizi ho'li minani' ve.

Nemu' nene lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' alevekizo, a'mine initekumu' gilingili igi gizebo igi minilizangu' nene Guvelesi ve ogo ningeline' nene laza luteu' goloso monovo nomivo ido' okodelo' gamazi nomivo mino hongu lo nonivo ningelive li a'midokovo' amuzo mili minilo.

Leze zuho mate, gamazi nene mo gize-lengemekune'za ma neine' nene lo-lengemelonge. Gililo. Guvetesi ve'mi gamazi lengita ine' ne'mino buu lo novivo ne'mi guvele vovo' minelive li lelikumu' ve li O'mosola livo' minilo.
Ne'mine oga' noune' nene a'mine Guvelesi ve Izesu'ni hilinguti' do ote-dive ne'mo nene Izesulesi maka' do ote-ledo lengikisi nene do ei' velelo' o-ledeleseive lo gele minosa nene ne'mine oga' noune.
Ido' lengikuti' ve ma inite' gize do ongo mino ma mono' gizebo ve mamu' elese molavo igi heteli O'mosola li Guvelesi ve'mi velemu' igi uveli noso hili-dilisave.
Ne'mine ogo mino kilisimasi've nene foti (40) ogo vavo eze zuho Isilaele' aleve vo ninge-ngedelove lo gelo lulo otavo vine'.

Gaza guvekasi ve naba make, ami ingine ve nene ma ele'mizi nivave. Aza nene Zuda ve ingine analo' dii bili hililisa navo naza nene Loma ve neive lo gelo ami ma ngele'mize do vo a'ninguti' ipe' ogo do u' izune' ve.

Ne'mine li likevo a'mine ebeto' aleve nene gopo gamazi li gulugulu li zohito' di gese' iga' ebeta loti' izi vi di gese' igi Makedonia misubo nabaukoti' Paulolesi monaa' ave seta' gulive'ine Gaioki Alisitakoki a'nido' di gelelehe' igi di vani'.

Ee, a'mine lulo laminekisi ve lisihe' lamine' nene ezemu' gosele' lengebelavo o've li-di evene' bele hilive ma gomukuti' nalato' neivo lingine Pilato' iseve ize-davo a'mine evene' bele hilive lezesi minelone lani'.
Ingine aka atoto' ngele'mize molamo a'mine a'mine do hamo' o-ledo heta ato' ve inginesi ezemu' gili ele'vole' ikevo engi' lu'ningu' goloso o minine' nesi gilite-ngidine' ma neive.

Ido' nemu' nene neze zuho lu'ne lengeme nouvoni' mate, inite' goloso mali'mo lengehuso' ogalize. Lingine monoku' nene amuzo mili ele'vole' igi oti pehe li minilo. Helakuti' otaa' nene nomidiniko Guvelesi ve'mi gono've di-daa' nani' nene hazamu' di-dadine'za helakuti' otaa' nene neine' nenako hazamu' ma di-damilisave. Nemu' lingine nene hazamu' do-dekunivo labuluvo amoloseive li gili nizani' nenaze. Guvelesi ve'mi gono nene gamene gamene vauve ili di minilo.
Nemu' nene neni' monovolo' e'meti alizave losa gatine do noluze. Gililo.

Ee, misubou' ve nete O'moso'mi monovomu' gele veveselone li vise' ani'za aza O'moso'mo gala lamine' gilido' do molo lavo engi' gili vevesaa'ine nene eze monovo ningilizado' lisihe' amivo eze monovo nene mo ningamani' ve. Ido' ne'mine igi engi' gamazi laminekuti' nene eze monovo ningamanako nemu' O'moso'mo ei' lulolo' do molo a'mine negi gamazi ve laa' nani' gamazi nene nolo-ngimunivo ve ma ingine a'mine gamazi gili ele'vole' ave nene O'moso'mo do ngu' izaa' neive.

Ido' nemu' nene Laza Kilisito' limiselavo ezelo' medelo mino asi've O'moso nene leli' gamaziteu' mine molo mino lengi' nene gatine dani' gelavo leli' nene Kilisito' liline' velemu' nene leli' medelo mino amuzonga ti' lo nolo-lingimune: O'mosola nene lingine biluva' i-di minani' monovo nene hulisa igi ezesi di bizi minilo.
Ne'mine ikeni'za gonoso milaa' angu' mine gili' lamiline' ogavo nemu' mulumo gelo hilinguti' O'moso'mo do ote-dine' ve.
Ido' Izesu' gulive lamine' lingine di nizani' nene inginesi di hozi laa' ilizanako a'mine heneni ve nete divi' ledivi' iga' nave.

Noso geli geli ogo naa' ive minamilive. Ido' evenekumu' izebolo' mala' mala' oga' ive minamo asi hongu lo-ngemo lamine' minaa' ive lovo lolize amaa' ilive minelive. Ido' a'mine mono' muliselo' gizebo o-ngedaa' ilive nene monimu' lulo molaa' ilive minamilive.

Ne'mine ilisani'za neni' ngemeloni' noso nalizave nene gohi a'minemu' ngisamivo mini di dizi nizavo a'mine ngemeloni' noso minevo' minevo' ogali'mi izeleho ne'mo engi' lu'ningu' nene hinipini' ne'mino dizo mineleseive.

Ido' ne'mine ogavo ma ninguvoni' nene sata' naba gele vine' loposo niteli'mi veleutikisi ezeloti' soto' ine' loposo niteli'mi veleutikisi ido' soza polohete ma minidi'mi veleutikisi nene sikalahu' goloso seto hamo ado' gizele' gili vanikovo' nene limi heta ani' ve.

Mono' godolou' Guvetesi ve naba'mo lo huko line' gamazi ma ne'mino neive: Geikumu' gelaa' naine' ne'mino gei' nanida nizavemu' gelo luka ngemezo lo lo neive. Lingine a'mine ele'vole' gamazi gili dalizani' nene inite' gihile dalisani'za

Ido' Izesu'nimu' gamazi ve luvoni' nene nemu' luve. Laza leli' nene le'metilizave losa ne'mine gamazi nene lo-lengemaa' nounivoba asi Izesu' Kilisito' nene Guvelesi ve ne neize. Ei' nene e'metilo losa nene lo-lengemaa' noune. Ido' la'lisetemu' nene laza Izesu'nimu' gelosa lengito' gelekele' izipe ne'mine nene none losa lo-lengemaa' noune.
Ido' ne'mine laa' avela vi gi'mizikevo gotine izikelizave. Evene' golosolo' vi gi'mizilizadoti' nene lutine lengemeni dameni vo goloso oloseive li gizikani' ma nene lamine' gizi nizani' neive.

Ido' O'moso nene zou lo minaa' monovo do soto' o-ledaa' ive mino aza nene ei' evenele sipisipi ize ne'mine gelo minunive leli' gizebo vete naba Izesu' Kilisito' aza vanise've lepo leli' gele daloningumu' ve lo O'moso'mo lo huko-lidine' minevo' minevo' iline' gamazi do amuzo molavo gohi hilinguti' do ote-dine' ne'mo
Nemu' nene O'moso'mo Guvelesi ve hele neinguti' do ote-dine' ve. Ido' a'mine'mine ogo amuzo'vedunu' lelikisi hele noloninguti' do ote-ledeleseive.
Nemu' nene naza a'ne hite-giduvongu' O'moso'mo gonou' amuzo lehize-gedavo geita neine' nene gaza amuzo molo do otezo lo gaka noduve.

Nemu' nene mono' gamazi lamine' nene hilavetidasi vo heteline' ve. Ingine haza oko'inesi minani' gameneu' nene O'moso'mo evene' muki' o-ledaa' neine' ne'mino engikisi goni' o-ngedo lihime ngemavo hilani'za ingine sikalahu'inesi mini O'moso'mo minevo' minevo' oga' neidi'mine igi minivi' minivi' ilizangumu' ve losa a'mine mono' gamazi lamine' nene engitasi hulavo vo heteline' ve.
Ee, Izesu' aza minevo' alevo've hulo lengikumu' helo lengi' meni hizavo ei' inite've lili' ikeni' nizanaze. Nemu' nene misubou' alevete meni hizi-lingidikevo engi' goboni gono di-ngidi minamilo.

Ido' evene' linge malite O'mosola nene inite' ato atokumu' emenga laa' ido' uvonga avanga li-daa' ikevo O'moso'mo angelo' ma imiselavo ogo lihime ngemo ngibiline' nenaze. Laza nene ingine lani' ne'mino O'moso uvonga avanga lo-damolone.

Evene' hamolitesi lisihe' mo amune'za laza nene evene' linge muki' go'ine izi moni polopeti lili' ilisa O'moso'mi gamazi di monaa' nadi'mine amo O'moso'mo do ote-ledavo asi've O'moso ninge neivosa nene Kilisitoda mine molo mino do voziu' vomiu' amo gono lisihe' lamine' dosa nene O'moso'mi gamazi laa' nounako a'mine gono nene leli' ne ha dalonido' o neive.
Laza monoku' amuzo molo nonive nene leli' lutelokovo' ogo molo minamo monoku' gilizevo i nizave hize ele' o-ngedo engi' geni ngibiline' inite' nene lazasi gehe-ngedelonido' o neive.
Ido' Guvelesi vemu' gele ele'vole' o nouvoni' nenako nemu' nene neni' nesi mo lite' lo lengita alosuve losa gele mu'musi' o nouve.

Neloti' ma ninguvoni' nene angelo' seta've seta've misubo lumola lumola oti'mi vi nizavo ninguve. Ingine misubolo' nehe guvo nosolo' nehe za mukito' nehe ne hepe' elo do goloso ogalive li a'mine misubolo' hepe' eleline' hepe' seta've seta've nene di gili' li mini' mini' ani' ve.

Ee, gomu' lingine O'moso'mi evenele minamave heta ato' velite ngumo helaa' ine' monovo goloso igi mili'mi dizani' nene mo moda ve lo noluze. Gohi amilo. A'mine goloso monovo nene ado' ne'mine mana'mine monovo goloso longovozo hilami gopo iga', inite' goloso mamu' lutine otaa', nosolo' moni sipaki goloso iga', noso' nite' naba ni zohi' igi noso ni sipaki iga' ido' noso naa' pati di soto' iga' ido' soza o'moso nge'metaa' monovo goloso iga' ani' mamu' nene noluze. Mo hulilo.

Ido' engi' biluva'ine a'mine ve seta' do goloso o-ngedelone li ave muki' nene a'mine ve setalitisi ve'ninguti' olo' gulumo ne'mo nene lemo gize' vote-ngedaa' neive. Ee, engi' di goloso i-ngidilisa gililizave nene ne'minisa di goloso i-ngidikesivo ne'minisa hililizado' o neive.

Likevo Paulo' aza ti' lo line': Lingine zuho gizebo o-lengedaa' ive guvelesi ve dovo' ledevo' amozo li gizikevo neine' ma nenako aza nene eveneto' medelo mino O'moso inite' lehize-daa' ive naba neive lo giluvodini ne'mine lo ma lamuvodine.

Ne neiha evene' ma ize gulo monovo'inesi minave poisini inite' pata' di monaa' avesi ido' vene' vemoho' monovo goloso gopo' napa' iga' avesi ido' evene' ngibili hilaa' avesi ido' soza o'mosolo' gelekele' i-ngidi gubi' izi ngimi ngopo'ni laa' avesi ido' soza gamazimu' lanite' gili laa' ave muki' nesi nene a'mine numuno ebeku' nene dizami haza hetavo' minilisave.

Ne neiha lengita inite' linge ngomo ma neine' nene edamive lo gele nouve. A'mine nene evene' linge ma Balaamu' gamene gomuta apize ngimine' monovo ha di minaa' nave nene lengiku' ma nizave. A'mine monovo nene ado' Balaamu' ne'mo guvelesi ve Balaki'ni aka elebizavo aza Isilaele' aleve ngimimise' ivo ingine soza o'moso ngimani' noso' nite' nisa vene' vemoho' gopo' napa ingaa' ani' ve.

Leze zuho mate, Izesu'nimu' gili ele'vole' iga' nani' nene naba ogavo lutine hamo hamo' ge neme ne geme li minaa' nani' nesi naba ogavo nemu' nene O'moso opo'ni lolonido' lisihe' ogavo gamene gamene lengikumu' ve lo opo'ni laa' noune.

Lingine gomu' O'mosomu' gilami nizavo gatine hizi gopo lengele'mizi vadaa vada nene nanite' nge'meti vaa' ani' neve. Lingine soza o'moso gamazi lisa'mani' initekovo' nge'meti vaa' ani' nene mo gili nizave.
Kilisito' aza nene evenele zuho mulise nene lulo limidi'mo lelikumu' oko'no hulo hiline' nenaze. Vemoho' lingine a'mine'mine igi eledingine nene lutine ngimilo.
Evene' malite di goloso i-lingidikevo ma nene a'mido' di tine' mili di goloso i-ngidamilo. Asi evene' mukiliti ve'nido' nene monovo lamine' ogave li ningilizani' monovovo' nene igi mili minilo.

Ido' O'moso neve nene ne'mine oga' neine' nenako nemu' nene lingine ei' molani' gamene soto' ilingu' nene do ote-ledelingumu' ve li lengi' okodine nene di'mi limisa O'moso'mi anau' vi mini ei' amuzo've nabalokovo' nene lehete i minisa

Lamine' nenako aza nene eze monovo ngelebizamo haza minine' nevoba eze monovo ningilizave lo do lamine' o-lengedo Okulumokuti' nene goline gamenesi noso' nite' vai' laa' ine' gamenesi lingimivo nivi' nivi' igi mini muludingu' lamine' gilaa' nave.

Ido' engikisi bizi minani' vene' neve nene evenelite gamangi mili-ngidilizado' lisihe' i minani' vene' minii divi ledivi' gamazi li-ngidisa'mani' vene' mini negi hizami monovo'nido' gizebo lamine' igi mini ne'mine mana'mine gono dalizani' nene monovo lisihetokovo' e'metisa di minilizani' vene' minilizave.
Ido' a'mine ne'mino gopo monaa' monovomu' nene lulo do velepe' izelihe lo lihime emamo ninge mate-miko gamene imuha lulo ma do velepe' izelesa gelamive.

A'mine gamene neu' Tilo alevemukisi ido' Sidoni alevemukisi Helode' izebolo' goloso molavo lovo gize ngimine'. Lovo gize ngemavo a'mine misubo ne'mi me'ninge nete gamazi'ine di hamo' igi ingine zuho noso' inite'ine guvelesi ve'mi misuboloti' meni hizi ni minani' nenako nemu' nene vi gomu' lele'mize lamine' ilingumu' ve li Helode' oko'nolo' niteto' gizebo o-daa' ive ma gulive Bilasito'ni gala di Helode' neida dizi igi zogo imi mulunou' do hongu liline' gamazi li-imani' ve.

Ne'mine likevo a'mido' Izesu' ti' lo lo-ngimine': Naza sikalahu' goloso neve nene mo keke' lu'neu' nomive noluve. Asi me'nehine nene gelekele' o-do do naba o-daa' nouve. Ne'mine oga' nouvoni'za lingine ne'mine i-nidami di limi-nidilisa iga' nave.
Gi'mizamivo haza nivavo hepe' nene amuzo malehe goloso noilivo noso nene amuzo molo sii' naba goloso olosa ine'.

Naza idise mela nene geni mulumo alumo nite' gehaa' noune' nemu' nene amuzo molo ti' lo gele nouve: Alinge' soto' o-ledeline' inite' ado' O'moso'mo do naba o-lidivo lamine' minelone' monovo ne'mo nene inite' naba goloso neine' nenako a'mine genimu' nene mo gele hulolonido' lisihe' o neive.
Izipaha'ne zuho mate, Izesu'nimu' ve lo O'moso'mo lihimetine hulo-lengede neive. Nemu' luhuvo nite' mene nogize-lingiduve.

A'mine amuzo gimive O'moso ne'mo leli' elese molo-ledo do lu' izo do eita o-lidine' nene evene' monovo lamine' uningumu' nene ne'mine ine' nevoba asi olihe inite' mata' do soto' amo asi'vevo' minida vomine aza nasahili' Izesu' Kilisitongu' lehize-ledelesuve lo ei' lulolo' do lisihe' okido' e'meto ine' ve.

Ne'mine nolivo eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' aveti ve naba'ine netesi ido' Zuda veti pilisi ve netesi Izesu'ni niningi geke' li lohoto' zalo' belezo belezo lani' ve. Likevo Pilato' aza a'mido' ti' lo lo-ngimine' ve: Ne'mine lii ma naza neve nene eze goni' o-do lihime emeloni' monovo've nene vise' ogo ma ningamuze. Neni' nene ne'mine amolosuze. Langisetine di vi lohoto' zalo' bililo.

O'moso'mo leli' lehize-ledelesa gele minine' nasahilikumu' li soto' ika' ika' iga' ave gozopo' minani' polohete nete nene a'mine a'me luvoni' gamazi ado' O'moso'mo lukuvo lemeline' nene nado lemelive li ne'mi monovomu' nene gelelone li vise' ika' ika' i'mi vi minani' ve.

Soza mono' li evene' ngele'mize gopo iga' ave muki' soto' igi misubou' misubou' nimonave. Ingine Izesu' Kilisito' aza leli' haza eveneliti okode ne'minesi soto' ine' ve li gili imisa'mave. A'ne'mine ve nene soza mono' li evene' ngele'mize gopo iga' ave mini Kilisito'ni lovo i imaa' ave nizave.

A'mine ve mene monovo goloso oga' ive mino misubou' misubou' mono Zuda ve mukiliti mulu'ningu' hizo lovo hizilizangumu' do avito' molo-ngedaa' neive. Ne'mine ogo Nasalete ve'mi mono' laa' aveti ve naba'ine ma neive.

Ido' suno' gamazi leli' monoteu' soto' ogo minine' nene gamazi naba neive lo lo soto' oga' noune' nene ado' Kilisito' ei' nene leli' okode ne'mine do otuho soto' ogo minavoo ei' monovo've nene mo lisihe' o neive lo Sikalahuli'mo do soto' ogo lelebizavosa angelo' ma netesi nene ningikevo evene' zuho ato atotidasi gamazi've nene li soto' igi li-ngimikevo me misubouko aleve linge netesi nene ezemu' gili ele'vole' ani' ve. Ido' eze nene O'moso'mo Okulumo' ebe' laminekuko ele'mizo dizine' ve.

Ne'mine ogavo okulumokuti' nene osupo gihile naba' naba ado' gihile hamo hamoli'mo geni've vanu hadeti (100) pauni (foti faef kilo (45Kg)) ne'mine mineka' mineka' ine' nene eveneto' limi'mi vani' ve. Ne'mine neivo a'mine nene inite' goloso gehepeve soto' o-ngidine' nenako a'mine osupo gihile eveneto' di'mozi' mozi' ani' nemu' nene a'mine aleve ingine O'moso divi ledivika li-dani' ve.

Ido' ne'mino lo osu' loloseine'za aza lo huko lo-lidine' gamazi do gihile izo monovo lisihe' laminekovo' mineline' Okulumo' atoli'mine gosohokisi misubo atoli'mine gosohokisi do soto' o-ledeleseive lo a'minemu' gilingili ogo gizebo ogo none.
Ido' okulumo' nene mati di gangaa' nani' ne'mino gango vo haha ine' ve. Ido' golo muki' nesi ido' ailani muki' nesi nene minani' ebe'ine hulisa ebe' mala vi minani' ve.
Ido' Kilisito' aza O'moso'mi lulolo' e'meto leli' mukikumu' nene gamene hamokovo' oko'no hulo helo O'moso imine' ne'mo lute do lisihe' o-ledo O'moso gelekele' o-do minelone' evenele lolo' o-ledave.
Laza lingine mukikumu' ve lo gamene gamene O'moso opo'ni lovo' lovo' oga' noune. Ido' gosele' lebelamivo lengikumukisi O'mosola lo minaa' noune.

Ne'mine lavo hosi gohi ma soto' ogo ani' nene olo' gulumo ne'mine gulehe' hosi ani' ve. Ido' a'mine hosilo' daa' ive nene evene' ge nebele hele ne gebele hele li minilizangumu' nene misuboukoti' hongu lo lamino minaa' monovo nene ipe' ogo do vilive lo O'moso'mo gele emosa bainati mite' naba ma emavo dani' ve.

Evene' malitesi nene O'moso'mi gulive di'mi limi apize lengemaa' noune' monote nesi nene divi ledivi' ikelizaze. Evene' malite gelekele' gono gihi-ngidikevo engi' gonou' inite'ine ne'mine lili' i minave muki' ingine a'mine gelekele' gono gihi-ngidaa' avemu' nene gilunivo diziivo' minilizado' o neive li gili gelekele' lamine' i-ngidivo' minilisave.
Lengiku' gamazi lilizangu' nene sozasi lamilo. Lingine gomu' lengemeni damenisi ido' a'mine'mo ogo molo oga' ine' monovo've golososi nene di hulisa

ne'mino mo gele nouvoni'za lengita monovo ma neine' nene mo edamive lo gele nouve. A'mine monovo nene ado' vene' Zezabele' aza polohete nouve lo neni' gelekele' evene'ne ma nene ngele'mize gopo ogo vene' vemoho' gopo' napa ingi'mi monaa' monovolokisi ido' soza o'moso ngimani' noso' nite' naa' monovolokisi nene apize ngemaa' neine' vene' neve nene ningi gosele' i-dami ningi mati-daa' naangumu' nene noluve.

Ido' Abalahamu' a'vopilemo' minamani' evene' heta ato' ve inginesi O'mosomu' alinge' gili ele'vole' ikevo nemu' nene O'moso'mo lihime'ine hulo-ngedo do lisihe' o-ngedeline' nene mo gele mino aza O'moso'mo a'minemu' nene Abalahamu'ni gamazi lamine' ti' lo lo-imine' mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizani' ma neive: Geitati' no'nohoka nene evene' zuho ato ato' mukita do soto' o-ngedelesuve.

Lengi' monoku' gizebo i-lingidaa' nave nete di minaa' nani' gono'ine ne'mi monovomu' nene alinge' gamene nabalo' O'moso'mi velelo' li soto' ilisanako nemu' gili mini ingine nene lengi' monovotido' gizebo lamine' igi di lisihe' i-lingidivo' minaa' nave. Nemu' nene lengikumu' geni ngebelamivo gono'ine nene ngolize izi lu'ine laminetotikovo' daa' ilizave li lingine engi' gamazi lilizado' gili di mini gelekelekovo' i-ngidi minilo. Ee, ingine lengikumu' gosele' ve li geni ngibilivo gono dalizani' ne'mo lengi' lengele'mize lamine' amilizado' o neine' nenako nemu' liliza gamazilo' nene gelekelekovo' i-ngidi minilo.

Ne'mine ogo Kanaha misubou' evene' gulive'ine ato atokisi zuho seveni nene ngebele gese' ogo engi' misubo'ine nene avotemotine ize' molo ngemavo go'nido' go'nido' di nizavo kilisimasi fo hadeti fifti (450) ogo vine'.
Evene' malite mono' gihile lamine' Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' gamazi mono' monovo lisiheto' lele'mize molaa' neido' nene lu'ine milami gamazi ato' apizi ngimilizani' nene
Evene' malite Kilisito' gamazi've di minami mono' apizi lingimilisa nilavo ma lingine ngele'mizi numudingu' milamilo. Ido' mese' aseka li-ngidamilo.

Ido' ne'mine noluvoni' nene nemu' noluve. Laza nene Kilisito' mulumo gilidi'mine ogo mulumo vauve elo gelaa' noune'za a'mingu' nene O'moso'mo Kilisito'nimu' ve lo hize ele' nesi vauve elo o-ledaa' neive.

Agae, engi' nene mo mulumo gono dalisave. Ee, ingine Kaini' eikumukovo' gelaa' ine' monovo malo' e'metikeve. Ido' moni heneni dalone li Balaamu' aka laminetoti' zovo' izo vo monilo' lulo molani' ma'mine monovolo' amuzo mili e'metikeve. Ido' ma nene Kola' ine' ne'mine igi ingine nene O'moso'mo line' gamazimu' nene o'ove li biluva' i-daa' nani' nenako labuluvo ine' ne'mine igi labuluvo ilisa nave.

Ne'mine ine'za me noluve nene gili hehe lamilizado' o minine' initekumukisi nene ganu' li gamazi goloso laa' nave. Ido' ingine inite' linge mamu' gilaa' nani' nene nama gaha ize gulolite haza oko'ine'mo lanite' giline' initekumukovo' gilaa' nani' ngemenilo' nene di milisa gilaa' nani' nenako nemu' nene a'mine gilaa' nani' initelite nene ngele'mize goloso iga' nave.

Ido' O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' oga' ive gohi ma Noa'ni nene O'moso'mo evene' ngebeleleseive line' noso nene olihe soto' amivo a'mine noso soto' ilingumu' nene lo soto' ogo lo-emavo Noa' aza O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo minine' ne'mo aza vene' izipesi goloso ogalone lo O'moso'mo lido' gele lamine' o mino sipi ma lolo' ogo noso velo angu' nene gipele zuhosi vene' izipesi nene do ngu' izine'. Ido' ne'mine ogo O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo minine' ne'mo misubouko aleve linge engita monovo goloso minine' nene ngelebizine'. Ido' O'moso'mo ezemu' gili ele'vole' igi minaa' ave mukiliti lu'ine nene do lisihe' o-ngedaa' neine' nenako Noa' aza ne'mine ogo O'mosomu' gele ele'vole' ogo minine' ne'mo nene ei' Noa' lulosi do lisihe' o-dine' ve.

Ido' a'mine inite' nene di va'va' igi osu' likevo eveneto' medeli mini O'moso inite' lehizi-daa' ave ingine mono' gono'ine nene nidi a'mine mono' numungu' gana' izi hukikani' numuno lulou' nene gamene gamene dizaa' naha

Ne'mine lo Setehano' aza kanisole aleve lo-ngemo imine' molo ti' lo line': Lingine a'manapa igi gamazi gilamaa' igi mini lutine gatine ngolo' lamivo avotinge igi mili iga' ani' suno ma'mine igisa lingine O'moso'mi Sikalahu' lovo i imaa' nave.

Ee, a'mine lou' gamazi neve nene evene' lisihe' i minavemu' nomive. Asi evene' ma lou' gamazilo' e'metamaa' ave gizengizelo' ve nizahe ido' O'mosomu' ngehelele izamaa' ive lihimelo' ve nizahe nemukisi ido' monovo lisihe' lamineto' e'metami mono'ine nomine' minave nizahe ido' me'ningine ize'ningine ngibili hilaa' ido' evene' ngibili hulaa' ave nizahe nemukisi ido'
Luhuvo inite' gomu' ma ti' lo gize lingimuvoni' ma neive: Lingine nene vene' vemoho' monovo goloso gopo' napa iga' avesi bizi moni zogo mili namilo lo lo-lengede nouvoni' ma neive.

Ido' ne'mine noluvoni' nene nemu' noluve: Naza nene olosa gelamuvoni' inite' monovo goloso nene ogo molo ogo mino naza gosele' gehepeve nebelaa' neine' inite' nene ha oga' nouve. Ne'mine oga' nouvoni' nene nanimu' nouhe nemu' nene mo gelesi amuve.

Ne'mine igi mini Guvetesi ve do lu' izaa' ive Izesu' Kilisito' ninge lamine' oga' neine' monovolo' e'metaa' naani' nene gohi di naba i'mi vi mini eze monovo danava've nesi nene gili ngolo' li'mi vi minilo. Eita guvele soto' oga' neine' monovo've nene minevo minevo' ogo idisesi alingetasi mine do vo minilihoo. Mo ne'mino minelive. Moda a'nesi' ve.

Laza nene Kilisito'ni e'metuningumu' ve losa negi ve ne'mino none'za lengi' nene Kilisitoda imi hili lengikumu' nene laza monoku' otohato ve none li gilaa' nave. Ido' laza nene amuzo molamune'za lingine lengikumu' nene amuzo malehe none laa' nave. Lingine nene evenelite lengikumu' gilavo dizaa' neive li laa' naha leli' nene evenelite divi ledivika li-lidaa' nave.

Mulumo geni lengi' nigihi-lingidani' ne'mino nene lengi' zuho Kilisito' evenele misubo vaiku' mini'mi monave engikisi nene a'mine'mine igi nigihi-ngidani' nenako lingine nemu' gili mini Kilisito'nimu' gele ele'vole' iga' nani' nene di gili' li minisa a'mine biluvatine nene lovo i imivo' minilo.

Ido' gonou' ve lingine nene me misubouko gizebo i-lingidaa' naavetine nene gamene gamene gelekele' i-ngidivo' minaa' ilo. Ido' ne'mini gelekele' i-ngidilizani' nene lengi' gizebo vetinelite lengikumu' ningi lamine' gililizave li engi' ve'nido' nene gono amuzo mili daa' naave gili gono di miniisa alinge' ingine ningamavo gono gilizevo igi di minaa' ne'mine nene amii asi Guvelesi vemu' golise gili mini lutine gonotidokovo' mili mini gono di minilo.

Ido' a'mine loposo niteli'mi komu've teni ningaine' nene ingine guve'inesi ve naba' naba tenimu' nene nizave. Ingine olihe guve'inesi ve mini eveneto' gizebo iga' gono api' igi damani'za alinge' a'mine loposo nite' nesi maka' a'mine gono dalizangumu' nene gamene li'nibemukovo' amuzo di mini gono dalisave.

Ido' Kilisito' evenele leze Sikalahute nene me misubou' soto' ine' nomive. Laza O'moso'mo inite' ato ato' nolehize-lidine' nene a'minemu' ningo geleloningumu' ve losa O'mosolati' do ogo do ti' une' ne neive.
Heneni nganeni ve lingine gililo. Mulumo nite' naba linginela soto' ilingumu' geke' geke' li ive nama igi minilo.

Ido' mulumo geni gihi-lingidilisa navo lingine mo gihilisa nangumu' nene mo golisesi gilamilo. Lingine gililo. Ve goloso ne'mo nene lengemengu' molo do ningelesa evene' ma do ote-ngedavo ingine lengikuti' evene' linge ma nene nala' numungu' huli-lingidilisa naaze. Mulumo geni inite' nene lengito' soto' ogo neivo gamene li'nibe gamene teni a'ne'minevo' nene mineleseive. Ne neiha nenito' gi'mizi minilizangumu' lingibili hililisa ilizangumukisi gili huli nenito' nene ha gi'mizi gilikovo' li minilo. Ne'mine ma ilizani' ne'mi meni've nene naza minevo' minevo' minaa' lengemeni nene lehize-lengedelesuve.

Ne'mine iga' nani'za O'moso'mi gonolo' ve gaza me luvoni' monovo golosoloti' nene golise ogo mehenga emo mene lo-gemeloni' monovo nene imiselo dalosa amuzo molozo. Ado' monovo lisihekovo' ogakisi mono' monovolo' e'metaakisi Guvelesi vemu' gele ele'vole' ogakisi lute ngemaa' monovo nesi ido' geni inite' soto' ilingu' zege' zege' ogakisi hongu monovo evene' ngelebizo minaakisi nene dalinge. Imiselezo.

Lingine me misubou' mini noso' nitetine vai' ivo nivi' nivi' igi mini lanite' ato atoli'mine gili ize ne'mine gehesani'. Ne'mine igi gehesi minikeni'za O'moso'mo lengebeleline' gamene nene mo noalitive.

Ido' a'mine Guvelesi ve'mi mo'mosi'velo' vodo vodo ogo mo'mosi' gohi tuvedi fo'a (24) minavo a'mine mo'mosito' nene gizebo ve tuvedi fo'a (24) genegana mokonokovo' ngili mini godo'nido' inite' ma kuvanadi ne'mine ngolidunu' lili' ani' gihikani' nene mito' minani' ve.

Aza nene ei' oko'no do dizo mino oko'no'mo lanite' giline' monovolokovo' geli geli ogo do'mo vo mine do dizine' votigilelo' nene di milisa di'mi limi-di mulumo alumo gelaa' ido' mulunou' mulumo alumo gelaa' ilido' di mili i-dilo. Aza nene lulou' ti' lo laa' neive: Naza nene guve'nesi vene' dizo nouvoni' vene' ma nene nouve. Evene'ne zuho ngeli ma hilamilisanako ngelo mulumo alumo gelo ma minamolosuve.

Ido' va'ninge lingine eledinginemu' luvodi'mine ogo ti' lo nolo-lingimuve: Lingine nene O'mosola laa' olone' akate nene goloso ogalive li eledinginemu' nene ingine amuzo damani' mini lelitoti' nene limisa nizave li ngele'mize lamine' igi mini O'moso'mo lehize-ledavo minevo' alevo' oga' lemeni dameni nene engikisi lelikisi makato' dalonive ne nizave li ele'vole' i-ngidami asi gili nge li mini zou li makato' lamini bizi minilo.
Vene' neve nene vemoho' gamazi apize ngemaa' nehe vemoho' ngivile' o mino gizebo o-ngedaa' nehe ne'mine ilizangumu' nene gele ngemamo o'ove noluze. Vene' ingine elese' ikiivo' minilizave.

O'moso'mi gipele leli' Guvetesi ve Izesu' Kilisito' eikisi lutine hamo' ogavo minilizave lo lengele'mize molave ei' nene gote izesa'mine' ve. Ido' eze gamazi line' nene vo haza amiline' nenako nemu' a'mine luvoni' gamazi nene asi've O'moso ne'mo do soto' ogo do gihile izeleseive.

Ne neiha O'moso'mo lengi' nene elese molo-lengedo do eita o-lingidine' nene lingine Mose' lou' gamazilo' gelekele' igi a'mine'mi goboni ve galapuso aleve ne'mini minami haza aleve minilizave losa elese molo-lengedo do eita o-lingidine' nenako nemu' nene ve ma ingine a'mine Mose' lou' gamazi'mi gesi mingu' nene vi minilizave li lengele'mizi gopo igi okodine lolovo huki huli-lingidilisa gilaa' nave ingine lengi' okodine lolovo nene huki hulilizado' nomine' nenako inite' ato' gohi ma huki hulilisa gili ma engi' inite'inesi vai' nene nanimu' huki hulamave. Ee, neze zuho mate, O'moso'mo goboni ve minami haza aleve minilizave lo elese molo-lengedo do eita o-lengedani'za lingine laza nene lou' gamazi'mi goboni ve minamune' nenako olosa gilune' inite' muki' nene ha olosune li okodine'mo goloso initekumu' lanite' gelaa' neine' ne'mo lengele'mize gopo iline' aka've vilikelizave. Ne'mine ami evene' lute ngemaa' monovolo' gelekele' igi ge nasahili' o-nede ne nasahili' o-gede li minilo.

Ido' O'moso'mo evene' muki' ize' molo-ledelesa nene lihime monovolo' gelekele' ogo minuninguti' apase-ledaa' ine' lou' gamazi've nene gili di minahe gili hulahe lo ize' molo-ledeleseive. Ne'mine ilingumu' nene gilii lingine gamazi lilizadokisi inite' igi mili ilizadokisi gizebo igi minilo.
Ido' mono' gonolo' ve nene gono ato ato' muki' nene ha dalisani'za Guvelesi ve hamokumukovo' nene gono dalisave.

A'mine Zuda ve nene gomu' guve'ine gelaa' unive muki' Abalahamule Mosele engikuti' nene soto' ani' ve. Ido' Kilisito' nene O'mosolati' soto' ine'za helala evenetati' soto' ine' nene mo a'mine zuhoti vaniseuti' soto' ine' ve. Ido' Kilisito' aza inite' mata' mukito' Guvelesi ve minive mino mo O'moso ne neive. Eze opo'ni lo'mo vo mineso' nene mo huko vamivo opo'ni lo mine do volonive ne neize. Mo ne'mino miniliho.

Laza mulumo gono nodune' nene O'moso'mo lengi' hize ele' o-lengedo do lungu' izelingumu' ve losa nene nodune. Ido' O'moso'mo leli' hize ele' o-lede neine' ne'mo nene lengi' hize ele' o-lengedelingumu' ve lo hize ele' o-lede neive. Laza mulumo gono nodunidi'mine igi linginesi nene mulumo gono di ha gihi di dizi minilizani' ne'mo nene O'moso'mo a'mine'mine ogo hize ele' o-lengedeleseive.
Ido' Kilisitoda gi'mize gili' lo mineloningumu' lezesi lengikisi hize ele' oga' ive nene O'moso ei' nene neive. Aza nene ei' gonolo' lele'mize molani' ve.
Ti' lo lavo gamazi ma imine' molo ti' lo line': O'moso'mo inite' mamu' goloso nite' do hulo do lamine' ogavo ma a'mine inite' nene mo ha nite' ve goloso nite' ve lamo ha dalosane.

Ne'mine lavo Izesu' a'mido' ti' lo lo-imine': Naza nemeni dameni lengelebizeloni' aka ne'mino neive: Ve ma ingine lu'ine neni' nimi minilizave nete nene neni' gamazi'nelo' e'meti gili di minilisave. Ne'mine ikevo me'neho lulo ngemavo azasi nazasi engita ogo mine molo minelesusive.
Lute ngemali'mi monovo ti' ogo neive: Laza lute O'moso emamunivosa asi've gomu' lulo lemo lelito' medelo mino oko'no hulo helo lihimete apase-ledelive lo gipeleine imiseline' ve.

Ne neiha aza nene labanaku' neine' ne'mino lazasi a'mine'mine ogo labanaku' minevo alevo' olone' nene lute do hamo' ogo lamine' bizo minelesune. Ido' ne'mine okunivo gipele Izesu' vanise ne'mo nene goloso nitete mudise gilite lede'mo vo neivo laminovo' minelesune.

Nemu' nene gaza goboni ve ido' gelekele' ve ne'mine gohi ma minamo asi O'moso'mi izipahala ne nane. Ido' mo izipahala lolo' ogo nane' nenako O'moso'mo nasahili' o-gedavo gazasi nene eze zuhomu' salani molo-ngidine' initekuti' dalinive lolo' ogane.

Ne'mine o neine'za gipelemu' neve mono' godolou' ti' lo line': O'mosoo, gaza gizebo oga' mo'mosikau' gizebo ogo mineline' nene huko vamo minevo' minevo' ogo mineleseive. Mineleseinako Guvekasi ve lolo' ogo mineline' ne'mi monovo nene monovo do lisihe' oga' monovo nene mineleseive.

Ne'mine lavo a'mido' nene Zuda ve ingine ti' li li-imani': Laza geheni gebelelesa noune' nene gono lamine' daningumu' nevoba asi O'moso ivile' iline' gamazi laine' nemu' nene geheni gebelelesa noune. Nene nanitekumu' ve. Gaza nene haza evenelike O'moso lolo' ogo gamazi laine' nemu' ve.

Ee, a'mine loposo nitetokisi ido' a'mine'mi avazahalokisi gelekele' i-di opo'ni li a'mine loposo niteli'mi maki ado' gulive've'mi luhuvo've ma dalizave mukita nene gamene gamene go' liliha liti'muso izeliha mulumo nene matamivo minii mo mini gilamilisave. Ee, mo a'mine oloku' mini mulumo alumo gilivi' gilivi' igivo' minilizadi'mo sokile've nesi dizeline' nene mo huko vamivo mo dizevo dizevo' ogovo' mineleseive.
Ne'mino neine' nenako O'moso'mo asi've lulo lamine' lemosa a'mine mono' gono lamine' mene lemavo do do vo minaa' nouningu' nene gosele' ogo muludeu' goloso ogavo ma hulosa'mune.

nemu' nene laza gopo gate gelamo ezemu' gele ele'vole' ogo mono' godolou' ti' li gizi nizani' gamazi ma nene ha ti' lo lolosune: Guvelesi ve aza hize ele' o-ledaa' neinako laza inite' mamu' lehelele izelido' nomivo ido' evene' nete ma di goloso i-lidilizado' minamune.

Noso' nite' ato ato' muki' naa' nave nete noso' nite' ma malise iga' navemu' nene gilavo haza nite' ve li gilikelizave. Ido' O'moso ne'mo nene noso' nite' muki' gopo naa' avesi nene mo ei' ve lo ngele'mize molani' nenako nemu' nene noso' nite' malise iga' ave nete noso' nite' muki' gopo naa' aveti monovomu' nene ize' mili lamilizado' o neive.
